5pt\">\r\n <v:imagedata src=\"file:///C:/Users/Lenovo/AppData/Local/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_image001.png\" o:title=\"\" chromakey=\"white\">\r\n</v:imagedata></v:shape></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">karena katrol tidak memberikan hambatan rotasi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">percepatan beban bergantung hanya pada massa\r\nbeban, bukan massa katrol</span></p>', '<p><br></p>', NULL, 'A', -2.001, 1, 1, '2026-04-16 06:59:49', '2026-04-16 07:00:06'),
(224, '5CRoD03', NULL, 14, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Pada suatu hari, Rahmat melakukan beberapa\r\nkegiatan berikut.</span></p><p><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\">(i) Mengayuh sepeda</font></p><p><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\">(ii) Bermain jungkat-jungkit dengan temannya</font></p><p><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\">(iii) Mendorong meja pada bidang datar yang licin</font></p><p><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\">(iv) Mendorong gerobak sampah</font></p><p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Budi menyadari bahwa tidak semua kegiatan\r\ntersebut melibatkan kecenderungan benda untuk berotasi terhadap suatu titik\r\natau sumbu tertentu, meskipun sama-sama melibatkan gaya. Kombinasi kegiatan\r\nyang benar-benar merupakan penerapan torsi, beserta alasan yang paling tepat\r\nadalah....</span><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\"></font></p>', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:18.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">i dan ii, karena gaya selalu bekerja pada benda yang bergerak<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:18.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">i dan iv, karena penggunaan tali selalu menghasilkan torsi<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:18.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\"><span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;</span></span><!--[endif]--><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">ii dan iii, karena gaya digunakan untuk memindahkan benda berat<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:18.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">iii dan iv, karena torsi berkaitan langsung dengan besar momentum\r\nbenda<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">ii dan i, karena gaya bekerja pada jarak\r\ntertentu dari titik tumpu sehingga menimbulkan rotasi.</span></p>', '<p><br></p>', NULL, 'E', -2.000, 1, 1, '2026-04-16 07:04:28', '2026-04-16 07:04:28'),
(225, '5BRoD01', NULL, 14, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Gambar 37 menunjukkan piringan putar dengan\r\nsepotong kecil permen karet yang digantung di atasnya. Sensor optik yang\r\nterhubung ke perekam data mengukur kecepatan sudut piringan putar.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1776323082_69e08a0a741ae.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin: 10px 0px;\"><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Gambar 37. Piringan putar</font></p><p><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\">Piringan dirancang untuk berputar terlebih dahulu sebelum berputar bebas. Gumpalan permen karet dijatuhkan dari ketinggian kecil di atas piringan dan menempel padanya.</font></p><p><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\">Piringan putar berbentuk cakram padat dengan momen inersia I = 12MR<sup>2</sup></font></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Permen karet adalah bola padat dengan momen inersia I = 25MR</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Berdasarkan informasi eksperimen, untuk menentukan besar perubahan energi kinetik rotasi piringan putar dari saat sebelum permen karet dijatuhkan hingga segera setelah menempel pada piringan putar adalah....</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">perubahan energi kinetik rotasi hanya ditentukan\r\noleh perubahan kecepatan sudut karena momen inersia seluruh sistem tetap</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">perubahan energi kinetik rotasi ditentukan oleh\r\nperubahan momen inersia sistem dan perubahan kecepatan sudut, karena tumbukan\r\ninelastik menambah massa pada radius tertentu</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">perubahan energi kinetik rotasi hanya\r\ndipengaruhi oleh massa permen karet karena permen karet menyebabkan gaya ke\r\nbawah yang memperlambat rotasi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">perubahan energi kinetik rotasi terutama\r\ndipengaruhi oleh energi potensial permen karet saat jatuh karena energi itu\r\nhilang dari sistem rotasi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">perubahan energi kinetik rotasi ditentukan oleh\r\nbesar gaya gesekan udara yang bekerja tepat saat permen karet menempel pada\r\npiringan</span></p>', '<p><br></p>', NULL, 'D', 0.000, 1, 1, '2026-04-16 21:11:53', '2026-04-16 21:11:53'),
(226, 'IMO001', NULL, 16, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:15.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n5.0pt;margin-left:0cm;background:#E8F4FD\"><b><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;color:#1A5276;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV\">Kasus 1: Energi Surya sebagai Sumber Energi Masa Depan</span></b><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\">Matahari memancarkan energi dalam jumlah sangat besar setiap detiknya.\r\nEnergi ini dapat diserap oleh panel surya melalui efek fotovoltaik, yaitu\r\nproses di mana foton cahaya matahari menabrak elektron pada material\r\nsemikonduktor (biasanya silikon) pada panel surya sehingga menghasilkan arus\r\nlistrik. Panel surya tidak memerlukan bahan bakar, tidak menghasilkan emisi\r\nsaat beroperasi, dan dapat dipasang di atap rumah maupun lahan terbuka.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Di Indonesia, potensi energi surya sangat besar\r\nkarena letak geografisnya di garis khatulistiwa yang mendapatkan sinar matahari\r\nrata-rata 4-5 jam per hari secara efektif. Namun, pemanfaatannya masih terbatas\r\nakibat biaya awal pemasangan yang tinggi dan keterbatasan teknologi penyimpanan\r\nenergi.</span></p><p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Berdasarkan\r\nbacaan, prinsip kerja panel surya dalam menghasilkan listrik adalah...</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Mengubah energi cahaya matahari menjadi listrik melalui efek\r\nfotosintesis</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Mengubah energi panas matahari menjadi listrik melalui panel surya</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Mengubah energi cahaya matahari menjadi listrik\r\nmelalui efek fotovoltaik</span></p>', '<span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Menyimpan energi cahaya matahari menjadi listrik melalui panel surya</span>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Mengubah energi panas matahari menjadi listrik melalui efek fotovoltaik</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Mengubah energi cahaya matahari menjadi listrik\r\nmelalui efek fotovoltaik</span></p>', NULL, 'C', -1.000, 1, 1, '2026-04-23 13:29:10', '2026-04-24 03:52:05'),
(227, 'IMO002', NULL, 16, '<p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:15.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n5.0pt;margin-left:0cm;background:#E8F4FD\"><b><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;color:#1A5276;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV\">Kasus 1: Energi Surya sebagai Sumber Energi Masa Depan</span></b><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\">Matahari memancarkan energi dalam jumlah sangat besar setiap detiknya.\r\nEnergi ini dapat diserap oleh panel surya melalui efek fotovoltaik, yaitu\r\nproses di mana foton cahaya matahari menabrak elektron pada material\r\nsemikonduktor (biasanya silikon) pada panel surya sehingga menghasilkan arus\r\nlistrik. Panel surya tidak memerlukan bahan bakar, tidak menghasilkan emisi\r\nsaat beroperasi, dan dapat dipasang di atap rumah maupun lahan terbuka.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Di Indonesia, potensi energi surya sangat besar\r\nkarena letak geografisnya di garis khatulistiwa yang mendapatkan sinar matahari\r\nrata-rata 4-5 jam per hari secara efektif. Namun, pemanfaatannya masih terbatas\r\nakibat biaya awal pemasangan yang tinggi dan keterbatasan teknologi penyimpanan\r\nenergi.</span><p></p><p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Seorang\r\nsiswa ingin menguji apakah panel surya menghasilkan daya listrik lebih besar\r\npada siang hari dibanding pagi hari. Berdasarkan prinsip efek fotovoltaik,\r\nvariabel utama yang harus diukur adalah....</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Intensitas panas matahari dan daya listrik yang dihasilkan</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Intensitas cahaya matahari dan daya listrik yang\r\ndihasilkan<b></b></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Suhu panas matahari dan daya listrik yang dihasilkan</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Kelembapan udara dan daya listrik yang dihasilkan</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Kapasitas baterai dan daya listrik yang dihasilkan</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Intensitas cahaya matahari dan daya listrik yang\r\ndihasilkan<b></b></span></p>', NULL, 'B', -1.100, 1, 1, '2026-04-23 13:41:58', '2026-04-24 03:52:28'),
(228, 'IMO003', NULL, 16, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:15.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n5.0pt;margin-left:0cm;background:#E8F4FD\"><b><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;color:#1A5276;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV\">Kasus 1: Energi Surya sebagai Sumber Energi Masa Depan</span></b><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\">Matahari memancarkan energi dalam jumlah sangat besar setiap detiknya.\r\nEnergi ini dapat diserap oleh panel surya melalui efek fotovoltaik, yaitu\r\nproses di mana foton cahaya matahari menabrak elektron pada material\r\nsemikonduktor (biasanya silikon) pada panel surya sehingga menghasilkan arus\r\nlistrik. Panel surya tidak memerlukan bahan bakar, tidak menghasilkan emisi\r\nsaat beroperasi, dan dapat dipasang di atap rumah maupun lahan terbuka.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Di Indonesia, potensi energi surya sangat besar\r\nkarena letak geografisnya di garis khatulistiwa yang mendapatkan sinar matahari\r\nrata-rata 4-5 jam per hari secara efektif. Namun, pemanfaatannya masih terbatas\r\nakibat biaya awal pemasangan yang tinggi dan keterbatasan teknologi penyimpanan\r\nenergi.</span></p><p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Dalam\r\npernyataan \"Panel surya adalah sumber energi bersih karena tidak\r\nmenghasilkan emisi,\" konsep fisika mana yang paling penting untuk\r\nmendukung pernyataan tersebut?</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Apakah panel surya menggunakan bahan bakar selama beroperasi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Apakah efek fotovoltaik mengeluarkan emisi gas\r\nbuang saat bekerja</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Apakah panel surya membutuhkan air untuk mendinginkan bahannya</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Apakah panel surya mengeluarkan asap saat bekerja</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Apakah material silikon pada panel surya bersifat ramah lingkungan</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Apakah efek fotovoltaik mengeluarkan emisi gas\r\nbuang saat bekerja</span></p>', NULL, 'B', -1.200, 1, 1, '2026-04-23 13:45:00', '2026-04-24 03:52:51'),
(229, 'IMO004', NULL, 16, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:15.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n5.0pt;margin-left:0cm;background:#E8F4FD\"><b><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;color:#1A5276;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV\">Kasus 1: Energi Surya sebagai Sumber Energi Masa Depan</span></b><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\">Matahari memancarkan energi dalam jumlah sangat besar setiap detiknya.\r\nEnergi ini dapat diserap oleh panel surya melalui efek fotovoltaik, yaitu\r\nproses di mana foton cahaya matahari menabrak elektron pada material\r\nsemikonduktor (biasanya silikon) pada panel surya sehingga menghasilkan arus\r\nlistrik. Panel surya tidak memerlukan bahan bakar, tidak menghasilkan emisi\r\nsaat beroperasi, dan dapat dipasang di atap rumah maupun lahan terbuka.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Di Indonesia, potensi energi surya sangat besar\r\nkarena letak geografisnya di garis khatulistiwa yang mendapatkan sinar matahari\r\nrata-rata 4-5 jam per hari secara efektif. Namun, pemanfaatannya masih terbatas\r\nakibat biaya awal pemasangan yang tinggi dan keterbatasan teknologi penyimpanan\r\nenergi.</span></p><p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Jika\r\nsebuah rumah memasang panel surya di atapnya, dampak apa yang paling mungkin\r\nterjadi dalam jangka panjang?</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Konsumsi listrik dari PLN akan berkurang</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Barang elektronik hanya bisa digunakan di siang\r\nhari</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Panel surya akan menghasilkan listrik lebih banyak di musim kemarau</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Rumah tidak lagi membutuhkan listrik dari PLN</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Penggunaan panel surya menyebabkan kenaikan suhu di sekitar rumah</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Konsumsi listrik dari PLN akan berkurang</span></p>', NULL, 'A', -1.300, 1, 1, '2026-04-23 13:48:51', '2026-04-24 03:53:35');
INSERT INTO `soal_ujian` (`soal_id`, `kode_soal`, `ujian_id`, `bank_ujian_id`, `pertanyaan`, `pilihan_a`, `pilihan_b`, `pilihan_c`, `pilihan_d`, `pilihan_e`, `pembahasan`, `foto`, `jawaban_benar`, `tingkat_kesulitan`, `is_bank_soal`, `created_by`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(230, 'IMO005', NULL, 16, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:15.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n5.0pt;margin-left:0cm;background:#E8F4FD\"><b><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;color:#1A5276;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV\">Kasus 1: Energi Surya sebagai Sumber Energi Masa Depan</span></b><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\">Matahari memancarkan energi dalam jumlah sangat besar setiap detiknya.\r\nEnergi ini dapat diserap oleh panel surya melalui efek fotovoltaik, yaitu\r\nproses di mana foton cahaya matahari menabrak elektron pada material\r\nsemikonduktor (biasanya silikon) pada panel surya sehingga menghasilkan arus\r\nlistrik. Panel surya tidak memerlukan bahan bakar, tidak menghasilkan emisi\r\nsaat beroperasi, dan dapat dipasang di atap rumah maupun lahan terbuka.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Di Indonesia, potensi energi surya sangat besar\r\nkarena letak geografisnya di garis khatulistiwa yang mendapatkan sinar matahari\r\nrata-rata 4-5 jam per hari secara efektif. Namun, pemanfaatannya masih terbatas\r\nakibat biaya awal pemasangan yang tinggi dan keterbatasan teknologi penyimpanan\r\nenergi.</span></p><p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Sebuah\r\nsekolah di daerah terpencil yang sering mengalami pemadaman listrik dan ingin\r\nmemanfaatkan energi surya. Langkah pertama yang paling tepat untuk dilakukan\r\nadalah....</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Membeli panel surya yang dapat menyerap cahaya matahari secara maksimal</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Berdiskusi dengan warga daerah untuk membangun panel surya</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Menentukan tempat yang baik untuk membangun panel surya</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Melakukan survei harga panel surya yang bagus</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Mengukur intensitas cahaya matahari rata-rata di\r\nlokasi tersebut</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Mengukur intensitas cahaya matahari rata-rata di\r\nlokasi tersebut</span></p>', NULL, 'E', -1.400, 1, 1, '2026-04-23 13:50:24', '2026-04-24 03:53:57'),
(231, 'IMO006', NULL, 16, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:15.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n5.0pt;margin-left:0cm;background:#E8F4FD\"><b><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;color:#1A5276;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV\">Kasus 2: Energi Angin dan Pemanfaatannya</span></b><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\">Energi angin merupakan salah satu sumber energi terbarukan yang\r\ndimanfaatkan melalui turbin angin. Ketika angin bertiup, energi kinetik angin\r\nmenggerakkan baling-baling turbin yang kemudian memutar generator untuk\r\nmenghasilkan listrik. Kecepatan angin sangat menentukan jumlah energi yang\r\ndapat dihasilkan, karena daya yang dihasilkan turbin angin berbanding lurus\r\ndengan pangkat tiga kecepatan angin.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Di Indonesia, potensi energi angin mencapai 9,5 giga\r\nwatt, namun pemanfaatannya masih sangat kecil. Salah satu kendalanya adalah\r\nkecepatan angin pada sebagian besar wilayah Indonesia yang relatif rendah dan\r\ntidak stabil dibandingkan negara-negara di wilayah Eropa dan Amerika.</span></p><p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Berdasarkan\r\nnarasi, jenis energi apakah yang pertama kali dimanfaatkan oleh turbin angin\r\nsebelum diubah menjadi listrik?</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Energi potensial angin</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Energi mekanik angin</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Energi kinetik angin</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Energi panas angin</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Energi gerak angin</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Energi kinetik angin</span></p>', NULL, 'C', -1.500, 1, 116, '2026-04-23 20:17:41', '2026-04-24 03:54:16'),
(232, 'IMO007', NULL, 16, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:15.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n5.0pt;margin-left:0cm;background:#E8F4FD\"><b><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;color:#1A5276;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV\">Kasus 2: Energi Angin dan Pemanfaatannya</span></b><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\">Energi angin merupakan salah satu sumber energi terbarukan yang\r\ndimanfaatkan melalui turbin angin. Ketika angin bertiup, energi kinetik angin\r\nmenggerakkan baling-baling turbin yang kemudian memutar generator untuk\r\nmenghasilkan listrik. Kecepatan angin sangat menentukan jumlah energi yang\r\ndapat dihasilkan, karena daya yang dihasilkan turbin angin berbanding lurus\r\ndengan pangkat tiga kecepatan angin.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Di Indonesia, potensi energi angin mencapai 9,5 giga\r\nwatt, namun pemanfaatannya masih sangat kecil. Salah satu kendalanya adalah\r\nkecepatan angin pada sebagian besar wilayah Indonesia yang relatif rendah dan\r\ntidak stabil dibandingkan negara-negara di wilayah Eropa dan Amerika.</span></p><p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Seorang\r\ninsinyur ingin menguji apakah lokasi di Bandung lebih baik dari lokasi di\r\nSukabumi untuk pemasangan turbin angin. Berdasarkan konsep daya yang dihasilkan\r\nturbin, informasi utama apa yang harus dikumpulkan?</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Data ketinggian tempat di kedua lokasi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Data kecepatan angin di kedua lokasi</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;color:black;mso-ansi-language:EN-ID;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Data cuaca di kedua lokasi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"NO-BOK\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:NO-BOK;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Data intensitas angin di kedua lokasi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"NO-BOK\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:NO-BOK;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Data potensi energi di kedua lokasi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Data kecepatan angin di kedua lokasi</span></p>', NULL, 'B', -1.600, 1, 116, '2026-04-23 20:20:22', '2026-04-24 03:54:35'),
(233, 'IMO008', NULL, 16, '<p><span lang=\"NO-BOK\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:NO-BOK;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Seorang\r\nsiswa berpendapat bahwa \"turbin angin tidak cocok dipasang di daerah\r\nperkotaan.\" Konsep fisika mana yang paling mendukung argumen tersebut?</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"NO-BOK\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:NO-BOK;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Turbin angin menghasilkan kebisingan yang mengganggu warga kota</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"NO-BOK\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:NO-BOK;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Gedung-gedung tinggi menghalangi kecepatan angin\r\nyang bergerak</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"NO-BOK\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:NO-BOK;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Turbin angin membutuhkan lahan yang sangat luas sehingga tidak cukup di\r\nkota</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Turbin angin hanya bisa bekerja di dekat laut karena hembusan angin yang\r\nstabil</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Biaya perawatan turbin angin di kota lebih mahal</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"NO-BOK\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:NO-BOK;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Gedung-gedung tinggi menghalangi kecepatan angin\r\nyang bergerak</span></p>', NULL, 'B', -1.700, 1, 1, '2026-04-23 20:28:24', '2026-04-24 03:54:56'),
(234, 'IMO009', NULL, 16, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:15.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n5.0pt;margin-left:0cm;background:#E8F4FD\"><b><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;color:#1A5276;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV\">Kasus 2: Energi Angin dan Pemanfaatannya</span></b><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\">Energi angin merupakan salah satu sumber energi terbarukan yang\r\ndimanfaatkan melalui turbin angin. Ketika angin bertiup, energi kinetik angin\r\nmenggerakkan baling-baling turbin yang kemudian memutar generator untuk\r\nmenghasilkan listrik. Kecepatan angin sangat menentukan jumlah energi yang\r\ndapat dihasilkan, karena daya yang dihasilkan turbin angin berbanding lurus\r\ndengan pangkat tiga kecepatan angin.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Di Indonesia, potensi energi angin mencapai 9,5 giga\r\nwatt, namun pemanfaatannya masih sangat kecil. Salah satu kendalanya adalah\r\nkecepatan angin pada sebagian besar wilayah Indonesia yang relatif rendah dan\r\ntidak stabil dibandingkan negara-negara di wilayah Eropa dan Amerika.</span></p><p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Jika\r\nkecepatan angin di suatu lokasi meningkat dua kali lipat, berdasarkan hubungan daya\r\ndan kecepatan angin, berapa kali lipat daya yang dihasilkan turbin angin\r\ntersebut?</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">2 kali lipat</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">4 kali lipat</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">6 kali lipat</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">8 kali lipat</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">16 kali lipat</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">8 kali lipat</span></p>', NULL, 'D', -1.800, 1, 1, '2026-04-23 20:30:51', '2026-04-24 03:55:13'),
(235, 'IMO010', NULL, 16, '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Sebuah\r\ndesa di pesisir pantai ingin memanfaatkan energi angin untuk kebutuhan listrik\r\nrumah. Solusi paling tepat yang dapat diterapkan adalah?</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Membangun kincir angin di pesisir pantai&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Memasang\r\nturbin angin pada masing-masing rumah</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Mengajukan bantuan ke pemerintah pembangunan turbin angin</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Membangun turbin angin skala besar agar energi yang dihasilkan besar</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-ID;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Membangun\r\nturbin angin disertai generator di pesisir pantai</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-ID;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Membangun\r\nturbin angin disertai generator di pesisir pantai</span></p>', NULL, 'E', -1.900, 1, 1, '2026-04-23 20:32:43', '2026-04-24 03:55:32'),
(236, 'IMO011', NULL, 16, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:15.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n5.0pt;margin-left:0cm;background:#E8F4FD\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;color:#1A5276\">Kasus 3: Pembangkit\r\nListrik Tenaga Air (PLTA) dan Dampak Sosialnya</span></b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:6.0pt;\r\nmargin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\">PLTA memanfaatkan energi potensial\r\nair yang tersimpan pada ketinggian tertentu. Air dari bendungan dialirkan\r\nmelalui pipa menuju turbin, sehingga energi potensial berubah menjadi energi\r\nkinetik yang memutar turbin dan generator. Efisiensi PLTA tergolong tinggi,\r\nmencapai 85-90%, jauh di atas PLTU batu bara yang hanya sekitar 35-40%.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:EN-ID;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Namun, pembangunan bendungan untuk PLTA sering\r\nmenimbulkan dampak sosial yang kompleks. Ribuan warga harus direlokasi dari\r\ndaerah yang akan dijadikan bendungan karena akan menenggelamkan daerah tersebut.\r\nSelain itu, bendungan dapat mengubah ekosistem sungai, menghambat migrasi ikan,\r\ndan mengubah pola sedimentasi tanah. Di sisi lain, bendungan juga berfungsi\r\nsebagai pengendali banjir dan sumber irigasi pertanian.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:EN-ID;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Berdasarkan bacaan, mengapa PLTA lebih unggul\r\ndibanding PLTU batu bara dari sisi teknis?</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:EN-ID;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"></span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-ID;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">PLTA\r\nmemiliki efisiensi konversi energi yang jauh lebih tinggi</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;color:black;mso-ansi-language:EN-ID;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">PLTA menggunakan sumber\r\nenergi terbarukan yaitu air</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;color:black;mso-ansi-language:EN-ID;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">PLTA berfungsi sebagai\r\npengendali banjir dan sumber irigasi pertanian</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;color:black;mso-ansi-language:EN-ID;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">PLTA dibangun dengan biaya\r\nyang lebih murah</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">PLTA tidak menghasilkan emisi gas saat dijalankan</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-ID;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">PLTA\r\nmemiliki efisiensi konversi energi yang jauh lebih tinggi</span></p>', NULL, 'A', 0.000, 1, 1, '2026-04-23 20:35:15', '2026-04-23 20:35:15'),
(237, 'IMO012', NULL, 16, '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Pemerintah\r\nIndonesia ingin menguji apakah pembangunan PLTA baru di suatu sungai akan\r\nberdampak negatif terhadap ekosistem perairan. Informasi apa yang paling\r\npenting untuk dikumpulkan terlebih dahulu?</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Jumlah penduduk yang tinggal di sekitar sungai</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Data keanekaragaman hayati, pola migrasi ikan,\r\ndan debit air sungai</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Luas lahan pertanian di sekitar sungai</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Kecepatan arus sungai saat musim kemarau dan musim hujan</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"NO-BOK\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:NO-BOK;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Data banjir yang sering terjadi di sekitar hilir sungai</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Data keanekaragaman hayati, pola migrasi ikan,\r\ndan debit air sungai</span></p>', NULL, 'B', 0.100, 1, 1, '2026-04-23 20:38:10', '2026-04-24 03:56:41'),
(238, 'IMO013', NULL, 16, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:15.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n5.0pt;margin-left:0cm;background:#E8F4FD\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;color:#1A5276\">Kasus 3: Pembangkit\r\nListrik Tenaga Air (PLTA) dan Dampak Sosialnya</span></b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:6.0pt;\r\nmargin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\">PLTA memanfaatkan energi potensial\r\nair yang tersimpan pada ketinggian tertentu. Air dari bendungan dialirkan\r\nmelalui pipa menuju turbin, sehingga energi potensial berubah menjadi energi\r\nkinetik yang memutar turbin dan generator. Efisiensi PLTA tergolong tinggi,\r\nmencapai 85-90%, jauh di atas PLTU batu bara yang hanya sekitar 35-40%.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:EN-ID;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Namun, pembangunan bendungan untuk PLTA sering\r\nmenimbulkan dampak sosial yang kompleks. Ribuan warga harus direlokasi dari\r\ndaerah yang akan dijadikan bendungan karena akan menenggelamkan daerah tersebut.\r\nSelain itu, bendungan dapat mengubah ekosistem sungai, menghambat migrasi ikan,\r\ndan mengubah pola sedimentasi tanah. Di sisi lain, bendungan juga berfungsi\r\nsebagai pengendali banjir dan sumber irigasi pertanian.</span></p><p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Dalam\r\nargumen \"Pembangunan bendungan PLTA lebih merugikan daripada menguntungkan\r\nkarena menyebabkan relokasi warga,\" manakah aspek yang harus\r\ndipertimbangkan agar argumen ini dapat dinilai secara adil?</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:EN-ID;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Mempertimbangkan biaya pembangunan bendungan dan estimasi energi yang dihasilkan</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Membandingkan dampak paling besar antara relokasi\r\nwarga dan perubahan ekosistem dengan kebutuhan listrik dan pengendalian banjir</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Mempertimbangkan jumlah warga yang direlokasi dan kebutuhan listrik yang\r\ndiperlukan</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Membandingkan kebutuhan air yang diperlukan pertanian dan jumlah daerah\r\nyang terendam di hulu sungai&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Membandingkan dampak dari sisi lingkungan dan mempertimbangkan kebutuhan\r\nenergi listrik nasional</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Membandingkan dampak paling besar antara relokasi warga dan perubahan ekosistem dengan kebutuhan listrik dan pengendalian banjir</span></p>', NULL, 'B', 0.200, 1, 1, '2026-04-23 20:49:27', '2026-04-24 03:57:00'),
(239, 'IMO014', NULL, 16, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:15.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n5.0pt;margin-left:0cm;background:#E8F4FD\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;color:#1A5276\">Kasus 3: Pembangkit\r\nListrik Tenaga Air (PLTA) dan Dampak Sosialnya</span></b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:6.0pt;\r\nmargin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\">PLTA memanfaatkan energi potensial\r\nair yang tersimpan pada ketinggian tertentu. Air dari bendungan dialirkan\r\nmelalui pipa menuju turbin, sehingga energi potensial berubah menjadi energi\r\nkinetik yang memutar turbin dan generator. Efisiensi PLTA tergolong tinggi,\r\nmencapai 85-90%, jauh di atas PLTU batu bara yang hanya sekitar 35-40%.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:EN-ID;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Namun, pembangunan bendungan untuk PLTA sering\r\nmenimbulkan dampak sosial yang kompleks. Ribuan warga harus direlokasi dari\r\ndaerah yang akan dijadikan bendungan karena akan menenggelamkan daerah tersebut.\r\nSelain itu, bendungan dapat mengubah ekosistem sungai, menghambat migrasi ikan,\r\ndan mengubah pola sedimentasi tanah. Di sisi lain, bendungan juga berfungsi\r\nsebagai pengendali banjir dan sumber irigasi pertanian.</span></p><p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Jika\r\ncurah hujan di suatu daerah menurun drastis akibat perubahan iklim, dampak apa\r\nyang paling mungkin terjadi pada PLTA di daerah tersebut?</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:EN-ID;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">PLTA tidak akan menghasilkan listrik karena air sungai surut&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Debit air sungai akan melemah sehingga produksi\r\nlistrik PLTA menurun</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Volume air sungai berkurang sehingga produksi listrik PLTA menurun</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Efisiensi turbin PLTA akan berkuang karena debit air sungai melemah</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Turbin PLTA tidak akan berputar karena kecepatan air sungai tidak cukup kuat&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Debit air sungai akan melemah sehingga produksi\r\nlistrik PLTA menurun</span></p>', NULL, 'B', 0.300, 1, 1, '2026-04-23 20:51:14', '2026-04-24 03:57:15'),
(240, 'IMO015', NULL, 16, '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Suatu\r\ndaerah pegunungan memiliki sungai dengan debit air besar namun penduduknya\r\nsedikit dan tersebar. Solusi pembangkit energi terbarukan apa yang paling tepat\r\nditerapkan?</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Mengajukan pembangunan PLTA skala besar ke pemerintah karena potensi\r\ndebit air yang besar&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p>Membuat donasi untuk pembangunan PLTA</p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Membangun PLTA skala kecil pada beberapa lokasi aliran\r\nsungai yang dekat dengan penduduk&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Melakukan diskusi dengan penduduk terkait lokasi pembangunan PLTA&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Membangun bendungan&nbsp; manual dan\r\nsambil menunggu tindakan pemerintah</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Membangun PLTA skala kecil pada beberapa lokasi aliran sungai yang dekat dengan penduduk&nbsp;</span></p>', NULL, 'C', 0.400, 1, 1, '2026-04-23 20:52:51', '2026-04-24 03:57:40');
INSERT INTO `soal_ujian` (`soal_id`, `kode_soal`, `ujian_id`, `bank_ujian_id`, `pertanyaan`, `pilihan_a`, `pilihan_b`, `pilihan_c`, `pilihan_d`, `pilihan_e`, `pembahasan`, `foto`, `jawaban_benar`, `tingkat_kesulitan`, `is_bank_soal`, `created_by`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(241, 'IMO016', NULL, 16, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:15.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n5.0pt;margin-left:0cm;background:#E8F4FD\"><b><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;color:#1A5276;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV\">Kasus 4: Biogas sebagai Energi Terbarukan Berbasis Limbah</span></b><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:6.0pt;\r\nmargin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\">Biogas merupakan energi terbarukan yang dihasilkan dari proses fermentasi\r\nanaerobik (tanpa oksigen) bahan organik seperti kotoran hewan, sisa makanan,\r\ndan limbah pertanian. Proses ini menghasilkan gas metana (CH<sub>4</sub>) yang dapat digunakan\r\nsebagai bahan bakar untuk memasak, memanaskan ruangan, atau menghasilkan\r\nlistrik melalui generator biogas.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Biogas memiliki keunggulan ganda selain\r\nmenghasilkan energi, proses fermentasinya juga mengurangi limbah organik dan\r\nmenghasilkan pupuk yang kaya nutrisi bagi tanaman. Di daerah pedesaan, biogas\r\ndari kotoran sapi sudah banyak dimanfaatkan oleh peternak skala kecil. Satu\r\nekor sapi dewasa dapat menghasilkan kotoran yang cukup untuk memproduksi\r\nsekitar 1,5-2 m<sup>3</sup></span><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;\r\nmso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">&nbsp;biogas per hari.</span></p><p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;\r\nmso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Berdasarkan\r\nbacaan, apa yang membuat biogas disebut sebagai energi terbarukan dengan\r\n\"keunggulan ganda\"?</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Biogas lebih murah dan lebih mudah diproduksi dibanding energi lainnya</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Biogas menghasilkan energi dan menghasilkan pupuk tanaman</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Biogas menghasilkan energi dan tidak mengeluarkan emisi&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Biogas dapat diproduksi oleh satu ekor sapi dan hemat energi&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Biogas menghasilkan energi dan mengurangi limbah\r\norganik</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Biogas menghasilkan energi dan mengurangi limbah organik</span></p>', NULL, 'E', -0.100, 1, 1, '2026-04-23 20:54:56', '2026-04-24 03:58:08'),
(242, 'IMO017', NULL, 16, '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Seorang\r\npeternak ingin menguji apakah biogas dari kotoran sapinya cukup untuk memenuhi\r\nkebutuhan memasak keluarganya setiap hari. Informasi apa yang paling\r\ndibutuhkan?</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Kotoran sapi yang dihasilkan dan produksi biogas per ekor sapi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Kebutuhan energi memasak per hari dan produksi\r\nbiogas per ekor sapi<b></b></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Jumlah sapi yang dimiliki dan kotoran sapi yang dihasilkan&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Jumlah\r\nsapi yang dimiliki dan produksi biogas per ekor sapi&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Kebutuhan energi memasak per hari dan jumlah sapi yang dimiliki&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Kebutuhan energi memasak per hari dan produksi biogas per ekor sapi</span></p>', NULL, 'B', -0.200, 1, 1, '2026-04-23 20:56:36', '2026-04-24 03:58:40'),
(243, 'IMO018', NULL, 16, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:15.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n5.0pt;margin-left:0cm;background:#E8F4FD\"><b><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;color:#1A5276;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV\">Kasus 4: Biogas sebagai Energi Terbarukan Berbasis Limbah</span></b><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:6.0pt;\r\nmargin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\">Biogas merupakan energi terbarukan yang dihasilkan dari proses fermentasi\r\nanaerobik (tanpa oksigen) bahan organik seperti kotoran hewan, sisa makanan,\r\ndan limbah pertanian. Proses ini menghasilkan gas metana (CH<sub>4</sub>) yang dapat digunakan\r\nsebagai bahan bakar untuk memasak, memanaskan ruangan, atau menghasilkan\r\nlistrik melalui generator biogas.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Biogas memiliki keunggulan ganda selain\r\nmenghasilkan energi, proses fermentasinya juga mengurangi limbah organik dan\r\nmenghasilkan pupuk yang kaya nutrisi bagi tanaman. Di daerah pedesaan, biogas\r\ndari kotoran sapi sudah banyak dimanfaatkan oleh peternak skala kecil. Satu\r\nekor sapi dewasa dapat menghasilkan kotoran yang cukup untuk memproduksi\r\nsekitar 1,5-2 m<sup>3</sup>&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;\r\nmso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">biogas per hari.</span></p><p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;\r\nmso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Dalam\r\nargumen \"Biogas lebih ramah lingkungan dibanding LPG karena berasal dari\r\nlimbah organik,\" konsep apa yang harus diuji untuk memvalidasi pernyataan\r\nini?</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Apakah api yang dihasilkan biogas lebih bagus dibanding LPG&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Apakah biogas menghasilkan emisi gas CO<sub>2</sub> lebih\r\nrendah dibanding LPG<b></b></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Apakah harga produksi biogas lebih murah dari LPG&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Apakah biogas dapat disimpan dalam tabung bertekanan seperti LPG&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Apakah pembakaran biogas menghasilkan asap lebih sedikit dibanding LPG&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Apakah biogas menghasilkan emisi gas CO</span><sub style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">2</sub><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;lebih rendah dibanding LPG</span></p>', NULL, 'B', -0.300, 1, 1, '2026-04-23 20:58:34', '2026-04-24 03:59:18'),
(244, 'IMO019', NULL, 16, '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Jika\r\nsebuah desa dengan 50 peternak sapi masing-masing memiliki 5 ekor sapi dan\r\nmengolah kotoran sapi menjadi biogas, dampak apa yang paling mungkin terjadi?</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Seluruh kebutuhan listrik desa akan terpenuhi dari pengolahan biogas</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Limbah organik sedikit berkurang karena tidak semua kotoran sapi dapat diolah&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Harga LPG di desa tersebut akan menurun&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Penggunaan\r\npupuk kimia berkurang karena beralih ke pupuk organik hasil biogas&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"NO-BOK\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:NO-BOK;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Kebutuhan gas memasak peternak terpenuhi dan\r\nlimbah organik berkurang<b></b></span></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Kebutuhan gas memasak peternak terpenuhi dan limbah organik berkurang</span></p>', NULL, 'E', -0.400, 1, 1, '2026-04-23 21:00:21', '2026-04-24 03:59:41'),
(245, 'IMO020', NULL, 16, '<p><span lang=\"NO-BOK\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Sebuah dapur Makan Bergizi Gratis (MBG) memiliki banyak limbah dari hasil memasak.&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Dapur MBG tersebut ingin menekan pengeluaran biaya dari kompor karena harga gas LPG yang meningkat akibat perang Amerika dan Iran.&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"NO-BOK\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Tindakan yang paling tepat dan efisien untuk mengatasi hal tersebut adalah?</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"NO-BOK\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:NO-BOK;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Memilah sampah dan mengubur limbah organik sebagai pupuk tanaman&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Memilah sampah dan memberikan ke hewan ternak limbah organik</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Memilah sampah dan membangun instalasi biogas\r\nuntuk mengolah limbah organik</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Membangun tempat pembuangan sampah mandiri untuk limbah MBG&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Memilah sampah dan membuang sampah tersebut ke TPA sesuai klasifikasi</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Memilah sampah dan membangun instalasi biogas untuk mengolah limbah organik</span></p>', NULL, 'C', -0.500, 1, 1, '2026-04-23 21:03:11', '2026-04-24 04:00:01'),
(246, 'IMO021', NULL, 16, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:15.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n5.0pt;margin-left:0cm;background:#E8F4FD\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;color:#1A5276\">Kasus 5: Tantangan\r\nTransisi Energi dan Sistem Penyimpanan Energi</span></b><span style=\"font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:6.0pt;\r\nmargin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\">Salah satu tantangan terbesar dalam\r\npemanfaatan energi terbarukan adalah sifatnya yang intermiten, yaitu tidak\r\nselalu tersedia secara konsisten. Panel surya hanya menghasilkan listrik saat\r\nada sinar matahari, turbin angin hanya bekerja saat angin bertiup cukup\r\nkencang. Untuk mengatasi hal ini, diperlukan sistem penyimpanan energi (Energy\r\nStorage System/ESS) seperti baterai lithium-ion, pumped hydro storage, atau\r\nhydrogen fuel cell.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:6.0pt;\r\nmargin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\">Pumped hydro storage bekerja dengan\r\ncara memompa air ke reservoir yang lebih tinggi saat energi berlebih, lalu\r\nmelepaskannya kembali melalui turbin saat energi dibutuhkan. </span><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\">Teknologi ini memiliki efisiensi sekitar 70-85% dan mampu menyimpan energi\r\ndalam skala besar. Sementara itu, baterai lithium-ion memiliki respons yang\r\nlebih cepat namun kapasitas penyimpanannya lebih terbatas dan biayanya masih\r\nrelatif tinggi.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Selain masalah teknis, transisi energi juga\r\nmenghadapi tantangan ekonomi dan sosial, seperti resistensi dari industri bahan\r\nbakar fosil, kebutuhan dana awal yang besar, dan perlunya peningkatan kapasitas\r\nsumber daya manusia di bidang energi terbarukan.</span></p><p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Berdasarkan\r\ndata efisiensi dalam bacaan, jika suatu sistem <i>pumped hydro storage </i>menerima\r\ninput energi sebesar 15 Mega Watt per jam, berapa kisaran energi yang dapat\r\ndikeluarkan kembali?</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">1,05 - 1,275 &nbsp;Kilo Watt per jam</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">105 - 127,5 Kilo Watt per jam&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">1.050 - 1.275 Kilo Watt per jam&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">10.500 - 12.750 Kilo Watt per jam<b></b></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">105.000 - 127.500 Kilo Watt per jam&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">10.500 - 12.750 Kilo Watt per jam</span></p>', NULL, 'D', 1.100, 1, 1, '2026-04-23 21:05:23', '2026-04-24 04:01:21'),
(247, 'IMO022', NULL, 16, '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Seorang\r\npeneliti ingin menguji apakah kombinasi panel surya + baterai lithium-ion lebih\r\nefisien dibanding panel surya tanpa sistem penyimpanan untuk kebutuhan listrik\r\nrumah tangga. Rancangan pengujian yang paling tepat adalah?</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Mengukur pasokan listrik yang dihasilkan dari\r\nkedua sistem di semua cuaca<b></b></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Membandingkan harga panel surya dengan baterai dan tanpa baterai&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Mengukur daya maksimum yang dihasilkan dari kedua sistem&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Mengukur pasokan listrik yang dihasilkan dari kedua sistem saat cuaca cerah&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Menghitung biaya instalasi pemasangan kedua sistem&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Mengukur pasokan listrik yang dihasilkan dari kedua sistem di semua cuaca</span></p>', NULL, 'A', 1.200, 1, 1, '2026-04-23 21:09:11', '2026-04-24 04:03:20'),
(248, 'IMO023', NULL, 16, '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Seseorang\r\nberargumen: \"Transisi ke energi terbarukan tidak perlu terburu-buru karena\r\ncadangan batu bara Indonesia masih cukup untuk 65 tahun ke depan.\"\r\nKelemahan mendasar dari argumen ini adalah?</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"NO-BOK\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:NO-BOK;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Argumen mengabaikan perubahan iklim yang terus terjadi setiap tahun&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Argumen mengabaikan dampak lingkungan jangka\r\npanjang dari penggunaan batubara</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Argumen tidak mempertimbangkan harga batu bara yang terus naik di pasar&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Argumen mengabaikan perhitungan kebutuhan ekspor batu bara Indonesia&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Argumen tidak membahas efisiensi PLTU batu bara yang digunakan&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Argumen mengabaikan dampak lingkungan jangka panjang dari penggunaan batubara</span></p>', NULL, 'B', 1.300, 1, 1, '2026-04-23 21:11:53', '2026-04-24 04:03:35'),
(249, 'IMO024', NULL, 16, '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Jika\r\nIndonesia mempercepat transisi energi terbarukan secara besar-besaran dalam 10\r\ntahun ke depan, komplikasi teknis apa yang paling mungkin terjadi pada jaringan\r\nlistrik nasional?</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Jaringan listrik akan menjadi lebih stabil karena energi terbarukan\r\nlebih efisien&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Fluktuasi pasokan pada jaringan listrik jika\r\ntidak didukung sistem penyimpanan beban yang memadai&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Kebutuhan listrik nasional akan meningkat tinggi karena teknologi\r\nkomunikasi yang semakin berkembang</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Seluruh PLTU batu bara dapat langsung dimatikan tanpa dampak negatif&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Harga listrik akan langsung turun signifikan karena pasokan listrik yang melimpah&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Fluktuasi pasokan pada jaringan listrik jika tidak didukung sistem penyimpanan beban yang memadai&nbsp;</span></p>', NULL, 'B', 1.400, 1, 1, '2026-04-23 21:13:42', '2026-04-24 04:03:49'),
(250, 'IMO025', NULL, 16, '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Sebuah\r\ndaerah berencana membangun PLTB tanpa baterai sebagai sumber energi listrik.\r\nSebelum dibangun dilakukan pengecekan kelayakan daerah dengan komponen yang\r\ndigunakan. Sebuah turbin angin memiliki spesifikasi diameter rotor 10 meter,\r\nefisiensi 35%, dan kecepatan angin minimum operasional 4 m/s. Data kecepatan\r\nangin harian daerah tersebut selama seminggu adalah: 6, 3, 5, 2, 7, 4, 3 m/s.\r\nBerdasarkan data tersebut, keputusan paling tepat terkait kelayakan daerah ini\r\nadalah....</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Daerah\r\ntersebut layak karena rata-rata kecepatan angin mingguan di atas 4 m/s</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Daerah\r\ntersebut tidak layak karena turbin hanya beroperasi 4 hari sehingga 3 hari\r\ntidak ada pasokan listrik&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Daerah tersebut layak karena kecepatan angin mingguan stabil dan cukup\r\nuntuk turbin beroperasi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Daerah\r\ntersebut tidak layak karena efisiensi turbin tersebut sangat rendah&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Daerah tersebut layak, namun perlu ditambah\r\nbaterai agar pasokan listrik yang dihasilkan cukup untuk setiap hari<b></b></span></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Daerah tersebut layak, namun perlu ditambah baterai agar pasokan listrik yang dihasilkan cukup untuk setiap hari</span></p>', NULL, 'E', 1.500, 1, 1, '2026-04-23 21:29:14', '2026-04-24 04:04:04'),
(251, 'IMO026', NULL, 16, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:15.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n5.0pt;margin-left:0cm;background:#E8F4FD\"><b><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;color:#1A5276;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV\">Kasus 6: Analisis Kebijakan Energi dan Perjanjian Paris</span></b><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:6.0pt;\r\nmargin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\">Indonesia telah menandatangani Perjanjian Paris (Paris Agreement) dan\r\nberkomitmen mengurangi emisi gas rumah kaca sebesar 29% secara mandiri dan 41%\r\ndengan dukungan internasional pada tahun 2030. Untuk mencapai target ini,\r\npemerintah mengeluarkan berbagai kebijakan, termasuk feed-in tariff (harga\r\npembelian listrik terbarukan yang dijamin), subsidi panel surya, dan moratorium\r\npembangunan PLTU batu bara baru.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Namun, implementasinya menghadapi berbagai\r\nhambatan. Pertama, investasi awal energi terbarukan masih sangat besar. Kedua,\r\njaringan transmisi listrik di Indonesia belum merata, terutama di luar Jawa.\r\nKetiga, masih ada ketergantungan ekonomi daerah penghasil batu bara terhadap\r\nindustri tersebut. Keempat, kemampuan teknologi domestik dalam memproduksi\r\nkomponen energi terbarukan masih terbatas sehingga sebagian besar komponen\r\nmasih diimpor.</span></p><p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Berdasarkan\r\nbacaan, mengapa kebijakan moratorium PLTU batu bara baru saja tidak cukup untuk\r\nmencapai target pengurangan emisi 29% pada tahun 2030?</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Moratorium hanya berlaku di Pulau Jawa dan tidak mencakup daerah lain&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Moratorium hanya mencegah penambahan PLTU baru\r\ntapi tidak mengurangi emisi dari PLTU yang sudah beroperasi<b></b></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Terdapat mafia di pemerintahan yang bekerja sama dengan perusahaan PLTU\r\nsehingga moratorium hanya formalitas&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Moratorium tidak didukung oleh regulasi hukum yang kuat&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Kebutuhan energi dari PLTU batu bara di Indonesia menjadi yang terbesar\r\nsehingga sulit beralih ke energi terbarukan</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Moratorium hanya mencegah penambahan PLTU baru tapi tidak mengurangi emisi dari PLTU yang sudah beroperasi</span></p>', NULL, 'B', 1.600, 1, 1, '2026-04-23 21:31:16', '2026-04-24 04:03:04'),
(252, 'IMO027', NULL, 16, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:15.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n5.0pt;margin-left:0cm;background:#E8F4FD\"><b><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;color:#1A5276;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV\">Kasus 6: Analisis Kebijakan Energi dan Perjanjian Paris</span></b><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:6.0pt;\r\nmargin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\">Indonesia telah menandatangani Perjanjian Paris (Paris Agreement) dan\r\nberkomitmen mengurangi emisi gas rumah kaca sebesar 29% secara mandiri dan 41%\r\ndengan dukungan internasional pada tahun 2030. Untuk mencapai target ini,\r\npemerintah mengeluarkan berbagai kebijakan, termasuk feed-in tariff (harga\r\npembelian listrik terbarukan yang dijamin), subsidi panel surya, dan moratorium\r\npembangunan PLTU batu bara baru.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Namun, implementasinya menghadapi berbagai\r\nhambatan. Pertama, investasi awal energi terbarukan masih sangat besar. Kedua,\r\njaringan transmisi listrik di Indonesia belum merata, terutama di luar Jawa.\r\nKetiga, masih ada ketergantungan ekonomi daerah penghasil batu bara terhadap\r\nindustri tersebut. Keempat, kemampuan teknologi domestik dalam memproduksi\r\nkomponen energi terbarukan masih terbatas sehingga sebagian besar komponen\r\nmasih diimpor.</span></p><p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Pemerintah\r\nmengklaim bahwa kebijakan feed-in tariff berhasil meningkatkan investasi energi\r\nterbarukan di Indonesia. Untuk menguji klaim ini secara ilmiah, data apa yang\r\npaling diperlukan?</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Jumlah perusahaan energi terbarukan yang mendaftar ke Kementerian ESDM&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Pendapat para ahli energi tentang efektivitas feed-in tariff&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Jumlah berita positif tentang energi terbarukan di media massa&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Data investasi energi terbarukan sebelum dan\r\nsesudah penerapan feed-in tarif</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Perbandingan harga listrik terbarukan dengan listrik batu bara setelah\r\nkebijakan diterapkan</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Data investasi energi terbarukan sebelum dan sesudah penerapan feed-in tarif</span></p>', NULL, 'D', 1.700, 1, 1, '2026-04-23 21:32:54', '2026-04-24 04:02:45');
INSERT INTO `soal_ujian` (`soal_id`, `kode_soal`, `ujian_id`, `bank_ujian_id`, `pertanyaan`, `pilihan_a`, `pilihan_b`, `pilihan_c`, `pilihan_d`, `pilihan_e`, `pembahasan`, `foto`, `jawaban_benar`, `tingkat_kesulitan`, `is_bank_soal`, `created_by`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(253, 'IMO028', NULL, 16, '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Seorang\r\npejabat daerah penghasil batu bara berargumen: \"Transisi energi terbarukan\r\nakan mematikan ekonomi daerah kami karena ribuan pekerja tambang akan\r\nkehilangan pekerjaan.\" Respons yang paling tepat secara analitis adalah?</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Argumen tersebut sepenuhnya salah karena energi terbarukan sama\r\nmenciptakan lebih banyak lapangan kerja&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Argumen tersebut hanya berlaku jika tidak ada investasi asing di sektor\r\nenergi terbarukan</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Argumen tersebut tidak relevan karena keputusan energi adalah kewenangan\r\npemerintah pusat&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Argumen tersebut benar, namun jika terus dilakukan lingkungan daerahnya\r\nakan rusak</span></p>', '<p>A<span style=\"color: black; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 12pt;\">rgumen tersebut hanya berlaku jika tidak ada investasi asing di sektor\r\nenergi terbarukan</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Argumen tersebut hanya berlaku jika tidak ada investasi asing di sektor energi terbarukan</span></p>', NULL, 'B', 1.800, 1, 1, '2026-04-23 21:34:13', '2026-04-24 04:02:28'),
(254, 'IMO029', NULL, 16, '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Jika\r\nharga panel surya global terus turun 10% per tahun selama 5 tahun ke depan,\r\nsementara harga batu bara tetap stabil, dampak ekonomi apa yang paling mungkin\r\nterjadi di Indonesia?</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Daya saing energi surya terhadap batu bara akan\r\nmeningkat signifikan</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Indonesia akan segera menghentikan seluruh penggunaan batu bara&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Harga listrik untuk konsumen akan langsung turun 50% dalam 5 tahun&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Penghasilan perusahaan batu bara Indonesia akan menurun</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Pemerintah tidak perlu lagi mengeluarkan kebijakan insentif energi terbarukan&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Daya saing energi surya terhadap batu bara akan meningkat signifikan</span></p>', NULL, 'A', 1.900, 1, 1, '2026-04-23 21:37:10', '2026-04-24 04:02:04'),
(255, 'IMO030', NULL, 16, '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Indonesia\r\ningin memaksimalkan pengurangan emisi sekaligus menjaga ketahanan energi\r\nnasional dalam 10 tahun ke depan dengan anggaran yang terbatas. Strategi\r\nkebijakan mana yang paling tepat?</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Fokus hanya pada pengembangan PLTS karena biayanya paling murah&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Memprioritaskan pembangunan pembangkit listrik\r\nenergi terbarukan di daerah dengan potensi tinggi<b></b></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Mengembangkan\r\nSDM unggul di bidang teknologi energi terbarukan</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Mengeluarkan tarif 0% untuk menarik investor untuk pengembangan energi\r\nterbarukan</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Memberhentikan\r\nsemua operasional PLTU dan beralih ke energi terbarukan&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Memprioritaskan pembangunan pembangkit listrik energi terbarukan di daerah dengan potensi tinggi</span></p>', NULL, 'B', 2.000, 1, 1, '2026-04-23 21:38:26', '2026-04-24 04:01:42'),
(256, 'IMO030', 10, NULL, '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Indonesia\r\ningin memaksimalkan pengurangan emisi sekaligus menjaga ketahanan energi\r\nnasional dalam 10 tahun ke depan dengan anggaran yang terbatas. Strategi\r\nkebijakan mana yang paling tepat?</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Fokus hanya pada pengembangan PLTS karena biayanya paling murah&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Memprioritaskan pembangunan pembangkit listrik\r\nenergi terbarukan di daerah dengan potensi tinggi<b></b></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Mengembangkan\r\nSDM unggul di bidang teknologi energi terbarukan</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Mengeluarkan tarif 0% untuk menarik investor untuk pengembangan energi\r\nterbarukan</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Memberhentikan\r\nsemua operasional PLTU dan beralih ke energi terbarukan&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Memprioritaskan pembangunan pembangkit listrik energi terbarukan di daerah dengan potensi tinggi</span></p>', NULL, 'B', 0.000, 0, 1, '2026-04-24 03:37:37', '2026-04-24 03:37:37'),
(257, 'IMO029', 10, NULL, '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Jika\r\nharga panel surya global terus turun 10% per tahun selama 5 tahun ke depan,\r\nsementara harga batu bara tetap stabil, dampak ekonomi apa yang paling mungkin\r\nterjadi di Indonesia?</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Daya saing energi surya terhadap batu bara akan\r\nmeningkat signifikan</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Indonesia akan segera menghentikan seluruh penggunaan batu bara&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Harga listrik untuk konsumen akan langsung turun 50% dalam 5 tahun&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Penghasilan perusahaan batu bara Indonesia akan menurun</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Pemerintah tidak perlu lagi mengeluarkan kebijakan insentif energi terbarukan&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Daya saing energi surya terhadap batu bara akan meningkat signifikan</span></p>', NULL, 'A', 0.000, 0, 1, '2026-04-24 03:37:37', '2026-04-24 03:37:37'),
(258, 'IMO028', 10, NULL, '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Seorang\r\npejabat daerah penghasil batu bara berargumen: \"Transisi energi terbarukan\r\nakan mematikan ekonomi daerah kami karena ribuan pekerja tambang akan\r\nkehilangan pekerjaan.\" Respons yang paling tepat secara analitis adalah?</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Argumen tersebut sepenuhnya salah karena energi terbarukan sama\r\nmenciptakan lebih banyak lapangan kerja&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Argumen tersebut hanya berlaku jika tidak ada investasi asing di sektor\r\nenergi terbarukan</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Argumen tersebut tidak relevan karena keputusan energi adalah kewenangan\r\npemerintah pusat&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Argumen tersebut benar, namun jika terus dilakukan lingkungan daerahnya\r\nakan rusak</span></p>', '<p>A<span style=\"color: black; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 12pt;\">rgumen tersebut hanya berlaku jika tidak ada investasi asing di sektor\r\nenergi terbarukan</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Argumen tersebut hanya berlaku jika tidak ada investasi asing di sektor energi terbarukan</span></p>', NULL, 'B', 0.000, 0, 1, '2026-04-24 03:37:37', '2026-04-24 03:37:37'),
(259, 'IMO027', 10, NULL, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:15.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n5.0pt;margin-left:0cm;background:#E8F4FD\"><b><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;color:#1A5276;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV\">Kasus 6: Analisis Kebijakan Energi dan Perjanjian Paris</span></b><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:6.0pt;\r\nmargin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\">Indonesia telah menandatangani Perjanjian Paris (Paris Agreement) dan\r\nberkomitmen mengurangi emisi gas rumah kaca sebesar 29% secara mandiri dan 41%\r\ndengan dukungan internasional pada tahun 2030. Untuk mencapai target ini,\r\npemerintah mengeluarkan berbagai kebijakan, termasuk feed-in tariff (harga\r\npembelian listrik terbarukan yang dijamin), subsidi panel surya, dan moratorium\r\npembangunan PLTU batu bara baru.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Namun, implementasinya menghadapi berbagai\r\nhambatan. Pertama, investasi awal energi terbarukan masih sangat besar. Kedua,\r\njaringan transmisi listrik di Indonesia belum merata, terutama di luar Jawa.\r\nKetiga, masih ada ketergantungan ekonomi daerah penghasil batu bara terhadap\r\nindustri tersebut. Keempat, kemampuan teknologi domestik dalam memproduksi\r\nkomponen energi terbarukan masih terbatas sehingga sebagian besar komponen\r\nmasih diimpor.</span></p><p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Pemerintah\r\nmengklaim bahwa kebijakan feed-in tariff berhasil meningkatkan investasi energi\r\nterbarukan di Indonesia. Untuk menguji klaim ini secara ilmiah, data apa yang\r\npaling diperlukan?</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Jumlah perusahaan energi terbarukan yang mendaftar ke Kementerian ESDM&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Pendapat para ahli energi tentang efektivitas feed-in tariff&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Jumlah berita positif tentang energi terbarukan di media massa&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Data investasi energi terbarukan sebelum dan\r\nsesudah penerapan feed-in tarif</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Perbandingan harga listrik terbarukan dengan listrik batu bara setelah\r\nkebijakan diterapkan</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Data investasi energi terbarukan sebelum dan sesudah penerapan feed-in tarif</span></p>', NULL, 'D', 0.000, 0, 1, '2026-04-24 03:37:37', '2026-04-24 03:37:37'),
(260, 'IMO026', 10, NULL, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:15.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n5.0pt;margin-left:0cm;background:#E8F4FD\"><b><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;color:#1A5276;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV\">Kasus 6: Analisis Kebijakan Energi dan Perjanjian Paris</span></b><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:6.0pt;\r\nmargin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\">Indonesia telah menandatangani Perjanjian Paris (Paris Agreement) dan\r\nberkomitmen mengurangi emisi gas rumah kaca sebesar 29% secara mandiri dan 41%\r\ndengan dukungan internasional pada tahun 2030. Untuk mencapai target ini,\r\npemerintah mengeluarkan berbagai kebijakan, termasuk feed-in tariff (harga\r\npembelian listrik terbarukan yang dijamin), subsidi panel surya, dan moratorium\r\npembangunan PLTU batu bara baru.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Namun, implementasinya menghadapi berbagai\r\nhambatan. Pertama, investasi awal energi terbarukan masih sangat besar. Kedua,\r\njaringan transmisi listrik di Indonesia belum merata, terutama di luar Jawa.\r\nKetiga, masih ada ketergantungan ekonomi daerah penghasil batu bara terhadap\r\nindustri tersebut. Keempat, kemampuan teknologi domestik dalam memproduksi\r\nkomponen energi terbarukan masih terbatas sehingga sebagian besar komponen\r\nmasih diimpor.</span></p><p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Berdasarkan\r\nbacaan, mengapa kebijakan moratorium PLTU batu bara baru saja tidak cukup untuk\r\nmencapai target pengurangan emisi 29% pada tahun 2030?</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Moratorium hanya berlaku di Pulau Jawa dan tidak mencakup daerah lain&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Moratorium hanya mencegah penambahan PLTU baru\r\ntapi tidak mengurangi emisi dari PLTU yang sudah beroperasi<b></b></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Terdapat mafia di pemerintahan yang bekerja sama dengan perusahaan PLTU\r\nsehingga moratorium hanya formalitas&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Moratorium tidak didukung oleh regulasi hukum yang kuat&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Kebutuhan energi dari PLTU batu bara di Indonesia menjadi yang terbesar\r\nsehingga sulit beralih ke energi terbarukan</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Moratorium hanya mencegah penambahan PLTU baru tapi tidak mengurangi emisi dari PLTU yang sudah beroperasi</span></p>', NULL, 'B', 0.000, 0, 1, '2026-04-24 03:37:37', '2026-04-24 03:37:37'),
(261, 'IMO025', 10, NULL, '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Sebuah\r\ndaerah berencana membangun PLTB tanpa baterai sebagai sumber energi listrik.\r\nSebelum dibangun dilakukan pengecekan kelayakan daerah dengan komponen yang\r\ndigunakan. Sebuah turbin angin memiliki spesifikasi diameter rotor 10 meter,\r\nefisiensi 35%, dan kecepatan angin minimum operasional 4 m/s. Data kecepatan\r\nangin harian daerah tersebut selama seminggu adalah: 6, 3, 5, 2, 7, 4, 3 m/s.\r\nBerdasarkan data tersebut, keputusan paling tepat terkait kelayakan daerah ini\r\nadalah....</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Daerah\r\ntersebut layak karena rata-rata kecepatan angin mingguan di atas 4 m/s</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Daerah\r\ntersebut tidak layak karena turbin hanya beroperasi 4 hari sehingga 3 hari\r\ntidak ada pasokan listrik&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Daerah tersebut layak karena kecepatan angin mingguan stabil dan cukup\r\nuntuk turbin beroperasi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Daerah\r\ntersebut tidak layak karena efisiensi turbin tersebut sangat rendah&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Daerah tersebut layak, namun perlu ditambah\r\nbaterai agar pasokan listrik yang dihasilkan cukup untuk setiap hari<b></b></span></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Daerah tersebut layak, namun perlu ditambah baterai agar pasokan listrik yang dihasilkan cukup untuk setiap hari</span></p>', NULL, 'E', 0.000, 0, 1, '2026-04-24 03:37:37', '2026-04-24 03:37:37'),
(262, 'IMO024', 10, NULL, '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Jika\r\nIndonesia mempercepat transisi energi terbarukan secara besar-besaran dalam 10\r\ntahun ke depan, komplikasi teknis apa yang paling mungkin terjadi pada jaringan\r\nlistrik nasional?</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Jaringan listrik akan menjadi lebih stabil karena energi terbarukan\r\nlebih efisien&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Fluktuasi pasokan pada jaringan listrik jika\r\ntidak didukung sistem penyimpanan beban yang memadai&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Kebutuhan listrik nasional akan meningkat tinggi karena teknologi\r\nkomunikasi yang semakin berkembang</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Seluruh PLTU batu bara dapat langsung dimatikan tanpa dampak negatif&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Harga listrik akan langsung turun signifikan karena pasokan listrik yang melimpah&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Fluktuasi pasokan pada jaringan listrik jika tidak didukung sistem penyimpanan beban yang memadai&nbsp;</span></p>', NULL, 'B', 0.000, 0, 1, '2026-04-24 03:37:37', '2026-04-24 03:37:37'),
(263, 'IMO023', 10, NULL, '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Seseorang\r\nberargumen: \"Transisi ke energi terbarukan tidak perlu terburu-buru karena\r\ncadangan batu bara Indonesia masih cukup untuk 65 tahun ke depan.\"\r\nKelemahan mendasar dari argumen ini adalah?</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"NO-BOK\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:NO-BOK;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Argumen mengabaikan perubahan iklim yang terus terjadi setiap tahun&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Argumen mengabaikan dampak lingkungan jangka\r\npanjang dari penggunaan batubara</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Argumen tidak mempertimbangkan harga batu bara yang terus naik di pasar&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Argumen mengabaikan perhitungan kebutuhan ekspor batu bara Indonesia&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Argumen tidak membahas efisiensi PLTU batu bara yang digunakan&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Argumen mengabaikan dampak lingkungan jangka panjang dari penggunaan batubara</span></p>', NULL, 'B', 0.000, 0, 1, '2026-04-24 03:37:37', '2026-04-24 03:37:37'),
(264, 'IMO022', 10, NULL, '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Seorang\r\npeneliti ingin menguji apakah kombinasi panel surya + baterai lithium-ion lebih\r\nefisien dibanding panel surya tanpa sistem penyimpanan untuk kebutuhan listrik\r\nrumah tangga. Rancangan pengujian yang paling tepat adalah?</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Mengukur pasokan listrik yang dihasilkan dari\r\nkedua sistem di semua cuaca<b></b></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Membandingkan harga panel surya dengan baterai dan tanpa baterai&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Mengukur daya maksimum yang dihasilkan dari kedua sistem&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Mengukur pasokan listrik yang dihasilkan dari kedua sistem saat cuaca cerah&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Menghitung biaya instalasi pemasangan kedua sistem&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Mengukur pasokan listrik yang dihasilkan dari kedua sistem di semua cuaca</span></p>', NULL, 'A', 0.000, 0, 1, '2026-04-24 03:37:37', '2026-04-24 03:37:37'),
(265, 'IMO021', 10, NULL, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:15.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n5.0pt;margin-left:0cm;background:#E8F4FD\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;color:#1A5276\">Kasus 5: Tantangan\r\nTransisi Energi dan Sistem Penyimpanan Energi</span></b><span style=\"font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:6.0pt;\r\nmargin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\">Salah satu tantangan terbesar dalam\r\npemanfaatan energi terbarukan adalah sifatnya yang intermiten, yaitu tidak\r\nselalu tersedia secara konsisten. Panel surya hanya menghasilkan listrik saat\r\nada sinar matahari, turbin angin hanya bekerja saat angin bertiup cukup\r\nkencang. Untuk mengatasi hal ini, diperlukan sistem penyimpanan energi (Energy\r\nStorage System/ESS) seperti baterai lithium-ion, pumped hydro storage, atau\r\nhydrogen fuel cell.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:6.0pt;\r\nmargin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\">Pumped hydro storage bekerja dengan\r\ncara memompa air ke reservoir yang lebih tinggi saat energi berlebih, lalu\r\nmelepaskannya kembali melalui turbin saat energi dibutuhkan. </span><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\">Teknologi ini memiliki efisiensi sekitar 70-85% dan mampu menyimpan energi\r\ndalam skala besar. Sementara itu, baterai lithium-ion memiliki respons yang\r\nlebih cepat namun kapasitas penyimpanannya lebih terbatas dan biayanya masih\r\nrelatif tinggi.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Selain masalah teknis, transisi energi juga\r\nmenghadapi tantangan ekonomi dan sosial, seperti resistensi dari industri bahan\r\nbakar fosil, kebutuhan dana awal yang besar, dan perlunya peningkatan kapasitas\r\nsumber daya manusia di bidang energi terbarukan.</span></p><p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Berdasarkan\r\ndata efisiensi dalam bacaan, jika suatu sistem <i>pumped hydro storage </i>menerima\r\ninput energi sebesar 15 Mega Watt per jam, berapa kisaran energi yang dapat\r\ndikeluarkan kembali?</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">1,05 - 1,275 &nbsp;Kilo Watt per jam</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">105 - 127,5 Kilo Watt per jam&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">1.050 - 1.275 Kilo Watt per jam&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">10.500 - 12.750 Kilo Watt per jam<b></b></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">105.000 - 127.500 Kilo Watt per jam&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">10.500 - 12.750 Kilo Watt per jam</span></p>', NULL, 'D', 0.000, 0, 1, '2026-04-24 03:37:37', '2026-04-24 03:37:37'),
(266, 'IMO020', 10, NULL, '<p><span lang=\"NO-BOK\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Sebuah dapur Makan Bergizi Gratis (MBG) memiliki banyak limbah dari hasil memasak.&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Dapur MBG tersebut ingin menekan pengeluaran biaya dari kompor karena harga gas LPG yang meningkat akibat perang Amerika dan Iran.&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"NO-BOK\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Tindakan yang paling tepat dan efisien untuk mengatasi hal tersebut adalah?</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"NO-BOK\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:NO-BOK;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Memilah sampah dan mengubur limbah organik sebagai pupuk tanaman&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Memilah sampah dan memberikan ke hewan ternak limbah organik</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Memilah sampah dan membangun instalasi biogas\r\nuntuk mengolah limbah organik</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Membangun tempat pembuangan sampah mandiri untuk limbah MBG&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Memilah sampah dan membuang sampah tersebut ke TPA sesuai klasifikasi</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Memilah sampah dan membangun instalasi biogas untuk mengolah limbah organik</span></p>', NULL, 'C', 0.000, 0, 1, '2026-04-24 03:37:37', '2026-04-24 03:37:37'),
(267, 'IMO019', 10, NULL, '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Jika\r\nsebuah desa dengan 50 peternak sapi masing-masing memiliki 5 ekor sapi dan\r\nmengolah kotoran sapi menjadi biogas, dampak apa yang paling mungkin terjadi?</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Seluruh kebutuhan listrik desa akan terpenuhi dari pengolahan biogas</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Limbah organik sedikit berkurang karena tidak semua kotoran sapi dapat diolah&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Harga LPG di desa tersebut akan menurun&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Penggunaan\r\npupuk kimia berkurang karena beralih ke pupuk organik hasil biogas&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"NO-BOK\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:NO-BOK;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Kebutuhan gas memasak peternak terpenuhi dan\r\nlimbah organik berkurang<b></b></span></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Kebutuhan gas memasak peternak terpenuhi dan limbah organik berkurang</span></p>', NULL, 'E', 0.000, 0, 1, '2026-04-24 03:37:37', '2026-04-24 03:37:37');
INSERT INTO `soal_ujian` (`soal_id`, `kode_soal`, `ujian_id`, `bank_ujian_id`, `pertanyaan`, `pilihan_a`, `pilihan_b`, `pilihan_c`, `pilihan_d`, `pilihan_e`, `pembahasan`, `foto`, `jawaban_benar`, `tingkat_kesulitan`, `is_bank_soal`, `created_by`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(268, 'IMO018', 10, NULL, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:15.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n5.0pt;margin-left:0cm;background:#E8F4FD\"><b><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;color:#1A5276;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV\">Kasus 4: Biogas sebagai Energi Terbarukan Berbasis Limbah</span></b><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:6.0pt;\r\nmargin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\">Biogas merupakan energi terbarukan yang dihasilkan dari proses fermentasi\r\nanaerobik (tanpa oksigen) bahan organik seperti kotoran hewan, sisa makanan,\r\ndan limbah pertanian. Proses ini menghasilkan gas metana (CH<sub>4</sub>) yang dapat digunakan\r\nsebagai bahan bakar untuk memasak, memanaskan ruangan, atau menghasilkan\r\nlistrik melalui generator biogas.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Biogas memiliki keunggulan ganda selain\r\nmenghasilkan energi, proses fermentasinya juga mengurangi limbah organik dan\r\nmenghasilkan pupuk yang kaya nutrisi bagi tanaman. Di daerah pedesaan, biogas\r\ndari kotoran sapi sudah banyak dimanfaatkan oleh peternak skala kecil. Satu\r\nekor sapi dewasa dapat menghasilkan kotoran yang cukup untuk memproduksi\r\nsekitar 1,5-2 m<sup>3</sup>&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;\r\nmso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">biogas per hari.</span></p><p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;\r\nmso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Dalam\r\nargumen \"Biogas lebih ramah lingkungan dibanding LPG karena berasal dari\r\nlimbah organik,\" konsep apa yang harus diuji untuk memvalidasi pernyataan\r\nini?</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Apakah api yang dihasilkan biogas lebih bagus dibanding LPG&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Apakah biogas menghasilkan emisi gas CO<sub>2</sub> lebih\r\nrendah dibanding LPG<b></b></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Apakah harga produksi biogas lebih murah dari LPG&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Apakah biogas dapat disimpan dalam tabung bertekanan seperti LPG&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Apakah pembakaran biogas menghasilkan asap lebih sedikit dibanding LPG&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Apakah biogas menghasilkan emisi gas CO</span><sub style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">2</sub><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;lebih rendah dibanding LPG</span></p>', NULL, 'B', 0.000, 0, 1, '2026-04-24 03:37:37', '2026-04-24 03:37:37'),
(269, 'IMO017', 10, NULL, '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Seorang\r\npeternak ingin menguji apakah biogas dari kotoran sapinya cukup untuk memenuhi\r\nkebutuhan memasak keluarganya setiap hari. Informasi apa yang paling\r\ndibutuhkan?</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Kotoran sapi yang dihasilkan dan produksi biogas per ekor sapi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Kebutuhan energi memasak per hari dan produksi\r\nbiogas per ekor sapi<b></b></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Jumlah sapi yang dimiliki dan kotoran sapi yang dihasilkan&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Jumlah\r\nsapi yang dimiliki dan produksi biogas per ekor sapi&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Kebutuhan energi memasak per hari dan jumlah sapi yang dimiliki&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Kebutuhan energi memasak per hari dan produksi biogas per ekor sapi</span></p>', NULL, 'B', 0.000, 0, 1, '2026-04-24 03:37:37', '2026-04-24 03:37:37'),
(270, 'IMO016', 10, NULL, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:15.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n5.0pt;margin-left:0cm;background:#E8F4FD\"><b><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;color:#1A5276;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV\">Kasus 4: Biogas sebagai Energi Terbarukan Berbasis Limbah</span></b><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:6.0pt;\r\nmargin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\">Biogas merupakan energi terbarukan yang dihasilkan dari proses fermentasi\r\nanaerobik (tanpa oksigen) bahan organik seperti kotoran hewan, sisa makanan,\r\ndan limbah pertanian. Proses ini menghasilkan gas metana (CH<sub>4</sub>) yang dapat digunakan\r\nsebagai bahan bakar untuk memasak, memanaskan ruangan, atau menghasilkan\r\nlistrik melalui generator biogas.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Biogas memiliki keunggulan ganda selain\r\nmenghasilkan energi, proses fermentasinya juga mengurangi limbah organik dan\r\nmenghasilkan pupuk yang kaya nutrisi bagi tanaman. Di daerah pedesaan, biogas\r\ndari kotoran sapi sudah banyak dimanfaatkan oleh peternak skala kecil. Satu\r\nekor sapi dewasa dapat menghasilkan kotoran yang cukup untuk memproduksi\r\nsekitar 1,5-2 m<sup>3</sup></span><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;\r\nmso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">&nbsp;biogas per hari.</span></p><p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;\r\nmso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Berdasarkan\r\nbacaan, apa yang membuat biogas disebut sebagai energi terbarukan dengan\r\n\"keunggulan ganda\"?</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Biogas lebih murah dan lebih mudah diproduksi dibanding energi lainnya</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Biogas menghasilkan energi dan menghasilkan pupuk tanaman</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Biogas menghasilkan energi dan tidak mengeluarkan emisi&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Biogas dapat diproduksi oleh satu ekor sapi dan hemat energi&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Biogas menghasilkan energi dan mengurangi limbah\r\norganik</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Biogas menghasilkan energi dan mengurangi limbah organik</span></p>', NULL, 'E', 0.000, 0, 1, '2026-04-24 03:37:37', '2026-04-24 03:37:37'),
(271, 'IMO015', 10, NULL, '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Suatu\r\ndaerah pegunungan memiliki sungai dengan debit air besar namun penduduknya\r\nsedikit dan tersebar. Solusi pembangkit energi terbarukan apa yang paling tepat\r\nditerapkan?</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Mengajukan pembangunan PLTA skala besar ke pemerintah karena potensi\r\ndebit air yang besar&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p>Membuat donasi untuk pembangunan PLTA</p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Membangun PLTA skala kecil pada beberapa lokasi aliran\r\nsungai yang dekat dengan penduduk&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Melakukan diskusi dengan penduduk terkait lokasi pembangunan PLTA&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Membangun bendungan&nbsp; manual dan\r\nsambil menunggu tindakan pemerintah</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Membangun PLTA skala kecil pada beberapa lokasi aliran sungai yang dekat dengan penduduk&nbsp;</span></p>', NULL, 'C', 0.000, 0, 1, '2026-04-24 03:37:37', '2026-04-24 03:37:37'),
(272, 'IMO014', 10, NULL, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:15.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n5.0pt;margin-left:0cm;background:#E8F4FD\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;color:#1A5276\">Kasus 3: Pembangkit\r\nListrik Tenaga Air (PLTA) dan Dampak Sosialnya</span></b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:6.0pt;\r\nmargin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\">PLTA memanfaatkan energi potensial\r\nair yang tersimpan pada ketinggian tertentu. Air dari bendungan dialirkan\r\nmelalui pipa menuju turbin, sehingga energi potensial berubah menjadi energi\r\nkinetik yang memutar turbin dan generator. Efisiensi PLTA tergolong tinggi,\r\nmencapai 85-90%, jauh di atas PLTU batu bara yang hanya sekitar 35-40%.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:EN-ID;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Namun, pembangunan bendungan untuk PLTA sering\r\nmenimbulkan dampak sosial yang kompleks. Ribuan warga harus direlokasi dari\r\ndaerah yang akan dijadikan bendungan karena akan menenggelamkan daerah tersebut.\r\nSelain itu, bendungan dapat mengubah ekosistem sungai, menghambat migrasi ikan,\r\ndan mengubah pola sedimentasi tanah. Di sisi lain, bendungan juga berfungsi\r\nsebagai pengendali banjir dan sumber irigasi pertanian.</span></p><p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Jika\r\ncurah hujan di suatu daerah menurun drastis akibat perubahan iklim, dampak apa\r\nyang paling mungkin terjadi pada PLTA di daerah tersebut?</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:EN-ID;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">PLTA tidak akan menghasilkan listrik karena air sungai surut&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Debit air sungai akan melemah sehingga produksi\r\nlistrik PLTA menurun</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Volume air sungai berkurang sehingga produksi listrik PLTA menurun</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Efisiensi turbin PLTA akan berkuang karena debit air sungai melemah</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Turbin PLTA tidak akan berputar karena kecepatan air sungai tidak cukup kuat&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Debit air sungai akan melemah sehingga produksi\r\nlistrik PLTA menurun</span></p>', NULL, 'B', 0.000, 0, 1, '2026-04-24 03:37:37', '2026-04-24 03:37:37'),
(273, 'IMO013', 10, NULL, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:15.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n5.0pt;margin-left:0cm;background:#E8F4FD\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;color:#1A5276\">Kasus 3: Pembangkit\r\nListrik Tenaga Air (PLTA) dan Dampak Sosialnya</span></b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:6.0pt;\r\nmargin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\">PLTA memanfaatkan energi potensial\r\nair yang tersimpan pada ketinggian tertentu. Air dari bendungan dialirkan\r\nmelalui pipa menuju turbin, sehingga energi potensial berubah menjadi energi\r\nkinetik yang memutar turbin dan generator. Efisiensi PLTA tergolong tinggi,\r\nmencapai 85-90%, jauh di atas PLTU batu bara yang hanya sekitar 35-40%.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:EN-ID;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Namun, pembangunan bendungan untuk PLTA sering\r\nmenimbulkan dampak sosial yang kompleks. Ribuan warga harus direlokasi dari\r\ndaerah yang akan dijadikan bendungan karena akan menenggelamkan daerah tersebut.\r\nSelain itu, bendungan dapat mengubah ekosistem sungai, menghambat migrasi ikan,\r\ndan mengubah pola sedimentasi tanah. Di sisi lain, bendungan juga berfungsi\r\nsebagai pengendali banjir dan sumber irigasi pertanian.</span></p><p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Dalam\r\nargumen \"Pembangunan bendungan PLTA lebih merugikan daripada menguntungkan\r\nkarena menyebabkan relokasi warga,\" manakah aspek yang harus\r\ndipertimbangkan agar argumen ini dapat dinilai secara adil?</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:EN-ID;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Mempertimbangkan biaya pembangunan bendungan dan estimasi energi yang dihasilkan</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Membandingkan dampak paling besar antara relokasi\r\nwarga dan perubahan ekosistem dengan kebutuhan listrik dan pengendalian banjir</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Mempertimbangkan jumlah warga yang direlokasi dan kebutuhan listrik yang\r\ndiperlukan</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Membandingkan kebutuhan air yang diperlukan pertanian dan jumlah daerah\r\nyang terendam di hulu sungai&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Membandingkan dampak dari sisi lingkungan dan mempertimbangkan kebutuhan\r\nenergi listrik nasional</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Membandingkan dampak paling besar antara relokasi warga dan perubahan ekosistem dengan kebutuhan listrik dan pengendalian banjir</span></p>', NULL, 'B', 0.000, 0, 1, '2026-04-24 03:37:37', '2026-04-24 03:37:37'),
(274, 'IMO012', 10, NULL, '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Pemerintah\r\nIndonesia ingin menguji apakah pembangunan PLTA baru di suatu sungai akan\r\nberdampak negatif terhadap ekosistem perairan. Informasi apa yang paling\r\npenting untuk dikumpulkan terlebih dahulu?</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Jumlah penduduk yang tinggal di sekitar sungai</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Data keanekaragaman hayati, pola migrasi ikan,\r\ndan debit air sungai</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Luas lahan pertanian di sekitar sungai</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Kecepatan arus sungai saat musim kemarau dan musim hujan</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"NO-BOK\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:NO-BOK;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Data banjir yang sering terjadi di sekitar hilir sungai</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Data keanekaragaman hayati, pola migrasi ikan,\r\ndan debit air sungai</span></p>', NULL, 'B', 0.000, 0, 1, '2026-04-24 03:37:37', '2026-04-24 03:37:37'),
(275, 'IMO011', 10, NULL, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:15.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n5.0pt;margin-left:0cm;background:#E8F4FD\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;color:#1A5276\">Kasus 3: Pembangkit\r\nListrik Tenaga Air (PLTA) dan Dampak Sosialnya</span></b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:6.0pt;\r\nmargin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\">PLTA memanfaatkan energi potensial\r\nair yang tersimpan pada ketinggian tertentu. Air dari bendungan dialirkan\r\nmelalui pipa menuju turbin, sehingga energi potensial berubah menjadi energi\r\nkinetik yang memutar turbin dan generator. Efisiensi PLTA tergolong tinggi,\r\nmencapai 85-90%, jauh di atas PLTU batu bara yang hanya sekitar 35-40%.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:EN-ID;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Namun, pembangunan bendungan untuk PLTA sering\r\nmenimbulkan dampak sosial yang kompleks. Ribuan warga harus direlokasi dari\r\ndaerah yang akan dijadikan bendungan karena akan menenggelamkan daerah tersebut.\r\nSelain itu, bendungan dapat mengubah ekosistem sungai, menghambat migrasi ikan,\r\ndan mengubah pola sedimentasi tanah. Di sisi lain, bendungan juga berfungsi\r\nsebagai pengendali banjir dan sumber irigasi pertanian.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:EN-ID;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Berdasarkan bacaan, mengapa PLTA lebih unggul\r\ndibanding PLTU batu bara dari sisi teknis?</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:EN-ID;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"></span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-ID;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">PLTA\r\nmemiliki efisiensi konversi energi yang jauh lebih tinggi</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;color:black;mso-ansi-language:EN-ID;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">PLTA menggunakan sumber\r\nenergi terbarukan yaitu air</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;color:black;mso-ansi-language:EN-ID;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">PLTA berfungsi sebagai\r\npengendali banjir dan sumber irigasi pertanian</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;color:black;mso-ansi-language:EN-ID;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">PLTA dibangun dengan biaya\r\nyang lebih murah</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">PLTA tidak menghasilkan emisi gas saat dijalankan</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-ID;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">PLTA\r\nmemiliki efisiensi konversi energi yang jauh lebih tinggi</span></p>', NULL, 'A', 0.000, 0, 1, '2026-04-24 03:37:37', '2026-04-24 03:37:37'),
(276, 'IMO010', 10, NULL, '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Sebuah\r\ndesa di pesisir pantai ingin memanfaatkan energi angin untuk kebutuhan listrik\r\nrumah. Solusi paling tepat yang dapat diterapkan adalah?</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Membangun kincir angin di pesisir pantai&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Memasang\r\nturbin angin pada masing-masing rumah</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Mengajukan bantuan ke pemerintah pembangunan turbin angin</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Membangun turbin angin skala besar agar energi yang dihasilkan besar</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-ID;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Membangun\r\nturbin angin disertai generator di pesisir pantai</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;color:black;mso-themecolor:text1;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-ID;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Membangun\r\nturbin angin disertai generator di pesisir pantai</span></p>', NULL, 'E', 0.000, 0, 1, '2026-04-24 03:37:37', '2026-04-24 03:37:37'),
(277, 'IMO009', 10, NULL, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:15.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n5.0pt;margin-left:0cm;background:#E8F4FD\"><b><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;color:#1A5276;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV\">Kasus 2: Energi Angin dan Pemanfaatannya</span></b><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\">Energi angin merupakan salah satu sumber energi terbarukan yang\r\ndimanfaatkan melalui turbin angin. Ketika angin bertiup, energi kinetik angin\r\nmenggerakkan baling-baling turbin yang kemudian memutar generator untuk\r\nmenghasilkan listrik. Kecepatan angin sangat menentukan jumlah energi yang\r\ndapat dihasilkan, karena daya yang dihasilkan turbin angin berbanding lurus\r\ndengan pangkat tiga kecepatan angin.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Di Indonesia, potensi energi angin mencapai 9,5 giga\r\nwatt, namun pemanfaatannya masih sangat kecil. Salah satu kendalanya adalah\r\nkecepatan angin pada sebagian besar wilayah Indonesia yang relatif rendah dan\r\ntidak stabil dibandingkan negara-negara di wilayah Eropa dan Amerika.</span></p><p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Jika\r\nkecepatan angin di suatu lokasi meningkat dua kali lipat, berdasarkan hubungan daya\r\ndan kecepatan angin, berapa kali lipat daya yang dihasilkan turbin angin\r\ntersebut?</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">2 kali lipat</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">4 kali lipat</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">6 kali lipat</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">8 kali lipat</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">16 kali lipat</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">8 kali lipat</span></p>', NULL, 'D', 0.000, 0, 1, '2026-04-24 03:37:37', '2026-04-24 03:37:37'),
(278, 'IMO008', 10, NULL, '<p><span lang=\"NO-BOK\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:NO-BOK;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Seorang\r\nsiswa berpendapat bahwa \"turbin angin tidak cocok dipasang di daerah\r\nperkotaan.\" Konsep fisika mana yang paling mendukung argumen tersebut?</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"NO-BOK\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:NO-BOK;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Turbin angin menghasilkan kebisingan yang mengganggu warga kota</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"NO-BOK\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:NO-BOK;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Gedung-gedung tinggi menghalangi kecepatan angin\r\nyang bergerak</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"NO-BOK\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:NO-BOK;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Turbin angin membutuhkan lahan yang sangat luas sehingga tidak cukup di\r\nkota</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Turbin angin hanya bisa bekerja di dekat laut karena hembusan angin yang\r\nstabil</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Biaya perawatan turbin angin di kota lebih mahal</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"NO-BOK\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:NO-BOK;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Gedung-gedung tinggi menghalangi kecepatan angin\r\nyang bergerak</span></p>', NULL, 'B', 0.000, 0, 1, '2026-04-24 03:37:37', '2026-04-24 03:37:37');
INSERT INTO `soal_ujian` (`soal_id`, `kode_soal`, `ujian_id`, `bank_ujian_id`, `pertanyaan`, `pilihan_a`, `pilihan_b`, `pilihan_c`, `pilihan_d`, `pilihan_e`, `pembahasan`, `foto`, `jawaban_benar`, `tingkat_kesulitan`, `is_bank_soal`, `created_by`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(279, 'IMO007', 10, NULL, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:15.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n5.0pt;margin-left:0cm;background:#E8F4FD\"><b><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;color:#1A5276;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV\">Kasus 2: Energi Angin dan Pemanfaatannya</span></b><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\">Energi angin merupakan salah satu sumber energi terbarukan yang\r\ndimanfaatkan melalui turbin angin. Ketika angin bertiup, energi kinetik angin\r\nmenggerakkan baling-baling turbin yang kemudian memutar generator untuk\r\nmenghasilkan listrik. Kecepatan angin sangat menentukan jumlah energi yang\r\ndapat dihasilkan, karena daya yang dihasilkan turbin angin berbanding lurus\r\ndengan pangkat tiga kecepatan angin.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Di Indonesia, potensi energi angin mencapai 9,5 giga\r\nwatt, namun pemanfaatannya masih sangat kecil. Salah satu kendalanya adalah\r\nkecepatan angin pada sebagian besar wilayah Indonesia yang relatif rendah dan\r\ntidak stabil dibandingkan negara-negara di wilayah Eropa dan Amerika.</span></p><p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Seorang\r\ninsinyur ingin menguji apakah lokasi di Bandung lebih baik dari lokasi di\r\nSukabumi untuk pemasangan turbin angin. Berdasarkan konsep daya yang dihasilkan\r\nturbin, informasi utama apa yang harus dikumpulkan?</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Data ketinggian tempat di kedua lokasi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Data kecepatan angin di kedua lokasi</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;color:black;mso-ansi-language:EN-ID;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Data cuaca di kedua lokasi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"NO-BOK\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:NO-BOK;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Data intensitas angin di kedua lokasi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"NO-BOK\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:NO-BOK;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Data potensi energi di kedua lokasi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Data kecepatan angin di kedua lokasi</span></p>', NULL, 'B', 0.000, 0, 1, '2026-04-24 03:37:37', '2026-04-24 03:37:37'),
(280, 'IMO006', 10, NULL, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:15.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n5.0pt;margin-left:0cm;background:#E8F4FD\"><b><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;color:#1A5276;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV\">Kasus 2: Energi Angin dan Pemanfaatannya</span></b><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\">Energi angin merupakan salah satu sumber energi terbarukan yang\r\ndimanfaatkan melalui turbin angin. Ketika angin bertiup, energi kinetik angin\r\nmenggerakkan baling-baling turbin yang kemudian memutar generator untuk\r\nmenghasilkan listrik. Kecepatan angin sangat menentukan jumlah energi yang\r\ndapat dihasilkan, karena daya yang dihasilkan turbin angin berbanding lurus\r\ndengan pangkat tiga kecepatan angin.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Di Indonesia, potensi energi angin mencapai 9,5 giga\r\nwatt, namun pemanfaatannya masih sangat kecil. Salah satu kendalanya adalah\r\nkecepatan angin pada sebagian besar wilayah Indonesia yang relatif rendah dan\r\ntidak stabil dibandingkan negara-negara di wilayah Eropa dan Amerika.</span></p><p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Berdasarkan\r\nnarasi, jenis energi apakah yang pertama kali dimanfaatkan oleh turbin angin\r\nsebelum diubah menjadi listrik?</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Energi potensial angin</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Energi mekanik angin</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Energi kinetik angin</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Energi panas angin</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Energi gerak angin</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Energi kinetik angin</span></p>', NULL, 'C', 0.000, 0, 1, '2026-04-24 03:37:37', '2026-04-24 03:37:37'),
(281, 'IMO005', 10, NULL, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:15.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n5.0pt;margin-left:0cm;background:#E8F4FD\"><b><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;color:#1A5276;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV\">Kasus 1: Energi Surya sebagai Sumber Energi Masa Depan</span></b><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\">Matahari memancarkan energi dalam jumlah sangat besar setiap detiknya.\r\nEnergi ini dapat diserap oleh panel surya melalui efek fotovoltaik, yaitu\r\nproses di mana foton cahaya matahari menabrak elektron pada material\r\nsemikonduktor (biasanya silikon) pada panel surya sehingga menghasilkan arus\r\nlistrik. Panel surya tidak memerlukan bahan bakar, tidak menghasilkan emisi\r\nsaat beroperasi, dan dapat dipasang di atap rumah maupun lahan terbuka.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Di Indonesia, potensi energi surya sangat besar\r\nkarena letak geografisnya di garis khatulistiwa yang mendapatkan sinar matahari\r\nrata-rata 4-5 jam per hari secara efektif. Namun, pemanfaatannya masih terbatas\r\nakibat biaya awal pemasangan yang tinggi dan keterbatasan teknologi penyimpanan\r\nenergi.</span></p><p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Sebuah\r\nsekolah di daerah terpencil yang sering mengalami pemadaman listrik dan ingin\r\nmemanfaatkan energi surya. Langkah pertama yang paling tepat untuk dilakukan\r\nadalah....</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Membeli panel surya yang dapat menyerap cahaya matahari secara maksimal</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Berdiskusi dengan warga daerah untuk membangun panel surya</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Menentukan tempat yang baik untuk membangun panel surya</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Melakukan survei harga panel surya yang bagus</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Mengukur intensitas cahaya matahari rata-rata di\r\nlokasi tersebut</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Mengukur intensitas cahaya matahari rata-rata di\r\nlokasi tersebut</span></p>', NULL, 'E', 0.000, 0, 1, '2026-04-24 03:37:37', '2026-04-24 03:37:37'),
(282, 'IMO004', 10, NULL, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:15.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n5.0pt;margin-left:0cm;background:#E8F4FD\"><b><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;color:#1A5276;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV\">Kasus 1: Energi Surya sebagai Sumber Energi Masa Depan</span></b><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\">Matahari memancarkan energi dalam jumlah sangat besar setiap detiknya.\r\nEnergi ini dapat diserap oleh panel surya melalui efek fotovoltaik, yaitu\r\nproses di mana foton cahaya matahari menabrak elektron pada material\r\nsemikonduktor (biasanya silikon) pada panel surya sehingga menghasilkan arus\r\nlistrik. Panel surya tidak memerlukan bahan bakar, tidak menghasilkan emisi\r\nsaat beroperasi, dan dapat dipasang di atap rumah maupun lahan terbuka.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Di Indonesia, potensi energi surya sangat besar\r\nkarena letak geografisnya di garis khatulistiwa yang mendapatkan sinar matahari\r\nrata-rata 4-5 jam per hari secara efektif. Namun, pemanfaatannya masih terbatas\r\nakibat biaya awal pemasangan yang tinggi dan keterbatasan teknologi penyimpanan\r\nenergi.</span></p><p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Jika\r\nsebuah rumah memasang panel surya di atapnya, dampak apa yang paling mungkin\r\nterjadi dalam jangka panjang?</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Konsumsi listrik dari PLN akan berkurang</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Barang elektronik hanya bisa digunakan di siang\r\nhari</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Panel surya akan menghasilkan listrik lebih banyak di musim kemarau</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Rumah tidak lagi membutuhkan listrik dari PLN</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Penggunaan panel surya menyebabkan kenaikan suhu di sekitar rumah</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Konsumsi listrik dari PLN akan berkurang</span></p>', NULL, 'A', 0.000, 0, 1, '2026-04-24 03:37:37', '2026-04-24 03:37:37'),
(283, 'IMO003', 10, NULL, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:15.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n5.0pt;margin-left:0cm;background:#E8F4FD\"><b><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;color:#1A5276;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV\">Kasus 1: Energi Surya sebagai Sumber Energi Masa Depan</span></b><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\">Matahari memancarkan energi dalam jumlah sangat besar setiap detiknya.\r\nEnergi ini dapat diserap oleh panel surya melalui efek fotovoltaik, yaitu\r\nproses di mana foton cahaya matahari menabrak elektron pada material\r\nsemikonduktor (biasanya silikon) pada panel surya sehingga menghasilkan arus\r\nlistrik. Panel surya tidak memerlukan bahan bakar, tidak menghasilkan emisi\r\nsaat beroperasi, dan dapat dipasang di atap rumah maupun lahan terbuka.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Di Indonesia, potensi energi surya sangat besar\r\nkarena letak geografisnya di garis khatulistiwa yang mendapatkan sinar matahari\r\nrata-rata 4-5 jam per hari secara efektif. Namun, pemanfaatannya masih terbatas\r\nakibat biaya awal pemasangan yang tinggi dan keterbatasan teknologi penyimpanan\r\nenergi.</span></p><p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Dalam\r\npernyataan \"Panel surya adalah sumber energi bersih karena tidak\r\nmenghasilkan emisi,\" konsep fisika mana yang paling penting untuk\r\nmendukung pernyataan tersebut?</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Apakah panel surya menggunakan bahan bakar selama beroperasi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Apakah efek fotovoltaik mengeluarkan emisi gas\r\nbuang saat bekerja</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Apakah panel surya membutuhkan air untuk mendinginkan bahannya</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Apakah panel surya mengeluarkan asap saat bekerja</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Apakah material silikon pada panel surya bersifat ramah lingkungan</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Apakah efek fotovoltaik mengeluarkan emisi gas\r\nbuang saat bekerja</span></p>', NULL, 'B', 0.000, 0, 1, '2026-04-24 03:37:37', '2026-04-24 03:37:37'),
(284, 'IMO002', 10, NULL, '<p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:15.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n5.0pt;margin-left:0cm;background:#E8F4FD\"><b><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;color:#1A5276;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV\">Kasus 1: Energi Surya sebagai Sumber Energi Masa Depan</span></b><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\">Matahari memancarkan energi dalam jumlah sangat besar setiap detiknya.\r\nEnergi ini dapat diserap oleh panel surya melalui efek fotovoltaik, yaitu\r\nproses di mana foton cahaya matahari menabrak elektron pada material\r\nsemikonduktor (biasanya silikon) pada panel surya sehingga menghasilkan arus\r\nlistrik. Panel surya tidak memerlukan bahan bakar, tidak menghasilkan emisi\r\nsaat beroperasi, dan dapat dipasang di atap rumah maupun lahan terbuka.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Di Indonesia, potensi energi surya sangat besar\r\nkarena letak geografisnya di garis khatulistiwa yang mendapatkan sinar matahari\r\nrata-rata 4-5 jam per hari secara efektif. Namun, pemanfaatannya masih terbatas\r\nakibat biaya awal pemasangan yang tinggi dan keterbatasan teknologi penyimpanan\r\nenergi.</span><p></p><p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Seorang\r\nsiswa ingin menguji apakah panel surya menghasilkan daya listrik lebih besar\r\npada siang hari dibanding pagi hari. Berdasarkan prinsip efek fotovoltaik,\r\nvariabel utama yang harus diukur adalah....</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Intensitas panas matahari dan daya listrik yang dihasilkan</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Intensitas cahaya matahari dan daya listrik yang\r\ndihasilkan<b></b></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Suhu panas matahari dan daya listrik yang dihasilkan</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Kelembapan udara dan daya listrik yang dihasilkan</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Kapasitas baterai dan daya listrik yang dihasilkan</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Intensitas cahaya matahari dan daya listrik yang\r\ndihasilkan<b></b></span></p>', NULL, 'B', 0.000, 0, 1, '2026-04-24 03:37:37', '2026-04-24 03:37:37'),
(285, 'IMO001', 10, NULL, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:15.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n5.0pt;margin-left:0cm;background:#E8F4FD\"><b><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;color:#1A5276;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV\">Kasus 1: Energi Surya sebagai Sumber Energi Masa Depan</span></b><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\">Matahari memancarkan energi dalam jumlah sangat besar setiap detiknya.\r\nEnergi ini dapat diserap oleh panel surya melalui efek fotovoltaik, yaitu\r\nproses di mana foton cahaya matahari menabrak elektron pada material\r\nsemikonduktor (biasanya silikon) pada panel surya sehingga menghasilkan arus\r\nlistrik. Panel surya tidak memerlukan bahan bakar, tidak menghasilkan emisi\r\nsaat beroperasi, dan dapat dipasang di atap rumah maupun lahan terbuka.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Di Indonesia, potensi energi surya sangat besar\r\nkarena letak geografisnya di garis khatulistiwa yang mendapatkan sinar matahari\r\nrata-rata 4-5 jam per hari secara efektif. Namun, pemanfaatannya masih terbatas\r\nakibat biaya awal pemasangan yang tinggi dan keterbatasan teknologi penyimpanan\r\nenergi.</span></p><p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Berdasarkan\r\nbacaan, prinsip kerja panel surya dalam menghasilkan listrik adalah...</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Mengubah energi cahaya matahari menjadi listrik melalui efek\r\nfotosintesis</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Mengubah energi panas matahari menjadi listrik melalui panel surya</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Mengubah energi cahaya matahari menjadi listrik\r\nmelalui efek fotovoltaik</span></p>', '<span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Menyimpan energi cahaya matahari menjadi listrik melalui panel surya</span>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Mengubah energi panas matahari menjadi listrik melalui efek fotovoltaik</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Mengubah energi cahaya matahari menjadi listrik\r\nmelalui efek fotovoltaik</span></p>', NULL, 'C', 0.000, 0, 1, '2026-04-24 03:37:37', '2026-04-24 03:37:37'),
(286, 'ACTofROD01', NULL, 17, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Di sebuah taman bermain dua anak dengan massa sama\r\nduduk pada jarak yang sama dari titik jungkat-jungkit. Ketika salah satu anak\r\nbergeser ke belakang, papan jungkat-jungkit langsung turun ke bawah dan anak di\r\nseberangnya naik ke atas.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777742178_69f631626d022.jpg\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin: 10px 0px;\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:115%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">Gambar 1. Dua anak sedang bermain jungkat-jungkit<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">\r\n\r\n</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">Pernyataan yang paling tepat untuk menjelaskan perubahan keadaan\r\njungkat-jungkit tersebut adalah....<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">perubahan posisi anak memperbesar torsi karena jarak\r\ngaya terhadap titik tumpu tidak berubah</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">perubahan posisi anak memperkecil torsi karena\r\njarak gaya terhadap titik tumpu berkurang</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">perubahan posisi anak memperkecil torsi karena\r\njarak gaya terhadap titik tumpu meningkat</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">perubahan posisi anak memperbesar torsi karena\r\njarak gaya terhadap titik tumpu berkurang</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">perubahan posisi anak memperbesar torsi karena\r\njarak gaya terhadap titik tumpu meningkat</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">perubahan posisi anak memperbesar torsi karena\r\njarak gaya terhadap titik tumpu meningkat</span></p>', NULL, 'E', -0.760, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 07:19:34', '2026-05-03 15:53:44'),
(287, 'ACTofROD02', NULL, 17, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Perhatikan gambar 2 berikut.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777742445_69f6326d100bf.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin: 10px 0px;\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">Gambar 2. Kunci torsi dengan dua posisi pegangan<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">Seorang mekanik menggunakan kunci torsi untuk mengencangkan baut\r\npada mesin. Kunci torsi tersebut dilengkapi skala penunjuk nilai torsi. Mekanik\r\nmemberikan gaya sebesar F = 20N secara tegak lurus pada dua posisi pegangan A\r\ndan posisi pegangan B dengan jarak berbeda dari sumbu rotasi.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">Pernyataan\r\nyang paling tepat untuk menjelaskan perbedaan pembacaan skala torsi pada kedua\r\nposisi adalah....</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">nilai torsi pada posisi A dan B sama besar\r\nkarena gaya yang diberikan sama besar&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">nilai torsi pada posisi B lebih kecil karena\r\nsemakin jauh posisi pegangan dari sumbu rotasi, gaya yang bekerja semakin lemah</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">nilai torsi pada posisi A lebih besar karena\r\nsemakin dekat posisi pegangan dari sumbu rotasi, gaya yang bekerja semakin besar&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">nilai torsi pada posisi B lebih besar karena\r\nlengan gaya lebih panjang, memudahkan mengencangkan baut&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">nilai torsi pada posisi A lebih besar karena\r\nlengan gaya lebih pendek, memudahkan mengencangkan baut&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">nilai torsi pada posisi B lebih besar karena lengan gaya lebih panjang, memudahkan mengencangkan baut&nbsp;</span></p>', NULL, 'D', -1.510, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 07:22:38', '2026-05-03 15:54:07'),
(288, 'ACTofROD03', NULL, 17, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Gambar 3 menunjukkan dua pelat seragam A dan B. Masing-masing\r\npelat berputar pada sumbu rotasi yang berbeda.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777742618_69f6331a6e0b6.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin: 10px 0px;\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">Gambar 3. Dua pelat seragam yang berputar pada sumbu rotasi berbeda<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">Perbandingan&nbsp; momen inersia terhadap sumbu rotasi antar\r\nkedua pelat adalah....</span></span></p>', '<p><strong><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nmajor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\r\nfont-weight:normal\">pelat a memiliki momen inersia lebih besar karena\r\ndistribusi massa berada lebih jauh dari sumbu rotasi</span></strong></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">pelat b memiliki momen inersia lebih besar\r\nkarena distribusi masa berpusat di sumbu rotasi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">kedua pelat memiliki momen inersia yang sama\r\nkarena bentuk dan massa keduanya identik</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">pelat b memiliki momen inersia lebih besar\r\nkarena distribusi masa berpusat di sumbu rotasi</span></p>', '<p>pelat a memiliki momen inersia lebih kecil karena distribusi massa berada lebih jauh dari sumbu rotasi</p>', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.12px; font-weight: normal;\">pelat a memiliki momen inersia lebih besar karena distribusi massa berada lebih jauh dari sumbu rotasi</span></span></p>', NULL, 'A', -0.510, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 07:26:32', '2026-05-03 15:54:57');
INSERT INTO `soal_ujian` (`soal_id`, `kode_soal`, `ujian_id`, `bank_ujian_id`, `pertanyaan`, `pilihan_a`, `pilihan_b`, `pilihan_c`, `pilihan_d`, `pilihan_e`, `pembahasan`, `foto`, `jawaban_benar`, `tingkat_kesulitan`, `is_bank_soal`, `created_by`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(289, 'ACTofROD04', NULL, 17, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Gambar 4 menunjukkan tiga kondisi berbeda bagi\r\nsebuah benda yang bergerak dengan kecepatan v menuju batang yang dapat berotasi.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777742853_69f6340560793.png\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin: 10px 0px;\" class=\"img-fluid\"></p><ul><li><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Gambar (a) benda bergerak dengan kecepatan v tanpa\r\nada batang</span></li><li><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Gambar (b) benda bergerak menabrak ujung batang kemudian berotasi</span></li><li><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%;\">Gambar (c) benda bergerak menabrak batang tepat pada\r\nsumbu rotasi&nbsp;</span></span></li></ul><p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%;\">Berdasarkan informasi tersebut, makna fisik yang\r\npaling tepat tentang kapan sebuah benda memiliki momentum sudut adalah....</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">benda memiliki momentum sudut jika benda\r\nbergerak menjauhi sumbu rotasi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">benda memiliki momentum sudut jika lintasan\r\ngeraknya melalui ujung sumbu rotasi, sehingga memberikan torsi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">benda memiliki momentum sudut jika kecepatannya\r\ncukup besar untuk menyebabkan rotasi pada batang</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">benda tidak memiliki momentum sudut jika\r\nbergerak lurus, karena hanya benda yang berputar yang dapat memiliki momentum\r\nsudut</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">benda memiliki momentum sudut jika lintasan\r\ngeraknya melalui sumbu rotasi, sehingga memberikan torsi</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 14.6667px;\">benda memiliki momentum sudut jika kecepatannya cukup besar untuk menyebabkan rotasi pada batang</span></p>', NULL, 'B', -0.050, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 07:32:26', '2026-05-03 15:55:26'),
(290, 'ACTofROD05', NULL, 17, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Seorang atlet <i>ice skating</i> melakukan\r\natraksi memukau di arena pertandingan. Ketika merentangkan tangan dan kakinya,\r\nputaran atlet tersebut menjadi lambat. </span><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Sedangkan saat atlet <i>ice\r\nskating</i> merapatkan tangan dan kakinya, putarannya menjadi sangat cepat\r\nseperti yang terlihat pada gambar 5 berikut.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777743275_69f635abdfd98.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin: 10px 0px;\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">Gambar 5. Gerakan atlet <i>ice skating</i> saat merentangkan dan\r\nmerapatkan kaki dan tangannya<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%;\">Faktor\r\nmenyebabkan putaran atlet <i>ice skating</i> semakin cepat adalah....</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">ketika posisi terentang, distribusi massa lebih\r\nbesar disumbu rotasi sehingga meningkatkan momen inersia dan jari-jari lebih\r\nbesar sehingga memperbesar momentum sudut&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">ketika posisi terentang, distribusi massa lebih\r\nbesar disumbu rotasi sehingga mengurangi momen inersia dan jari-jari lebih\r\nbesar sehingga memperkecil momentum sudut&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">ketika posisi tangan rapat, distribusi massa\r\nlebih kecil disumbu rotasi sehingga mengurangi momen inersia dan jari-jari\r\nlebih kecil sehingga memperbesar momentum sudut&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">ketika posisi tangan rapat, distribusi massa\r\nlebih kecil disumbu rotasi sehingga meningkatkan momen inersia dan jari-jari\r\nlebih kecil sehingga memperbesar momentum sudut&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">ketika posisi tangan rapat, distribusi massa\r\nlebih kecil disumbu rotasi sehingga meningkatkan momen inersia dan jari-jari\r\nlebih kecil sehingga memperkecil momentum sudut&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">ketika posisi tangan rapat, distribusi massa\r\nlebih kecil disumbu rotasi sehingga mengurangi momen inersia dan jari-jari\r\nlebih kecil sehingga memperbesar momentum&nbsp;</span></p>', NULL, 'C', -0.510, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 07:36:24', '2026-05-03 15:56:08'),
(291, 'ACTofROD06', NULL, 17, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Gambar 6 menunjukkan posisi seorang atlet loncat\r\nindah saat melompat dari papan loncat hingga memasuki air. Selama terjun, atlet\r\nmenarik lengan dan kakinya ke posisi jongkok yang rapat saat berada di udara\r\ndan meluruskan keduanya sebelum memasuki air.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777743435_69f6364bc0a3d.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin: 10px 0px;\"></p><p class=\"Default\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:center;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV\">Gambar 6. Berbagai posisi atlet loncat indah</span></p><p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%;\">Ketika\r\natlet loncat indah melakukan salto dengan menarik lengan dan kakinya ke posisi\r\njongkok yang rapat, perubahan momen inersia dan kecepatan sudut atlet pada\r\nposisi tersebut adalah....</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">momen inersia meningkat dan kecepatan sudut\r\nmeningkat</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">momen inersia menurun dan kecepatan sudut meningkat&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">momen inersia meningkat dan kecepatan sudut menurun</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">momen inersia menurun dan kecepatan sudut menurun&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">momen inersia konstan dan kecepatan sudut konstan&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 14.6667px;\">momen inersia menurun dan kecepatan sudut meningkat&nbsp;</span></p>', NULL, 'B', -2.520, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 07:39:23', '2026-05-03 15:56:39'),
(292, 'ACTofROD08', NULL, 17, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Perhatikan Gambar 7 yang menunjukkan perubahan\r\nkecepatan sudut ω rotor terhadap waktu t selama periode 12 detik.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777743630_69f6370e46dc2.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin: 10px 0px;\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:115%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">Gambar 7. Grafik kecepatan sudut terhadap waktu<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">Berdasarkan\r\ngrafik kecepatan sudut terhadap waktu, grafik yang menunjukkan periode rotasi\r\npada rotor selama 12 detik adalah....</span></span></p>', '<p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777743660_69f6372c86496.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin: 10px 0px;\"><br></p>', '<p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777743669_69f637351d66c.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin: 10px 0px;\"><br></p>', '<p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777743677_69f6373d045ed.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin: 10px 0px;\"><br></p>', '<p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777743685_69f63745853ce.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin: 10px 0px;\"><br></p>', '<p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777743693_69f6374d9268e.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin: 10px 0px;\"><br></p>', '<p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777743708_69f6375c61567.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin: 10px 0px;\"><br></p>', NULL, 'C', -0.760, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 07:42:06', '2026-05-03 15:57:09'),
(293, 'ACTofROD08', NULL, 17, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Perhatikan Gambar 8 yang menunjukkan tampilan\r\nsamping dari lengan kran menara.</span><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777743869_69f637fde31c3.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: 235.812px; margin: 10px 0px; width: 419.502px;\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">Gambar 8. Tampilan samping lengan kran menara</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:0cm;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\">Beban ditopang\r\noleh troli yang dapat bergerak sepanjang lengan kran. Lengan kran terdiri dari\r\nsemua bagian kran di atas bantalan poros, tetapi tidak termasuk troli dan\r\nbeban. Momen inersia lengan kran pada sumbu rotasi&nbsp; (</span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><font face=\"Calibri, sans-serif\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.6667px;\">2,6 x 10<sup>7</sup></span><span style=\"font-size: 14.6667px;\">kg.m</span><span style=\"font-size: 11px;\"><sup>2</sup></span></font></span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\">). Massa troli\r\ndan beban (</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 14.6667px;\">2,2 x 10</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><sup>3</sup></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 14.6667px;\">kg</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 12pt;\">).</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Berdasarkan\r\ninformasi pada gambar 8, makna fisik dari perubahan posisi troli pada lengan\r\nkran terhadap momen inersia total sistem kran adalah....</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">menggeser troli menjauh dari sumbu rotasi\r\nmeningkatkan momen inersia sistem karena massa berada lebih jauh dari sumbu\r\nrotasi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">menggeser troli menjauh dari sumbu rotasi\r\nmenurunkan momen inersia sistem karena beban bergerak tanpa memengaruhi lengan kran&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">menggeser troli mendekati sumbu rotasi\r\nmeningkatkan momen inersia sistem karena massa berpusat disekitar sumbu rotasi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">menggeser troli mendekati sumbu rotasi\r\nmenurunkan momen inersia sistem karena beban bergerak tanpa memengaruhi lengan\r\nkran</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">menggeser troli menjauh dari sumbu rotasi\r\nmenyebabkan momen inersia sistem tidak berubah, tetapi meningkatkan torsi\r\nsistem</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">menggeser troli menjauh dari sumbu rotasi\r\nmeningkatkan momen inersia sistem karena massa berada lebih jauh dari sumbu\r\nrotasi</span></p>', NULL, 'A', -0.630, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 07:48:55', '2026-05-03 15:57:33'),
(294, 'ACTofROD09', NULL, 17, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Gambar 9 menunjukkan sebuah wahana permainan kora-kora\r\nyang berputar di sekitar sumbu rotasi.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777744226_69f639628b3d6.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: 181.573px; margin: 10px 0px; width: 323.104px;\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">Gambar 9. Wahana permainan komedi putar<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:0cm;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\">Terdiri dari\r\ndua batang, masing-masing membawa tempat duduk berisi penumpang. Sistem\r\ndinyatakan <b><i>“</i></b><i>sepenuhnya seimbang”,</i> dan arah putaran dapat\r\ndibalik selama berputar.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">Berdasarkan\r\ninformasi tersebut, makna fisik dari pernyataan bahwa rotor “sepenuhnya\r\nseimbang” adalah....</span></span></p>', '<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">massa pada setiap tempat duduk memiliki jarak yang\r\nsama terhadap sumbu rotasi sehingga tidak ada torsi yang menyebabkan kora-kora condong\r\nke salah satu sisi</span>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">massa total kora-kora lebih besar dari massa dua\r\ntempat duduk sehingga tidak mudah terganggu oleh beban penumpang</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">kora-kora </span><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:\r\n11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">tidak mengalami gesekan\r\nudara sehingga dapat berputar terus menerus secara konstan</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">tempat duduk dapat menahan beban penumpang\r\nsehingga komedi putar tetap stabil meskipun terjadi putaran</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">kora-kora </span><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:\r\n11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">mempertahankan kecepatan\r\nputar yang sama meskipun arah putaran dibalik</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">massa pada setiap tempat duduk memiliki jarak yang\r\nsama terhadap sumbu rotasi sehingga tidak ada torsi yang menyebabkan kora-kora condong\r\nke salah satu sisi</span></p>', NULL, 'A', 2.050, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 07:53:44', '2026-05-03 15:58:08'),
(295, 'ACTofROD10', NULL, 17, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Perhatikan gambar 10 ketika dua cakram yang\r\nberada pada satu sumbu rotasi yang sama. Cakram A memiliki momen inersia I<sub>A</sub></span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">&nbsp;= 10 kg.m</span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 12px;\"><sup>2</sup></span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">&nbsp;berotasi\r\npada kecepatan sudut sebesar 30 rad/s. Sedangkan cakram B yang mula-mula diam\r\ndengan momen inersia I<sub>B</sub></span><!--[if gte msEquation 12]><m:oMath><m:sSub><m:sSubPr><span\r\n   style=\'font-size:12.0pt;mso-ansi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;\r\n   font-family:\"Cambria Math\",serif;mso-ascii-font-family:\"Cambria Math\";\r\n   mso-hansi-font-family:\"Cambria Math\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\n   mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;font-style:italic;\r\n   mso-bidi-font-style:normal\'><m:ctrlPr></m:ctrlPr></span></m:sSubPr><m:e><i\r\n   style=\'mso-bidi-font-style:normal\'><span lang=IN style=\'font-size:12.0pt;\r\n   line-height:107%;font-family:\"Cambria Math\",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n   Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\n   mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\n   EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\'><m:r>I</m:r></span></i></m:e><m:sub><i\r\n   style=\'mso-bidi-font-style:normal\'><span lang=IN style=\'font-size:12.0pt;\r\n   line-height:107%;font-family:\"Cambria Math\",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n   Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\n   mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\n   EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\'><m:r>B</m:r></span></i></m:sub></m:sSub></m:oMath><![endif]--><!--[if !msEquation]--><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;position:relative;top:3.5pt;mso-text-raise:-3.5pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><v:shape id=\"_x0000_i1025\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style=\"width:10.5pt;height:15pt\"><v:imagedata src=\"file:///C:/Users/Lenovo/AppData/Local/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_image003.png\" o:title=\"\" chromakey=\"white\"></v:imagedata></v:shape></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">&nbsp;= 5&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">kg.m</span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"line-height: 12.84px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 12px;\"><sup>2</sup></span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 12pt;\">. Setelah kedua cakram\r\ndihubungkan, keduanya berputar dengan kecepatan sudut yang sama.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777744472_69f63a58e2ff1.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: 132.603px; margin: 10px 0px; width: 333.104px;\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">Gambar 10. Dua cakram berada pada sumbu rotasi yang sama<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nIN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">Berdasarkan\r\nanalisis kondisi awal pada gambar 10 dan interaksi kedua cakram, keadaan sistem\r\nsetelah kedua cakram digabungkan adalah....</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">kecepatan sudut sistem menjadi 10 rad/s karena\r\nmomentum sudut sistem tetap tetapi momen inersia bertambah</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">kecepatan sudut sistem menjadi 40 rad/s karena\r\nmomentum sudut sistem tetap tetapi momen inersia berkurang</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">kecepatan sudut sistem menjadi 15 rad/s karena\r\nmomentum sudut sistem tetap tetapi momen inersia bertambah</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">kecepatan sudut sistem menjadi 20 rad/s karena\r\nmomentum sudut sistem tetap tetapi momen inersia bertambah</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">kecepatan sudut sistem menjadi 15 rad/s karena\r\nenergi kinetik rotasi terbagi sama pada kedua cakram</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">kecepatan sudut sistem menjadi 20 rad/s karena momentum sudut sistem tetap tetapi momen inersia bertambah</span></p>', NULL, 'D', 0.180, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 07:57:10', '2026-05-03 15:58:29'),
(296, 'ACTofROD11', NULL, 17, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Seorang teknisi sedang menguji lengan penyangga\r\npapan reklame sepanjang 60 cm yang dapat berputar bebas pada engsel di titik B.\r\nIa memberikan tiga gaya masing-masing sebesar 10 N dengan arah yang berbeda\r\nseperti yang ditunjukkan pada gambar 11.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777744672_69f63b20d8bb8.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: 79.4542px; margin: 10px 0px; width: 305.104px;\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">Gambar 11. Lengan penyangga papan reklame<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">Arah\r\nputaran papan reklame dan besar torsi total yang bekerja pada papan reklame di\r\nengsel titik B adalah....</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">berputar berlawanan arah jarum jam dengan torsi\r\ntotal 1,5 nm</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">berputar berlawanan arah jarum jam dengan torsi\r\ntotal 3 nm</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">berputar searah jarum jam dengan torsi total 1,5 nm&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">berputar searah jarum jam dengan torsi total 3 nm&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">tidak berputar karena resultan gaya nol&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">berputar berlawanan arah jarum jam dengan torsi total 1,5 nm</span></p>', NULL, 'A', -0.890, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 07:59:50', '2026-05-03 15:58:45'),
(297, 'ACTofROD12', NULL, 17, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Salah dan Mane mengikuti kunjungan museum seni\r\ndi Paris. Mereka menemukan lima benda bernilai seni unik berjejer yaitu (P)\r\nbola pingpong yang diletakkan di dalam mangkuk, (Q) piramida yang berdiri\r\nterbalik, (R) bola di atas topi, (S) helm yang diletakan terbalik, dan (T) bola\r\n<i>bowling</i> yang diletakkan di atas meja datar. Ketika benda disentuh atau\r\ndidorong secara perlahan, mereka menyadari bahwa titik berat atau pusat\r\ngravitasi setiap benda berbeda. Tidak semua benda menunjukkan respons yang sama\r\nterhadap gangguan kecil yang diberikan.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777744896_69f63c00cac30.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: 248.969px; margin: 10px 0px; width: 266.104px;\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">Gambar 12. Lima benda dengan posisi tertentu pada meja<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">Berdasarkan\r\nilustrasi Gambar 12, benda yang memiliki keseimbangan stabil adalah....</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">(P) bola pingpong yang diletakan di dalam\r\nmangkuk</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">(T) bola <i>bowling</i> yang diletakan di atas\r\nmeja datar&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">(S) helm yang diletakan terbalik&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">(Q) piramida berdiri terbalik&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">(R) bola di\r\natas topi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">(P) bola pingpong yang diletakan di dalam\r\nmangkuk</span></p>', NULL, 'A', -1.930, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 08:03:34', '2026-05-03 16:00:09');
INSERT INTO `soal_ujian` (`soal_id`, `kode_soal`, `ujian_id`, `bank_ujian_id`, `pertanyaan`, `pilihan_a`, `pilihan_b`, `pilihan_c`, `pilihan_d`, `pilihan_e`, `pembahasan`, `foto`, `jawaban_benar`, `tingkat_kesulitan`, `is_bank_soal`, `created_by`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(298, 'ACTofROD13', NULL, 17, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Sebuah batang kaku horizontal dipasang pada\r\nporosnya di tengah sehingga dapat berputar bebas. Sebuah beban bermassa 3M\r\ndipasang pada salah satu ujung batang dan sebuah tempat beban dipasang pada\r\nujung lainnya, keduanya berjarak R dari poros tengah.&nbsp; Sebuah beban bermassa M bergerak dengan\r\nkecepatan v tegak lurus menuju batang yang diam seperti yang ditunjukkan pada\r\ngambar 13.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777745082_69f63cba7a407.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: 194.281px; margin: 10px 0px; width: 345.815px;\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">Gambar 13. Batang kaku horizontal</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:0cm;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\">Beban M\r\nmenabrak tempat beban dan tetap berada di dalamnya saat sistem mulai berputar\r\ndengan kecepatan sudut </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:EN-ID\">ω</span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">. Massa batang dan tempat beban diabaikan.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">Berdasarkan\r\nkondisi tersebut, besaran fisika yang menentukan momentum sudut total sistem\r\nsegera setelah tabrakan adalah....</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">momen inersia gabungan kedua beban (M dan 3M)\r\nterhadap sumbu rotasi dikurang kecepatan sudut ω, karena keduanya berada pada\r\njarak R dari sumbu rotasi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">momen inersia gabungan kedua beban (M dan 3M)\r\nterhadap sumbu rotasi dikalikan kecepatan sudut ω, karena keduanya berada pada\r\njarak R dari sumbu rotasi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">momen inersia gabungan kedua beban (M dan 3M)\r\nterhadap sumbu rotasi ditambah kecepatan sudut ω, karena keduanya berada pada\r\njarak R dari sumbu rotasi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">momen inersia gabungan kedua beban (M dan 3M)\r\nterhadap sumbu rotasi dibagi kecepatan sudut ω, karena keduanya berada pada\r\njarak R dari sumbu rotasi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">momentum sudut hanya bergantung pada kecepatan\r\nsudut ω, karena batang dianggap sama sehingga beban di ujung tidak berpengaruh</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">momen inersia gabungan kedua beban (M dan 3M)\r\nterhadap sumbu rotasi dikalikan kecepatan sudut ω, karena keduanya berada pada\r\njarak R dari sumbu rotasi</span></p>', NULL, 'B', -0.630, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 08:06:21', '2026-05-03 16:00:42'),
(299, 'ACTofROD14', NULL, 17, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ligatures:none;mso-ansi-language:IN;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Gambar 14 menunjukkan\r\nhubungan torsi total τ terhadap waktu t pada benda tegar yang memiliki momen\r\ninersia 6,0 kg.m<sup>2</sup>.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777761361_69f67c51bcd07.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: 169.85px; margin: 10px 0px; width: 298.104px;\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%;\r\nmso-outline-level:3\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ligatures:none;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID\">Gambar 14.\r\nGrafik hubungan torsi terhadap waktu<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ligatures:none;mso-ansi-language:IN;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">Pada saat t = 0, benda berputar searah jarum jam.\r\nAnggap arah berlawanan jarum jam sebagai arah positif. Berdasarkan Gambar 14,\r\narah putaran benda pada t = 5 dan alasan yang paling tepat adalah....</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ligatures:none;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">benda\r\nberputar berlawanan arah jarum jam karena torsi akhir bernilai negatif&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ligatures:none;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">benda\r\nberputar searah jarum jam karena jumlah torsi positif lebih besar dibanding\r\ntorsi negatif pada akhir interval&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ligatures:none;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">benda\r\nberputar searah jarum jam karena karena perubahan arah hanya ditentukan oleh\r\ntanda torsi terbesar yang bekerja selama selang waktu tersebut&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ligatures:none;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">benda\r\nberputar berlawanan arah jarum jam, karena torsi positif pada awalnya hanya\r\nmemperkecil besar kecepatan sudut awal tanpa membalik arahnya, dan torsi\r\nnegatif pada akhir interval kembali mendukung arah putaran semula&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ligatures:none;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">benda\r\nberputar searah jarum jam, karena torsi positif pada awalnya hanya memperkecil\r\nbesar kecepatan sudut awal tanpa membalik arahnya, dan torsi negatif pada akhir\r\ninterval kembali mendukung arah putaran semula</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ligatures:none;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">benda\r\nberputar searah jarum jam, karena torsi positif pada awalnya hanya memperkecil\r\nbesar kecepatan sudut awal tanpa membalik arahnya, dan torsi negatif pada akhir\r\ninterval kembali mendukung arah putaran semula</span></p>', NULL, 'E', 1.310, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 12:37:42', '2026-05-03 16:01:01'),
(300, 'ACTofROD15', NULL, 17, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ansi-language:\r\nIN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Dua bola padat\r\nberpasangan dihubungkan pada ujung batang tipis. Bola tersebut berputar dengan\r\npusat massa setiap bola pada jarak 22 cm dari sumbu rotasi. Batang tipis\r\ntersebut memiliki massa 20 g. Setiap bola memiliki jari-jari 4 cm dan massa 750\r\ng.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777761508_69f67ce4845a5.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: 208.948px; margin: 10px 0px; width: 237.441px;\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">Gambar 15. Dua bola padat berpasangan\r\ndihubungkan pada ujung batang tipis</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:0cm;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:150%;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">Momen inersia batang tipis 1/2 ML<sup>2</sup></span><!--[if gte msEquation 12]><m:oMath><m:f><m:fPr><span\r\n   style=\'font-size:12.0pt;mso-ansi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;\r\n   font-family:\"Cambria Math\",serif;mso-ascii-font-family:\"Cambria Math\";\r\n   mso-hansi-font-family:\