n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">Rasio momen inersia batang tipis terhadap momen\r\ninersia total bola berpasangan adalah....</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ligatures:none;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">0,044\r\n%, karena momen inersia bola hanya ditentukan oleh jari-jari bola sehingga\r\nkontribusi bola tidak terlalu besar</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ligatures:none;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">0,44\r\n%, karena momen inersia batang sangat kecil dibandingkan kontribusi dua bola\r\nyang berjarak jauh dari sumbu rotasi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ligatures:none;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">4,4 %,\r\nkarena momen inersia batang sangat kecil dibandingkan kontribusi dua bola yang\r\nberjarak jauh dari sumbu rotasi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ligatures:none;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">14 %,\r\nkarena massa batang walaupun kecil tetap menyumbang momen inersia yang cukup\r\nsignifikan terhadap sistem</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ligatures:none;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">44%,\r\nkarena massa batang dan massa bola sama-sama berperan sehingga kontribusi\r\nbatang tidak dapat diabaikan</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ligatures:none;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">0,44\r\n%, karena momen inersia batang sangat kecil dibandingkan kontribusi dua bola\r\nyang berjarak jauh dari sumbu rotasi</span></p>', NULL, 'B', -0.890, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 12:40:54', '2026-05-03 16:01:22'),
(301, 'ACTofROD16', NULL, 17, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Gambar 16 menunjukkan dua poros A dan B yang\r\nberputar bebas pada sumbu rotasi yang sama. Poros A&nbsp; berputar searah jarum jam dengan kecepatan\r\nsudut 95 rad/detik dan momen inersia 7,2&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">kg/m</span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"line-height: 12.84px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 12px;\"><sup>2</sup></span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">. Sedangkan poros B\r\nberputar berlawanan arah jarum jam dengan kecepatan sudut 45 rad/detik dan\r\nmomen inersia 11,5 kg/m</span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 12px;\"><sup>2</sup></span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777761750_69f67dd6572fd.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: 116.399px; margin: 10px 0px; width: 368.104px;\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">Gambar 16. Dua poros yang berputar bebas pada sumbu rotasi yang\r\nsama</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-