p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">berlawanan jarum jam, karena poros b memiliki\r\nmomen inersia lebih besar</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">berlawanan jarum jam, karena momentum sudut\r\ntotal awal bernilai negatif</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">tidak bisa ditentukan karena gesekan\r\nmenghilangkan momentum sudut sistem</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">searah jarum jam, karena gesekan selalu\r\nmemperkuat putaran poros yang lebih cepat</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">berlawanan jarum jam, karena momentum sudut\r\ntotal awal bernilai negatif</span></p>', NULL, 'C', -0.161, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 12:44:41', '2026-05-03 16:01:58'),
(302, 'ACTofROD17', NULL, 17, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Gambar 17 menunjukkan sebuah eksperimen untuk\r\nmenentukan momen inersia roda sepeda.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777761917_69f67e7da2399.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: 169.615px; margin: 10px 0px; width: 271.69px;\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">Gambar 17. Sepeda terbalik yang pada ujung roda dipasang beban<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">Salah\r\nsatu ujung benang yang kuat diikatkan ke roda. Benang tersebut dililitkan di\r\nsekitar roda, dan beban sebesar 0,2 kg diikatkan pada ujung bebas benang. Roda\r\ndipegang sedemikian rupa sehingga beban berada pada ketinggian 1,5 m di atas\r\nlantai. Dengan mengabaikan gesekan antara poros dan sumbu rotasi, perubahan\r\nenergi yang terjadi mulai dari saat roda dilepaskan hingga beban menyentuh\r\nlantai adalah....</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">energi potensial berubah seluruhnya menjadi\r\nenergi kinetik saat mencapai lantai, sementara roda tetap tidak berputar karena\r\nbenang mencegah rotasi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">energi potensial berubah sebagian menjadi energi\r\nkinetik dan sebagian menjadi energi kinetik rotasi roda ketika benang\r\nmengerahkan torsi pada roda</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">energi potensial berubah sebagian menjadi energi\r\nbunyi karena gesekan udara pada roda, sementara energi kinetik rotasi tidak berubah</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">energi kinetik roda berubah menjadi energi\r\npotensial sehingga massa turun lebih lambat dari jatuh bebas</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">energi potensial berubah sepenuhnya menjadi\r\nenergi panas akibat gesekan pada poros roda</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">energi potensial berubah sebagian menjadi energi\r\nkinetik dan sebagian menjadi energi kinetik rotasi roda ketika benang\r\nmengerahkan torsi pada roda</span></p>', NULL, 'B', 0.180, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 12:46:45', '2026-05-03 16:02:20');
INSERT INTO `soal_ujian` (`soal_id`, `kode_soal`, `ujian_id`, `bank_ujian_id`, `pertanyaan`, `pilihan_a`, `pilihan_b`, `pilihan_c`, `pilihan_d`, `pilihan_e`, `pembahasan`, `foto`, `jawaban_benar`, `tingkat_kesulitan`, `is_bank_soal`, `created_by`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(303, 'ACTofROD18', NULL, 17, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Gambar 18 menunjukkan prinsip kerja pengering\r\nsayuran untuk mengeringkan sayuran yang telah dicuci.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777762055_69f67f0795ade.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: 190.322px; margin: 10px 0px; width: 262.104px;\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">Gambar 18. Prinsip kerja pengering sayuran</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:0cm;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\">Sayuran\r\nditempatkan dalam keranjang dan tutupnya dipasang. Ketika pegangan A diputar,\r\nkeranjang dan isinya berputar dengan cepat. Air pada sayuran terdorong melalui\r\nlubang-lubang di keranjang ke dalam mangkuk penampung air. Poros untuk\r\ngear&nbsp; B dipasang pada tutup. Ketika gear\r\nB berputar, gear C juga berputar.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">Bagaimana\r\ngaya pada pegangan A menyebabkan keranjang berputar adalah....</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">gaya pada pegangan A menghasilkan torsi pada\r\ngear B dan karena ukuran gear C lebih kecil maka keranjang berputar lebih cepat</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">gaya pada pegangan A menghasilkan torsi pada\r\ngear B, dan karena gear C memiliki jumlah gigi berbeda maka putarannya\r\nmeningkat sehingga keranjang berputar lebih cepat</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">gaya pada pegangan A menghasilkan torsi pada\r\ngear B, dan karena gear C terhubung langsung ke keranjang membuat keranjang\r\nmemperoleh kecepatan sudut yang lebih cepat</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">gaya pada pegangan A menghasilkan torsi pada\r\ngear B, dan karena gear C memiliki pada rasio gear berbeda maka putaran yang\r\nditransmisikan ke keranjang meningkat menjadi lebih cepat</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">gaya pada pegangan A menghasilkan torsi pada\r\ngear B, dan karena gear C memiliki ukuran gear lebih besar maka keranjang\r\nberputar dengan kecepatan sudut yang lebih cepat</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">gaya pada pegangan A menghasilkan torsi pada\r\ngear B, dan karena gear C memiliki ukuran gear lebih besar maka keranjang\r\nberputar dengan kecepatan sudut yang lebih cepat</span></p>', NULL, 'E', -0.390, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 12:49:09', '2026-05-03 16:02:47'),
(304, 'ACTofROD19', NULL, 17, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Rina memperhatikan seorang ayah mendorong komedi\r\nputar bermassa 15 kg berjari-jari 1,5 m dengan gaya 250 N di tepinya. Anggap\r\nkomedi putar sebagai cakram seragam dan gesekan diabaikan.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777762210_69f67fa256443.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: 139.108px; margin: 10px 0px; width: 443.104px;\"></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin:0cm;text-align:center;line-height:150%\">Gambar 19.\r\nAyah mendorong komedi putar</p><ul><li><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%;\">kondisi 1: komedi putar didorong tanpa anak</span></span></li><li><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%;\">kondisi2:&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">komedi putar didorong dengan anak bermassa 18 kg\r\nduduk berjarak 1,25m dari pusat</span></li></ul><p class=\"Default\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nIN\">Rina berpendapat “Percepatan sudut pada Kondisi 1 dan Kondisi 2 adalah\r\nsama, karena anak tidak memberikan gaya dorong sehingga tidak memengaruhi gerak\r\nrotasi”<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%;\">Penilaian\r\nyang paling tepat terhadap pendapat Rina adalah....</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Rina benar, karena anak tidak memberikan torsi\r\nsehingga percepatan sudut tetap 6,67 rad/s² pada kedua kondisi&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Rina tidak tepat karena pada kondisi 2\r\npercepatan sudut lebih besar menjadi 5,12 rad/s² karena anak menambah gaya\r\ntotal sistem&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Rina tidak tepat karena pada kondisi 2\r\npercepatan sudut lebih kecil menjadi 4,44 rad/s² karena massa anak menambah\r\nmomen inersia sistem&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Rina tidak tepat karena pada kondisi 2\r\npercepatan sudut lebih kecil menjadi 3,34 rad/s² karena massa anak mengurangi\r\ntorsi yang bekerja&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Rina tidak tepat karena pada kondisi 2\r\npercepatan sudut lebih kecil menjadi 2,67 rad/s² karena massa anak memperkecil\r\nmomen inersia sistem&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 14.6667px;\">Rina tidak tepat karena pada kondisi 2 percepatan sudut lebih kecil menjadi 4,44 rad/s² karena massa anak menambah momen inersia sistem&nbsp;</span></p>', NULL, 'C', 1.019, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 12:54:20', '2026-05-03 16:04:06'),
(305, 'ACTofROD20', NULL, 17, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Suatu sistem yang terdiri dari dua roda saling\r\nterhubung dan berputar pada sumbu rotasi sama yang melalui pusat kedua roda. </span><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Roda\r\npertama dengan jari-jari 3R dan roda kedua dengan jari-jari 2R.&nbsp; Empat gaya diberikan pada tepi roda, seperti\r\nyang ditunjukkan pada gambar 20.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777762515_69f680d31b21e.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: 179.948px; margin: 10px 0px; width: 314.906px;\"></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"SV\">Gambar 20. Dua roda berputar pada sumbu rotasi sama\r\ndiberi gaya dari beberapa arah<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%;mso-layout-grid-align:\r\nnone;text-autospace:none\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt;mso-ansi-language:SV\">Seorang siswa, Andi, menyatakan: “Karena gaya\r\nterbesar adalah </span><!--[if gte msEquation 12]><m:oMath><i style=\'mso-bidi-font-style:\r\n normal\'><span lang=SV style=\'font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n \"Cambria Math\",serif;mso-bidi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\n major-bidi;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ansi-language:SV\'><m:r>2</m:r></span></i><i\r\n style=\'mso-bidi-font-style:normal\'><span style=\'font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n 150%;font-family:\"Cambria Math\",serif;mso-bidi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\n mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-ID\'><m:r>F</m:r></span></i></m:oMath><![endif]--><!--[if !msEquation]--><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;position:relative;top:3.5pt;mso-text-raise:-3.5pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><v:shapetype id=\"_x0000_t75\" coordsize=\"21600,21600\" o:spt=\"75\" o:preferrelative=\"t\" path=\"m@4@5l@4@11@9@11@9@5xe\" filled=\"f\" stroked=\"f\">\r\n <v:stroke joinstyle=\"miter\">\r\n <v:formulas>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"if lineDrawn pixelLineWidth 0\">\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @0 1 0\">\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum 0 0 @1\">\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @2 1 2\">\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelWidth\">\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelHeight\">\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @0 0 1\">\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @6 1 2\">\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelWidth\">\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @8 21600 0\">\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelHeight\">\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @10 21600 0\">\r\n </v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:formulas>\r\n <v:path o:extrusionok=\"f\" gradientshapeok=\"t\" o:connecttype=\"rect\">\r\n <o:lock v:ext=\"edit\" aspectratio=\"t\">\r\n</o:lock></v:path></v:stroke></v:shapetype><v:shape id=\"_x0000_i1025\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style=\"width:14.5pt;\r\n height:15pt\">\r\n <v:imagedata src=\"file:///C:/Users/Lenovo/AppData/Local/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_image001.png\" o:title=\"\" chromakey=\"white\">\r\n</v:imagedata></v:shape></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ansi-language:SV\">yang bekerja pada\r\njari-jari terbesar yaitu </span><!--[if gte msEquation 12]><m:oMath><i\r\n style=\'mso-bidi-font-style:normal\'><span lang=SV style=\'font-size:12.0pt;\r\n line-height:150%;font-family:\"Cambria Math\",serif;mso-bidi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\n mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ansi-language:SV\'><m:r>3</m:r></span></i><i\r\n style=\'mso-bidi-font-style:normal\'><span style=\'font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n 150%;font-family:\"Cambria Math\",serif;mso-bidi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\n mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-ID\'><m:r>R</m:r></span></i></m:oMath><![endif]--><!--[if !msEquation]--><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;position:relative;top:3.5pt;mso-text-raise:-3.5pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><v:shape id=\"_x0000_i1025\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style=\"width:14.5pt;height:15pt\">\r\n <v:imagedata src=\"file:///C:/Users/Lenovo/AppData/Local/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_image002.png\" o:title=\"\" chromakey=\"white\">\r\n</v:imagedata></v:shape></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt;mso-ansi-language:SV\">, maka torsi total sistem searah jarum jam dan\r\nbernilai 6FR.”<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">Tanggapan yang paling tepat terhadap pernyataan Andi\r\nadalah....</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ansi-language:\r\nIN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">pernyataan Andi tidak\r\ntepat, karena gaya yang menghasilkan torsi berlawanan arah jarum jam lebih\r\nbesar sehingga torsi total adalah 2FR berlawanan arah jarum jam</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ansi-language:\r\nIN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">pernyataan Andi tidak\r\ntepat, karena gaya yang menghasilkan torsi berlawanan arah jarum jam lebih\r\nbesar sehingga torsi total adalah 4FR berlawanan arah jarum jam&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ansi-language:\r\nIN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">pernyataan Andi tidak\r\ntepat, karena gaya yang menghasilkan torsi berlawanan arah jarum jam lebih\r\nbesar sehingga torsi total adalah 6FR berlawanan arah jarum jam&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ansi-language:\r\nIN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">pernyataan Andi tepat,\r\nkarena gaya yang menghasilkan torsi searah jarum jam lebih besar sehingga torsi\r\ntotal adalah 6FR searah jarum jam&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ansi-language:\r\nIN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">pernyataan Andi tepat,\r\nkarena gaya yang menghasilkan torsi searah jarum jam lebih besar sehingga torsi\r\ntotal adalah 2FR searah jarum jam&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">pernyataan Andi tidak tepat, karena gaya yang menghasilkan torsi berlawanan ar