-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;position:relative;top:3.5pt;mso-text-raise:-3.5pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><v:shape id=\"_x0000_i1025\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style=\"width:38.5pt;height:15.5pt\"><v:imagedata src=\"file:///C:/Users/Lenovo/AppData/Local/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_image002.png\" o:title=\"\" chromakey=\"white\"></v:imagedata></v:shape></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">. </span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Sebuah roda kedua bermassa 0,5M dan berjari-jari\r\n0,5R diletakkan di atas roda pertama. Kecepatan sudut baru dari gabungan kedua roda\r\nadalah 2/3</span><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">ω.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777762763_69f681cb4880f.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: 197.244px; margin: 10px 0px; width: 245.104px;\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">Gambar 21. Dua roda yang dihubungkan pada sumbu rotasi yang sama</span></p><p class=\"Default\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nIN\">Naro memberikan pendapat bahwa “Karena kecepatan sudut berkurang dari&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: start;\">ω&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 1rem; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">menjadi 2/3</span><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: start;\">ω</span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 1rem; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">, maka energi kinetik rotasi sistem juga hanya\r\nbergantung pada kecepatan sudut. Jadi energi kinetik akhirnya menjadi 1/3 E<sub>k</sub></span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; position: relative; top: 6pt;\"><v:shape id=\"_x0000_i1025\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style=\"width:19.5pt;height:20pt\"><v:imagedata src=\"file:///C:/Users/Lenovo/AppData/Local/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_image003.png\" o:title=\"\" chromakey=\"white\"></v:imagedata></v:shape></span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 1rem; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">”</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r