o:lock v:ext=\"edit\" aspectratio=\"t\">\r\n</o:lock></v:path></v:stroke></v:shapetype><v:shape id=\"_x0000_i1025\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style=\"width:9pt;\r\n height:15pt\">\r\n <v:imagedata src=\"file:///C:/Users/Lenovo/AppData/Local/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_image001.png\" o:title=\"\" chromakey=\"white\">\r\n</v:imagedata></v:shape></span><!--[endif]-->', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">pernyataan Naro tepat sebagian, karena perubahan\r\nenergi kinetik rotasi juga disebabkan oleh momen inersia yang meningkat\r\nsehingga energi kinetik akhirnya 1/2 Ek&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">pernyataan Naro tidak tepat, karena kecepatan\r\nsudut berkurang disebabkan oleh momen inersia yang meningkat sehingga energi\r\nkinetik akhirnya 1/4 Ek&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">pernyataan Naro tidak tepat, karena kecepatan\r\nsudut berkurang disebabkan oleh momen inersia yang meningkat sehingga energi\r\nkinetik akhirnya 1/2 Ek&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">pernyataan Naro tepat, karena perubahan energi\r\nkinetik rotasi disebabkan oleh kecepatan sudut berkurang sehingga energi\r\nkinetik akhirnya 1/2 Ek&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">pernyataan Naro tepat sebagian, karena perubahan\r\nenergi kinetik rotasi juga disebabkan oleh momen inersia yang meningkat\r\nsehingga energi kinetik akhirnya 1/4 Ek&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 14.6667px;\">pernyataan Naro tepat sebagian, karena perubahan energi kinetik rotasi juga disebabkan oleh momen inersia yang meningkat sehingga energi kinetik akhirnya 1/2 Ek&nbsp;</span></p>', NULL, 'A', -2.591, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 13:02:00', '2026-05-03 16:30:08'),
(307, 'ACTofROD22', NULL, 17, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Perhatikan gambar berikut.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777762969_69f68299b5eb2.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: 177.367px; margin: 10px 0px; width: 355.104px;\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">Seorang teknisi sedang menguji dua jenis pintu dalam proyek\r\npembangunan mall. Kedua pintu memiliki massa dan ukuran yang sama. Pintu\r\npertama adalah pintu engsel dengan tuas di ujung pintu. Pintu kedua adalah\r\nsliding door dengan tuas di tengah pintu. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">Teknisi menjelaskan kepada kontraktor: “Kedua pintu sama mudahnya\r\nuntuk dibuka karena massa dan ukurannya identik. Posisi tuas tidak memengaruhi\r\nkemudahan membuka pintu pada kedua jenis pintu tersebut”<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">Penilaian\r\nyang paling tepat terhadap pernyataan tersebut adalah....</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">kedua pintu memiliki momen inersia yang sama\r\nsehingga sama mudahnya dibuka dengan gaya F yang sama&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">posisi tuas tidak relevan karena yang menentukan\r\nkemudahan membuka pintu hanyalah besar gaya F yang diberikan</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">sliding door lebih mudah dibuka karena tidak\r\nmemiliki momen inersia, sedangkan pintu engsel memiliki momen inersia yang besar&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">keduanya melibatkan rotasi sehingga posisi tuas\r\npada kedua pintu sama-sama memengaruhi torsi yang dihasilkan&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">pintu engsel bergerak rotasi sehingga kemudahan\r\nmembukanya ditentukan oleh torsi, sedangkan sliding door bergerak translasi\r\nsehingga kemudahannya ditentukan oleh gaya yang diberikan</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">pintu engsel bergerak rotasi sehingga kemudahan\r\nmembukanya ditentukan oleh torsi, sedangkan sliding door bergerak translasi\r\nsehingga kemudahannya ditentukan oleh gaya yang diberikan</span></p>', NULL, 'E', -0.620, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 13:04:17', '2026-05-03 16:30:27'),
(308, 'ACTofROD23', NULL, 17, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Perhatikan roda kemudi pada gambar 22. Dua gaya\r\nsama besar F bekerja pada tepi roda kemudi yang berjari-jari r. Gaya pertama\r\nbekerja ke atas di sisi kiri, dan gaya kedua bekerja ke bawah di sisi kanan\r\nroda.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777763157_69f68355972ac.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: 132.545px; margin: 10px 0px; width: 171.104px;\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">Pernyataan yang paling tepat berdasarkan\r\nberdasarkan kondisi tersebut adalah....</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Roda kemudi berada dalam kesetimbangan penuh\r\nkarena resultan gaya dan resultan torsi keduanya bernilai nol&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Roda kemudi tidak bergerak sama sekali karena\r\nkedua gaya berlawanan arah sehingga saling meniadakan&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Roda kemudi mengalami resultan gaya nol namun\r\nresultan torsi tidak nol sebesar 2FR, sehingga roda berotasi tanpa berpindah posisi&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Roda kemudi mengalami translasi karena resultan\r\ngaya dari kedua gaya tersebut tidak nol&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Roda kemudi hanya berotasi jika salah satu gaya\r\nlebih besar dari gaya yang lain&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Roda kemudi mengalami resultan gaya nol namun resultan torsi tidak nol sebesar 2FR, sehingga roda berotasi tanpa berpindah posisi&nbsp;</span></p>', NULL, 'C', -0.341, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 13:08:04', '2026-05-03 16:31:07');
INSERT INTO `soal_ujian` (`soal_id`, `kode_soal`, `ujian_id`, `bank_ujian_id`, `pertanyaan`, `pilihan_a`, `pilihan_b`, `pilihan_c`, `pilihan_d`, `pilihan_e`, `pembahasan`, `foto`, `jawaban_benar`, `tingkat_kesulitan`, `is_bank_soal`, `created_by`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(309, 'ACTofROD24', NULL, 17, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Gambar 23 menunjukkan grafik kecepatan sudut ω\r\nterhadap waktu t untuk sebuah benda yang diputar di sekitar sumbu rotasi.\r\nKecepatan sudut meningkat dari t = 0 hingga t = 3 s, lalu menurun hingga\r\nberhenti pada t = 6 s. Torsi bernilai positif jika putarannya searah jarum jam.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777763325_69f683fdab916.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: 119.027px; margin: 10px 0px; width: 345.104px;\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV\">Gambar 23. Grafik kecepatan sudut terhadap\r\nwaktu</span></p><p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<strong><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;\r\nmso-bidi-language:AR-SA;font-weight:normal\">Berdasarkan grafik tersebut,\r\npernyataan yang paling tepat mengenai torsi yang bekerja pada benda adalah....</span></strong></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">torsi bernilai positif dari t = 0 hingga t = 3 s\r\nkarena ω meningkat, dan torsi bernilai negatif dari t = 3 hingga 6 s karena ω\r\nmenurun</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">torsi bernilai negatif dari t = 0 hingga t = 3 s\r\nkarena ω meningkat, dan torsi bernilai positif dari t = 3 hingga 6 s karena ω\r\nmenurun</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">torsi tetap bernilai positif karena nilai ω\r\nberkisar pada angka positif&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"NO-BOK\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:NO-BOK;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">torsi tetap bernilai positif karena tidak\r\ndipengaruhi oleh&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 11pt;\">ω</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">torsi bernilai negatif karena berlawanan arah\r\ndengan&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 11pt;\">ω</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 14.6667px;\">torsi bernilai positif dari t = 0 hingga t = 3 s karena ω meningkat, dan torsi bernilai negatif dari t = 3 hingga 6 s karena ω menurun</span></p>', NULL, 'A', 2.180, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 13:10:20', '2026-05-03 16:31:26'),
(310, 'ACTofROD25', NULL, 17, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Seorang atlet senam turun dari gerakan di mana\r\nia berayun di atas palang tinggi. Atlet senam berputar di udara sebelum\r\nmendarat. Gambar &nbsp;24 menunjukkan atlet\r\nsenam dalam tiga posisi selama proses turun.</span></p><ul><li><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777763501_69f684ad6b232.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: 195.709px; margin: 10px 0px; width: 297.104px;\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">Posisi 1, atlet senam baru melepaskan\r\npegangannya dari palang. Tubuhnya dalam posisi terentang sepenuhnya</span></span></li><li><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">Posisi 2, atlet senam berputar beberapa saat\r\nkemudian. Lututnya telah didekatkan ke dada dalam posisi meringkuk</span></span></span></li><li><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">Posisi 3, berada di akhir gerakan pendaratan\r\nsaat pesenam mendarat di matras. Tubuhnya kembali berdiri sepenuhnya</span></span></span></span></li></ul><p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">Mengapa momen inersia terhadap sumbu rotasi\r\nberkurang ketika lututnya di gerakan ke arah dada dan pengaruh terhadap\r\nkecepatan sudut adalah....</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">momen inersia berkurang karena tinggi pesenam\r\nterhadap sumbu rotasi berkurang sehingga kecepatan sudut mengalami peningkatan</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">momen inersia berkurang karena distribusi&nbsp; masa pesenam berada lebih dekat ke sumbu\r\nrotasi sehingga kecepatan sudut mengalami peningkatan&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">momen inersia berkurang karena tinggi pesenam\r\nterhadap sumbu rotasi berkurang dan distribusi massa lebih dekat ke sumbu\r\nrotasi sehingga kecepatan sudut mengalami penurunan&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">momen inersia berkurang karena tinggi pesenam\r\nterhadap sumbu rotasi berkurang dan distribusi massa lebih dekat ke sumbu\r\nrotasi sehingga kecepatan sudut mengalami peningkatan&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">momen inersia berkurang karena tinggi pesenam\r\nterhadap sumbu rotasi berkurang dan distribusi massa lebih dekat ke sumbu\r\nrotasi sehingga kecepatan sudut tetap sama karena tidak ada torsi eksternal</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">momen inersia berkurang karena tinggi pesenam terhadap sumbu rotasi berkurang dan distribusi massa lebih dekat ke sumbu rotasi sehingga kecepatan sudut mengalami peningkatan&nbsp;</span></p>', NULL, 'D', 0.310, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 13:16:00', '2026-05-03 16:31:49'),
(311, 'ACTofROD26', NULL, 17, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Perhatikan gambar 25 menunjukkan baling-baling\r\ndipasang di tengah meja putar.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777763830_69f685f61b5fb.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: 132.967px; margin: 10px 0px; width: 333.896px;\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">Gambar 25. Baling-baling pada meja putar<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">Baling-baling\r\ndan meja putar memiliki sumbu rotasi yang sama dan digerakkan oleh motor\r\nbaterai. Awalnya dalam keadaan diam, kemudian motor dihidupkan dan\r\nbaling-baling dengan cepat berputar mencapai kecepatan sudut akhir yang tinggi\r\ndan berputar searah jarum jam jika dilihat dari atas. Dengan menggunakan konsep\r\nkekekalan momentum sudut, gerakan meja putar dibandingkan dengan baling-baling\r\nadalah....</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">meja putar berputar searah jarum jam, sama\r\nseperti baling-baling, karena keduanya memiliki satu sumber motor yang sama</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">meja putar tidak bergerak karena motor hanya\r\nmemberikan torsi pada baling-baling, bukan pada meja putar</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">meja putar berputar berlawanan arah jarum jam\r\nkarena momentum sudut total sistem harus tetap nol</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">meja putar akan berputar acak tergantung besar\r\ngesekan bantalan, tidak terkait arah baling-baling</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">meja putar hanya bergoyang tanpa rotasi karena\r\nmotor tidak menempel pada meja putar</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">meja putar berputar berlawanan arah jarum jam\r\nkarena momentum sudut total sistem harus tetap nol</span></p>', NULL, 'C', 0.180, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 13:18:20', '2026-05-03 16:07:05'),
(312, 'ACTofROD27', NULL, 17, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Perhatikan gambar 26 yaitu sebuah mesin cetak\r\nlogam. Jarak dari sumbu rotasi ke pusat setiap bola adalah y. Jari-jari setiap\r\nbola adalah R.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777763944_69f6866801aa3.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: 192.228px; margin: 10px 0px; width: 341.896px;\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">Gambar 26. Mesin cetak logam</span></p><p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">Energi\r\nyang tersimpan dalam sistem berasal dari energi kinetik rotasi bola E<sub>k</sub>=1/2 I</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">ω<sup>2</sup></span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">&nbsp;dengan momen inersia bola pejal 2/5 mR<sup>2</sup>+my<sup>2</sup></span><span lang=\"IN\" style