(314, 'ACTofROD29', NULL, 17, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Gambar &nbsp;27\r\nmenunjukkan satelit dengan tiga panel surya yang dilipat dekat badan satelit\r\nyang digunakan untuk perjalanan ke luar angkasa. Setelah dilepaskan, panel\r\nsurya direntangkan untuk mendapat pasokan energi dari cahaya matahari. Sebelum\r\npanel surya di rentangkan, momen inersia satelit terhadap sumbunya adalah 110 kg.m<sup>2</sup></span><!--[if gte msEquation 12]><m:oMath><i\r\n style=\'mso-bidi-font-style:normal\'><span lang=IN style=\'font-size:12.0pt;\r\n line-height:107%;font-family:\"Cambria Math\",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\n mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;\r\n mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\'><m:r>kg</m:r></span></i><m:sSup><m:sSupPr><span\r\n   style=\'font-size:12.0pt;mso-ansi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;\r\n   font-family:\"Cambria Math\",serif;mso-ascii-font-family:\"Cambria Math\";\r\n   mso-hansi-font-family:\"Cambria Math\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\n   mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;font-style:italic;mso-bidi-font-style:normal\'><m:ctrlPr></m:ctrlPr></span></m:sSupPr><m:e><i\r\n   style=\'mso-bidi-font-style:normal\'><span lang=IN style=\'font-size:12.0pt;\r\n   line-height:107%;font-family:\"Cambria Math\",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n   Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\n   mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\n   EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\'><m:r> </m:r><m:r>m</m:r></span></i></m:e><m:sup><i\r\n   style=\'mso-bidi-font-style:normal\'><span lang=IN style=\'font-size:12.0pt;\r\n   line-height:107%;font-family:\"Cambria Math\",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n   Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\n   mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\n   EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\'><m:r>2</m:r></span></i></m:sup></m:sSup></m:oMath><![endif]--><!--[if !msEquation]--><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;position:relative;top:3.5pt;mso-text-raise:-3.5pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><v:shapetype id=\"_x0000_t75\" coordsize=\"21600,21600\" o:spt=\"75\" o:preferrelative=\"t\" path=\"m@4@5l@4@11@9@11@9@5xe\" filled=\"f\" stroked=\"f\"><v:stroke joinstyle=\"miter\"><v:formulas><v:f eqn=\"if lineDrawn pixelLineWidth 0\"><v:f eqn=\"sum @0 1 0\"><v:f eqn=\"sum 0 0 @1\"><v:f eqn=\"prod @2 1 2\"><v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelWidth\"><v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelHeight\"><v:f eqn=\"sum @0 0 1\"><v:f eqn=\"prod @6 1 2\"><v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelWidth\"><v:f eqn=\"sum @8 21600 0\"><v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelHeight\"><v:f eqn=\"sum @10 21600 0\"></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:formulas><v:path o:extrusionok=\"f\" gradientshapeok=\"t\" o:connecttype=\"rect\"><o:lock v:ext=\"edit\" aspectratio=\"t\"></o:lock></v:path></v:stroke></v:shapetype><v:shape id=\"_x0000_i1025\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style=\"width:32.5pt;\r\n height:15.5pt\"><v:imagedata src=\"file:///C:/Users/Lenovo/AppData/Local/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_image001.png\" o:title=\"\" chromakey=\"white\"></v:imagedata></v:shape></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">. Sedangkan momen inersia satelit terhadap\r\nsumbunya setelah panel surya direntangkan adalah 230 kg.m<sup>2</sup>.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777764488_69f68888214e8.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: 142.459px; margin: 10px 0px; width: 307.896px;\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">Alasan yang paling tepat mengapa merentangkan\r\npanel surya dapat meningkatkan momen inersia satelit adalah....</span></span><!--[if gte msEquation 12]><m:oMath><i\r\n style=\'mso-bidi-font-style:normal\'><span lang=IN style=\'font-size:12.0pt;\r\n line-height:107%;font-family:\"Cambria Math\",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\n mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;\r\n mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\'><m:r>kg</m:r></span></i><m:sSup><m:sSupPr><span\r\n   style=\'font-size:12.0pt;mso-ansi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;\r\n   font-family:\"Cambria Math\",serif;mso-ascii-font-family:\"Cambria Math\";\r\n   mso-hansi-font-family:\"Cambria Math\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\n   mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;font-style:italic;mso-bidi-font-style:normal\'><m:ctrlPr></m:ctrlPr></span></m:sSupPr><m:e><i\r\n   style=\'mso-bidi-font-style:normal\'><span lang=IN style=\'font-size:12.0pt;\r\n   line-height:107%;font-family:\"Cambria Math\",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n   Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\n   mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\n   EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\'><m:r> </m:r><m:r>m</m:r></span></i></m:e><m:sup><i\r\n   style=\'mso-bidi-font-style:normal\'><span lang=IN style=\'font-size:12.0pt;\r\n   line-height:107%;font-family:\"Cambria Math\",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n   Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\n   mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\n   EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\'><m:r>2</m:r></span></i></m:sup></m:sSup></m:oMath><![endif]--><!--[if !msEquation]--><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;position:relative;top:3.5pt;mso-text-raise:-3.5pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><v:shape id=\"_x0000_i1025\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style=\"width:32.5pt;height:15.5pt\"><v:imagedata src=\"file:///C:/Users/Lenovo/AppData/Local/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_image001.png\" o:title=\"\" chromakey=\"white\"></v:imagedata></v:shape></span><!--[endif]--></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">karena saat panel direntangkan, distribusi massa\r\nberpusat di ujung sumbu rotasi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">karena saat panel direntangkan, jarak panel\r\ndengan sumbu rotasi semakin jauh</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">karena saat panel direntangkan, distribusi massa\r\nberpusat di sumbu rotasi dan jarak panel dengan sumbu rotasi semakin jauh</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">karena saat panel direntangkan, distribusi massa\r\nberpusat di ujung sumbu rotasi dan jarak panel dengan sumbu rotasi semakin jauh</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">karena saat panel direntangkan, distribusi massa\r\ntersebar merata pada ujung dan sumbu rotasi, serta jarak panel dengan sumbu\r\nrotasi semakin jauh</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">karena saat panel direntangkan, distribusi massa\r\nberpusat di ujung sumbu rotasi dan jarak panel dengan sumbu rotasi semakin jauh</span></p>', NULL, 'D', 1.099, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 13:29:29', '2026-05-03 16:34:42'),
(315, 'ACTofROD30', NULL, 17, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Gambar 28 berikut menunjukkan atlet senam sedang\r\nlatihan salto.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777764636_69f6891c39713.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: 248.281px; margin: 10px 0px; width: 376.916px;\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">Gambar 28. Atlet senam sedang salto dengan beberapa posisi berbeda<o:p></o:p></span></p><ul><li><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%;\">Posisi\r\n1, atlet senam baru saja melepaskan pegangannya dari palang. Tubuhnya dalam\r\nposisi terentang sepenuhnya.</span></span></li><li><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%;\">Posisi 2, atlet senam berputar beberapa saat.\r\nLututnya telah didekatkan ke dada dalam posisi meringkuk</span></span></span></li><li><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%;\">Posisi 3, pendaratan pesenam di matras. Tubuhnya\r\nkembali berdiri sepenuhnya</span></span></span></span></li></ul><p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%;\">Pesenam ingin menyelesaikan lebih banyak putaran\r\nsebelum mendarat. Tindakan yang dapat dilakukan pesenam selama gerakan udara\r\nuntuk meningkatkan jumlah putarannya adalah....</span></span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Menarik tubuh lebih rapat saat diudara&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Meluruskan tubuh saat diudara</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Merentangkan kedua tangan saat diudara&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Merentangkan satu kaki dan satu tangan saat diudara&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Merentangkan kedua kaki saat diudara</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 14.6667px;\">Menarik tubuh lebih rapat saat diudara&nbsp;</span></p>', NULL, 'A', 1.250, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 13:32:55', '2026-05-03 16:35:07'),
(316, 'ACTofROD31', NULL, 17, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Bagian mesin cetak logam yaitu baut, piston\r\ntekan, dan lengan memiliki massa total yang sama dengan massa total dua bola\r\nbaja.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777764810_69f689caeea12.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: 179.615px; margin: 10px 0px; width: 319.462px;\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">Gambar 29. Mesin cetak logam</span></p><p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">Momen\r\ninersia gabungan baut, piston tekan, dan lengan nilainya lebih kecil dibanding\r\nmomen inersia gabungan dua bola baja. Mengapa momen inersia baut, piston tekan,\r\ndan lengan terhadap sumbu rotasi jauh lebih kecil daripada momen inersia bola\r\nbaja terhadap sumbu rotasi yang sama adalah....</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">momen inersia baut, piston tekan, dan lengan\r\nlebih kecil karena sebagian besar massanya berada dekat sumbu rotasi sehingga\r\nkontribusi momen inersianya jauh lebih kecil</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">momen inersia baut, piston tekan, dan lengan\r\nlebih kecil karena ukurannya lebih kecil dari bola baja, sehingga momen\r\ninersianya tidak sebesar bola baja</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">momen inersia baut, piston tekan, dan lengan\r\nlebih kecil karena jaraknya ke sumbu rotasi lebih jauh dibanding bola baja</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">momen inersia baut, piston tekan, dan lengan\r\nlebih kecil karena jaraknya ke sumbu rotasi lebih dekat dibanding bola baja</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">momen inersia baut, </span><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">piston\r\ntekan</span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;\r\nmso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">, dan lengan lebih kecil karena massanya berpusat di\r\nujung sumbu rotasi</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 14.6667px;\">momen inersia baut, piston tekan, dan lengan lebih kecil karena sebagian besar massanya berada dekat sumbu rotasi sehingga kontribusi momen inersianya jauh lebih kecil</span></p>', NULL, 'A', -2.590, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 13:34:59', '2026-05-03 16:35:33'),
(317, 'ACTofROD32', NULL, 17, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Sebuah roda sepeda bermassa M dan berjari-jari R\r\ndipasang pada poros. Massa roda dianggap terkonsentrasi di tepinya (seperti\r\ncincin tipis). Awalnya roda dalam keadaan diam. Sebuah anak panah bermassa m</span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">c</span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">\r\ndilemparkan secara horizontal dengan kecepatan v</span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">c</span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"> dan\r\nmenancap pada tepi roda pada sudut&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">θ</span><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); font-size: 14px;\"><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\">.</font></span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777764979_69f68a73782f3.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: 163.615px; margin: 10px 0px; width: 350.142px;\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">Gambar 30. Roda sepeda yang ditembak anak\r\npanah<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Setelah\r\nanak panah menancap, roda berputar dengan kecepatan sudut tertentu. Pernyataan\r\nyang paling tepat untuk menentukan kecepatan sudut akhir sistem adalah....</span><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); font-size: 14px;\"><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\"></font></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">kecepatan sudut akhir ditentukan dari kekekalan\r\nmomentum sudut sistem karena tidak ada gaya luar yang bekerja pada sistem</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">kecepatan sudut akhir ditentukan dengan\r\nmenggunakan kekekalan energi mekanik karena tidak ada gaya luar yang bekerja\r\npada sistem selama tumbukan</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">kecepatan sudut akhir ditentukan dengan\r\nmenggunakan kekekalan momentum sudut terhadap sumbu rotasi, karena tidak ada\r\ntorsi eksternal terhadap sumbu rotasi selama tumbukan berlangsung</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">kecepatan sudut akhir ditentukan dengan\r\nmenggunakan kekekalan momentum sudut dan energi kinetik secara bersamaan karena\r\nsistem tidak mengalami gesekan pada sumbu rotasi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">kecepatan sudut akhir ditentukan dengan\r\nmenggunakan kekekalan momentum sudut terhadap sumbu rotasi, karena terdapat\r\ntorsi eksternal pada sumbu rotasi selama tumbukan berlangsung</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">kecepatan sudut akhir ditentukan dengan\r\nmenggunakan kekekalan momentum sudut terhadap sumbu rotasi, karena tidak ada\r\ntorsi eksternal terhadap sumbu rotasi selama tumbukan berlangsung</span></p>', NULL, 'C', -0.621, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 13:37:41', '2026-05-03 16:36:07'),
(318, 'ACTofROD33', NULL, 17, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Sebuah helikopter penyelamat yang memiliki empat\r\nbaling-baling dengan panjang L dan massa M. Baling-baling tersebut berbentuk\r\nbatang tipis yang berputar pada sumbu rotasi yang tegak lurus terhadap\r\npanjangnya. Helikopter bergerak dengan kecepatan sudut&nbsp;</span><!--[if gte msEquation 12]><m:oMath><i\r\n style=\'mso-bidi-font-style:normal\'><span lang=IN style=\'font-size:11.0pt;\r\n line-height:107%;font-family:\"Cambria Math\",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\n mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;\r\n mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\'><m:r>ω</m:r></span></i></m:oMath><![endif]--><!--[if !msEquation]--><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;position:relative;top:3.5pt;mso-text-raise:-3.5pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><v:shapetype id=\"_x0000_t75\" coordsize=\"21600,21600\" o:spt=\"75\" o:preferrelative=\"t\" path=\"m@4@5l@4@11@9@11@9@5xe\" filled=\"f\" stroked=\"f\"><v:stroke joinstyle=\"miter\"><v:formulas><v:f eqn=\"if lineDrawn pixelLineWidth 0\"><v:f eqn=\"sum @0 1 0\"><v:f eqn=\"sum 0 0 @1\"><v:f eqn=\"prod @2 1 2\"><v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelWidth\"><v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelHeight\"><v:f eqn=\"sum @0 0 1\"><v:f eqn=\"prod @6 1 2\"><v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelWidth\"><v:f eqn=\"sum @8 21600 0\"><v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelHeight\"><v:f eqn=\"sum @10 21600 0\"></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:formulas><v:path o:extrusionok=\"f\" gradientshapeok=\"t\" o:connecttype=\"rect\"><o:lock v:ext=\"edit\" aspectratio=\"t\"></o:lock></v:path></v:stroke></v:shapetype><v:shape id=\"_x0000_i1025\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style=\"width:8pt;\r\n height:14pt\"><v:imagedata src=\"file:///C:/Users/Lenovo/AppData/Local/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_image001.png\" o:title=\"\" chromakey=\"white\"></v:imagedata></v:shape></span><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">ω.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777765129_69f68b0974578.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: 171.948px; margin: 10px 0px; width: 446.061px;\"></p><p class=\"Default\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nIN\">Gambar 31. Dua helikopter dengan panjang baling-baling berbeda<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Jika\r\npanjang setiap baling-baling helikopter diperbesar menjadi dua kali lipat,\r\nsementara massa tiap bilah dan kecepatan sudut tetap, maka perubahan energi\r\nkinetik rotasi total sistem adalah....</span><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"></span><!--[endif]--></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">energi kinetik rotasi menjadi dua kali lipat\r\nkarena berbanding lurus dengan panjang baling-baling</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">e</span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">nergi kinetik rotasi menjadi empat kali lipat\r\nkarena memiliki hubungan kuadratik dengan panjang baling-baling</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">energi kinetik rotasi menjadi setengahnya karena\r\nberbanding terbalik dengan panjang baling-baling</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">energi kinetik rotasi menjadi satu per empatnya\r\nkarena memiliki hubungan akar kuadrat dengan panjang baling-baling</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">energi kinetik rotasi tetap karena panjang\r\nbaling-baling tidak memengaruhi&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 15.6933px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">e</span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 15.6933px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">nergi kinetik rotasi menjadi empat kali lipat karena memiliki hubungan kuadratik dengan panjang baling-baling</span></p>', NULL, 'B', -0.340, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 13:40:14', '2026-05-03 16:36:41'),
(319, 'ACTofROD34', NULL, 17, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Perhatikan sebuah batang tipis seragam bermassa\r\nM dan panjang l seperti yang ditunjukkan pada gambar 32.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777765249_69f68b810384c.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: 281.615px; margin: 10px 0px; width: 287.461px;\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">Gambar 32. Batang tipis seragam yang direkatkan pada lingkaran\r\ntipis</span></p><p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%;\">Batang\r\ntersebut direkatkan ke sebuah lingkaran tipis bermassa M dan jari-jari l/2\r\nuntuk membentuk sistem kaku. Pusat batang dan lingkaran berimpit di titik P. </span><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%;\">Sistem\r\nmengalami dua perubahan secara terpisah:</span></span></p><ul><li><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%;\">Panjang batang l diperbesar 2 kali lipat (R\r\ntetap)</span></span></span></li><li><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%;\">Jari-jari lingkaran R diperbesar 2 kali lipat (l\r\ntetap)</span></span></span></span></li></ul><p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%;\">Pernyataan yang paling tetap untuk menentukan\r\npengaruh perubahan variabel tersebut terhadap momen inersia total sistem adalah....</span></span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">perubahan l dan R memberikan pengaruh yang sama\r\nbesar terhadap momen inersia total karena keduanya muncul dalam bentuk kuadrat</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">perubahan l memberikan pengaruh lebih besar\r\nkarena momen inersia batang lebih besar dibanding momen inersia lingkaran</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">perubahan R memberikan pengaruh lebih besar\r\nkarena momen inersia lingkaran lebih besar dibanding momen inersia batang</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">perubahan l memberikan pengaruh lebih besar\r\nkarena momen inersia lingkaran lebih besar dibanding momen inersia batang</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">perubahan R memberikan pengaruh lebih besar\r\nkarena momen inersia batang lebih besar dibanding momen inersia lingkaran</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">perubahan R memberikan pengaruh lebih besar\r\nkarena momen inersia lingkaran lebih besar dibanding momen inersia batang</span></p>', NULL, 'C', 2.180, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 13:42:49', '2026-05-03 16:37:01'),
(320, 'ACtofROD35', NULL, 17, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Gambar 33 menunjukkan sebuah yoyo yang terdiri\r\ndari dua cakram yang dipisahkan oleh poros silinder. Tali tipis dililit erat di\r\nsekitar poros.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777765430_69f68c3624911.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: 261.615px; margin: 10px 0px; width: 286.336px;\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">Gambar 33. Tampilan yoyo</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:0cm;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\">Awalnya, ujung\r\nbebas tali A dan yoyo ditahan dalam keadaan diam. Dengan ujung A tetap diam,\r\nyoyo dilepaskan sehingga jatuh secara vertikal. Saat yoyo jatuh, lilitan tali\r\npada poros bernilai minimal sehingga yoyo berputar di tengah.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">Mengapa\r\nyoyo bisa terus berputar konstan di tengah ketika lilitan tali pada porosnya\r\nbernilai minimal adalah....</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">karena gravitasi menyebabkan salah satu sisi\r\nporos berputar lebih dulu</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">karena lilitan tali memberikan torsi yang\r\nmenghasilkan percepatan sudut</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">karena momen inersia yoyo sangat kecil sehingga\r\nberputar otomatis</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">karena lilitan tali mengurangi gaya gesek udara\r\nsehingga rotasi menjadi dominan</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">karena energi potensial langsung berubah menjadi\r\nenergi rotasi tanpa pengaruh gaya lain</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">karena lilitan tali memberikan torsi yang menghasilkan percepatan sudut</span></p>', NULL, 'B', 0.310, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 13:45:29', '2026-05-03 16:38:04');
INSERT INTO `soal_ujian` (`soal_id`, `kode_soal`, `ujian_id`, `bank_ujian_id`, `pertanyaan`, `pilihan_a`, `pilihan_b`, `pilihan_c`, `pilihan_d`, `pilihan_e`, `pembahasan`, `foto`, `jawaban_benar`, `tingkat_kesulitan`, `is_bank_soal`, `created_by`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(321, 'ACTofROD36', NULL, 17, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Mesin cetak logam yang ditunjukkan gambar 34\r\ndigunakan oleh seorang perajin perhiasan untuk mencetak bentuk dari lembaran\r\nlogam tipis.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777765579_69f68ccbeb1cf.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: 221.948px; margin: 10px 0px; width: 394.756px;\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">Gambar 34. Mesin cetak logam<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">Sumber: physicsandmathstutor.com<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:0cm;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\">Ketika piston\r\ntekan mencapai lembaran logam, kecepatan rotasi lengan adalah 2,9 putaran per\r\ndetik. Pada kecepatan ini, energi kinetik rotasi lengan, baut, piston tekan,\r\ndan bola baja adalah 10,3 J dan dua bola baja menghasilkan sebagian besar momen\r\ninersia.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">Kesimpulan\r\nyang paling tepat mengenai distribusi massa sistem adalah....</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">massa lengan dan baut terdistribusi dekat ke\r\nsumbu rotasi&nbsp; sehingga hanya memberi kontribusi kecil pada momen inersia</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">massa bola baja terdistribusi dekat sumbu\r\nrotasi&nbsp; sehingga hampir tidak memengaruhi momen inersia</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">semua bagian sistem memiliki momen inersia sama\r\nkarena massanya sama</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">sistem memiliki momen inersia kecil karena\r\nkecepatan sudutnya tinggi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">momen inersia bola lebih besar karena memiliki\r\ndua buah</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">massa lengan dan baut terdistribusi dekat ke\r\nsumbu rotasi&nbsp; sehingga hanya memberi kontribusi kecil pada momen inersia</span></p>', NULL, 'A', -0.941, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 13:47:27', '2026-05-03 16:38:27'),
(322, 'ACTofROD37', NULL, 17, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Sebuah yoyo terus jatuh hingga seluruh tali\r\nhabis. Yoyo kemudian berputar konstan. Ini berarti yoyo terus berputar dalam\r\nlingkaran tali yang longgar seperti yang ditunjukkan pada gambar 35.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777765696_69f68d4010eb0.png\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: 254.948px; margin: 10px 0px; width: 167.236px;\" class=\"img-fluid\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">Pada tahap ini, kecepatan sudut yoyo menjadi\r\nkonstan. Berdasarkan informasi tersebut, kesimpulan yang paling tepat mengenai\r\ngaya dan torsi yang bekerja pada yoyo adalah....</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">kecepatan sudut yoyo konstan karena gaya\r\ngravitasi memberi torsi yang seimbang dengan gaya gesekan udara</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">kecepatan sudut yoyo konstan karena tidak ada\r\nlagi torsi bersih yang bekerja setelah tali menjadi longgar</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">kecepatan sudut yoyo konstan karena tegangan\r\ntali meningkat ketika tali menjadi longgar</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">kecepatan sudut yoyo konstan karena gaya\r\nsentripetal dari tali menggantikan torsi gravitasi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">kecepatan sudut yoyo konstan karena gaya gesekan\r\nudara menjadi nol saat tali habis</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">kecepatan sudut yoyo konstan karena tidak ada\r\nlagi torsi bersih yang bekerja setelah tali menjadi longgar</span></p>', NULL, 'B', -1.550, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 13:49:32', '2026-05-03 16:38:57'),
(323, 'ACTofROD38', NULL, 17, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Perhatikan gambar 36 berikut.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777765872_69f68df02b7be.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: 137.948px; margin: 10px 0px; width: 258.314px;\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">Gambar 36. Katrol cakram yang dipasang beban<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">Sebuah\r\nkatrol cakram padat bermassa M dan jari-jari R ditopang oleh bantalan yang\r\nmemiliki gesekan yang dapat diabaikan. Seutas tali dengan massa diabaikan\r\ndililitkan sekeliling katrol. Beban dengan massa 0,5 M diikat pada ujung tali.\r\nMomen inersia katrol terhadap sumbu rotasi adalah 0,5 MR<sup>2</sup></span><!--[if gte msEquation 12]><m:oMath><i\r\n style=\'mso-bidi-font-style:normal\'><span lang=IN style=\'font-size:12.0pt;\r\n line-height:107%;font-family:\"Cambria Math\",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\n mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;\r\n mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\'><m:r>M</m:r></span></i><m:sSup><m:sSupPr><span\r\n   style=\'font-size:12.0pt;mso-ansi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;\r\n   font-family:\"Cambria Math\",serif;mso-ascii-font-family:\"Cambria Math\";\r\n   mso-hansi-font-family:\"Cambria Math\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\n   mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;font-style:italic;mso-bidi-font-style:normal\'><m:ctrlPr></m:ctrlPr></span></m:sSupPr><m:e><i\r\n   style=\'mso-bidi-font-style:normal\'><span lang=IN style=\'font-size:12.0pt;\r\n   line-height:107%;font-family:\"Cambria Math\",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n   Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\n   mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\n   EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\'><m:r>R</m:r></span></i></m:e><m:sup><i\r\n   style=\'mso-bidi-font-style:normal\'><span lang=IN style=\'font-size:12.0pt;\r\n   line-height:107%;font-family:\"Cambria Math\",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n   Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\n   mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\n   EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\'><m:r>2</m:r></span></i></m:sup></m:sSup></m:oMath><![endif]--><!--[if !msEquation]--><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;position:relative;top:3.5pt;mso-text-raise:-3.5pt;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><v:shapetype id=\"_x0000_t75\" coordsize=\"21600,21600\" o:spt=\"75\" o:preferrelative=\"t\"