IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">percepatan beban lebih kecil dari g</span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 15.6933px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; position: relative; top: 3.5pt;\"><v:shapetype id=\"_x0000_t75\" coordsize=\"21600,21600\" o:spt=\"75\" o:preferrelative=\"t\" path=\"m@4@5l@4@11@9@11@9@5xe\" filled=\"f\" stroked=\"f\"><v:stroke joinstyle=\"miter\"><v:formulas><v:f eqn=\"if lineDrawn pixelLineWidth 0\"><v:f eqn=\"sum @0 1 0\"><v:f eqn=\"sum 0 0 @1\"><v:f eqn=\"prod @2 1 2\"><v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelWidth\"><v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelHeight\"><v:f eqn=\"sum @0 0 1\"><v:f eqn=\"prod @6 1 2\"><v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelWidth\"><v:f eqn=\"sum @8 21600 0\"><v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelHeight\"><v:f eqn=\"sum @10 21600 0\"></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:formulas><v:path o:extrusionok=\"f\" gradientshapeok=\"t\" o:connecttype=\"rect\"><o:lock v:ext=\"edit\" aspectratio=\"t\"></o:lock></v:path></v:stroke></v:shapetype><v:shape id=\"_x0000_i1025\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style=\"width: 7.5pt; height: 15pt;\"><v:imagedata src=\"file:///C:/Users/Lenovo/AppData/Local/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_image001.png\" o:title=\"\" chromakey=\"white\"></v:imagedata></v:shape></span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">karena sebagian gaya digunakan untuk memutar katrol</span></p>', NULL, 'A', -0.202, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 13:53:51', '2026-05-03 16:39:47'),
(324, 'ACTofROD39', NULL, 17, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Pada suatu hari, Rahmat melakukan beberapa\r\nkegiatan berikut.</span></p><p><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\">(i) mengayuh sepeda</font></p><p><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\">(ii) bermain jungkat jungkit dengan temannya</font></p><p><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\">(iii) mendorong meja pada bidang datar yang licin</font></p><p><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\">(iv) mendorong gerobak sampah</font></p><p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Rahmat menyadari bahwa tidak semua kegiatan\r\ntersebut melibatkan kecenderungan benda untuk berotasi terhadap suatu titik\r\natau sumbu tertentu, meskipun sama-sama melibatkan gaya. Kombinasi kegiatan\r\nyang benar-benar merupakan penerapan torsi, beserta alasan yang paling tepat\r\nadalah....</span><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\"></font></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">i dan ii, karena gaya selalu bekerja pada benda\r\nyang bergerak</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">i dan iv, karena penggunaan tali selalu\r\nmenghasilkan torsi&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">ii dan iii, karena gaya digunakan untuk\r\nmemindahkan benda berat&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">iii dan iv, karena torsi berkaitan langsung\r\ndengan besar momentum benda&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">ii dan i, karena gaya bekerja pada jarak\r\ntertentu dari titik tumpu sehingga menimbulkan rotasi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">ii dan i, karena gaya bekerja pada jarak\r\ntertentu dari titik tumpu sehingga menimbulkan rotasi</span></p>', NULL, 'E', 1.400, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 13:56:39', '2026-05-03 16:40:21'),
(325, 'ACTofROD40', NULL, 17, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Gambar 37 menunjukkan piringan putar dengan\r\nsepotong kecil permen karet yang digantung di atasnya. Sensor optik yang\r\nterhubung ke perekam data mengukur kecepatan sudut piringan putar.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777766246_69f68f66626bb.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: 113.281px; margin: 10px 0px; width: 288.756px;\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">Gambar 37. Piringan putar<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"Default\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nIN\">Piringan dirancang untuk berputar terlebih dahulu sebelum berputar bebas.\r\nGumpalan permen karet dijatuhkan dari ketinggian kecil di atas piringan dan\r\nmenempel padanya.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"Default\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\">Piringan putar berbentuk cakram padat dengan momen inersia I = 12MR²<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"Default\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\">Permen karet adalah bola padat dengan momen inersia I = 25MR²<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%;\">Berdasarkan\r\ninformasi eksperimen, untuk menentukan besar perubahan energi kinetik rotasi </span><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%;\">piringan\r\nputar dari saat sebelum permen karet dijatuhkan hingga segera setelah menempel\r\npada piringan putar adalah....</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">perubahan energi kinetik rotasi hanya ditentukan\r\noleh perubahan kecepatan sudut karena momen inersia seluruh sistem tetap</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">perubahan energi kinetik rotasi ditentukan oleh\r\nperubahan momen inersia sistem dan perubahan kecepatan sudut, karena tumbukan\r\ninelastik menambah massa pada radius tertentu</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">perubahan energi kinetik rotasi hanya\r\ndipengaruhi oleh massa permen karet karena permen karet menyebabkan gaya ke\r\nbawah yang memperlambat rotasi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">perubahan energi kinetik rotasi terutama\r\ndipengaruhi oleh energi potensial permen karet saat jatuh karena energi itu\r\nhilang dari sistem rotasi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">perubahan energi kinetik rotasi ditentukan oleh\r\nbesar gaya gesekan udara yang bekerja tepat saat permen karet menempel pada\r\npiringan</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">perubahan energi kinetik rotasi terutama\r\ndipengaruhi oleh energi potensial permen karet saat jatuh karena energi itu\r\nhilang dari sistem rotasi</span></p>', NULL, 'D', -0.481, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 13:58:39', '2026-05-03 16:40:45'),
(326, 'ACTofROD41', NULL, 17, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Mesin jahit tradisional menggunakan roda untuk\r\nmenghasilkan gerakan, bahkan ketika pedal tidak ditekan. Saat berputar, torsi\r\nmasukan diubah menjadi energi kinetik rotasi yang disimpan dalam roda.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777767188_69f693140ee62.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: 172.615px; margin: 10px 0px; width: 203.462px;\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">Gambar 38. Mesin jahit tradisional</span></p><p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%;\">Bentuk\r\nroda yang sering digunakan adalah cincin (I=mr²) daripada yang berbentuk\r\npiringan (I=12mr²). Mengapa roda berbentuk cincin lebih disukai daripada roda\r\nberbentuk piringan adalah....</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">roda berbentuk cincin lebih disukai karena\r\nseluruh massanya berada pada jarak yang lebih besar dari sumbu rotasi, sehingga\r\nmomen inersia maksimum dapat dicapai untuk menghasilkan&nbsp; energi kinetik rotasi lebih besar</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">roda berbentuk cincin lebih disukai karena massa\r\nyang lebih jauh dari sumbu rotasi membuat gaya gesekan menjadi lebih kecil\r\nsehingga putaran lebih stabil</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">roda berbentuk cincin lebih disukai karena\r\nbentuk cincin memungkinkan energi kinetik rotasi berubah langsung menjadi torsi\r\ntanpa perubahan kecepatan</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">roda berbentuk cincin lebih disukai karena massa\r\nyang tersebar merata membuat perubahan energi kinetik rotasi menjadi lebih\r\ncepat saat pedal ditekan</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">roda berbentuk cincin lebih disukai karena massa\r\nyang lebih jauh menyebabkan torsi luar yang bekerja mengecil sehingga mesin\r\nlebih mudah berputar</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">roda berbentuk cincin lebih disukai karena\r\nseluruh massanya berada pada jarak yang lebih besar dari sumbu rotasi, sehingga\r\nmomen inersia maksimum dapat dicapai untuk menghasilkan&nbsp; energi kinetik rotasi lebih besar</span></p>', NULL, 'A', 0.060, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 14:14:21', '2026-05-03 16:45:15');
INSERT INTO `soal_ujian` (`soal_id`, `kode_soal`, `ujian_id`, `bank_ujian_id`, `pertanyaan`, `pilihan_a`, `pilihan_b`, `pilihan_c`, `pilihan_d`, `pilihan_e`, `pembahasan`, `foto`, `jawaban_benar`, `tingkat_kesulitan`, `is_bank_soal`, `created_by`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(327, 'ACTofROD42', NULL, 17, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Gambar 39 menunjukkan roda gerinda batu berat\r\nyang digunakan untuk mengasah perkakas.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777767298_69f69382e80c7.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin: 10px 0px;\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">Gambar 39. Roda gerinda batu berat<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">Pedal\r\nterhubung ke poros roda melalui tuas penghubung dan engkol. Operator menekan\r\npedal ke bawah untuk mempercepat roda dari keadaan diam. Roda mulai berputar ke\r\narah yang ditunjukkan panah. Mengapa torsi yang diterapkan pada poros berubah\r\nsaat operator menekan pedal ke bawah adalah....</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">karena gaya gravitasi pada pedal berubah-ubah\r\nsepanjang lintasan gerak kaki operator</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">karena massa roda gerinda bertambah selama\r\nputaran sehingga membutuhkan torsi berbeda</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">karena gesekan pada poros meningkat setiap kali\r\npedal ditekan lebih cepat</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">karena pedal menghasilkan energi tetap sehingga\r\ntorsinya otomatis naik dengan kecepatan roda</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">karena panjang efektif lengan gaya berubah\r\nakibat perubahan sudut antara tuas penghubung dan engkol</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">karena panjang efektif lengan gaya berubah\r\nakibat perubahan sudut antara tuas penghubung dan engkol</span></p>', NULL, 'E', -0.070, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 14:16:03', '2026-05-03 16:44:57'),
(328, 'ACtofROD43', NULL, 17, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Sebuah gambar 40 menunjukkan satelit yang\r\nberputar dengan dua teleskop kecil pada ujung lengan teleskop. Ketika\r\nlengan-lengan sepenuhnya diperpanjang, momen inersia total satelit adalah 240\r\nkg·m². Momen inersia badan satelit sendiri adalah 71 kg·m², dan setiap teleskop\r\nbermassa 5 kg. Motor pada badan satelit perlahan menarik lengan, membuat\r\nteleskop bergerak lebih dekat ke sumbu rotasi dengan momentum sudut yang\r\nkonstan.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777767397_69f693e571aef.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin: 10px 0px;\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">Gambar 40. Satelit yang berputar dengan 2 teleskop kecil</span></p><p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%;\">Perubahan kecepatan sudut satelit yang terjadi saat lengan teleskop\r\nditarik adalah....</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">kecepatan sudut satelit meningkat karena momen\r\ninersia berkurang sehingga dengan momentum sudut yang tetap, satelit harus\r\nberputar lebih cepat</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">kecepatan sudut satelit menurun karena momen\r\ninersia berkurang sehingga dengan momentum sudut yang tetap, satelit harus\r\nberputar lebih lambat</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">kecepatan sudut satelit meningkat karena momen\r\ninersia bertambah sehingga dengan momentum sudut yang tetap, satelit harus\r\nberputar lebih cepat</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">kecepatan sudut satelit menurun karena momen\r\ninersia bertambah sehingga dengan momentum sudut yang tetap, satelit harus\r\nberputar lebih lambat</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">kecepatan sudut satelit meningkat karena momen\r\ninersia berkurang sehingga dengan momentum sudut yang tetap, satelit harus\r\nberputar lebih lambat</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">kecepatan sudut satelit meningkat karena momen\r\ninersia berkurang sehingga dengan momentum sudut yang tetap, satelit harus\r\nberputar lebih cepat</span></p>', NULL, 'A', -0.200, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 14:17:40', '2026-05-03 16:44:40'),
(329, 'ACTofROD44', NULL, 17, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Sebuah Gambar 41\r\nmenunjukkan perubahan momen inersia I (kg·m²) seorang atlet loncat indah\r\nterhadap waktu selama melakukan rotasi di udara. Pada t = 0, memiliki kecepatan\r\nsudut awal ω₀ = 4,4 rad/s.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777767501_69f6944d9654f.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: 368.615px; margin: 10px 0px; width: 474.567px;\"></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin:0cm;text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"SV\">Gambar 41. Grafik momen inersia terhadap waktu</span></p><p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%;\">Dengan\r\nmengacu pada grafik &nbsp;4 dan prinsip\r\nkekekalan momentum sudut, kecepatan sudut maksimum yang diperoleh atlet loncat\r\nindah adalah....</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">7,4 rad/s karena kecepatan sudut maksimum\r\nterjadi ketika momen inersia maksimum</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">7,5 </span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">rad/s karena kecepatan sudut maksimum terjadi\r\nketika momen inersia minimum</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">7,5 rad/s karena kecepatan sudut maksimum\r\nterjadi ketika momen inersia maksimum&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">7,4 rad/s karena kecepatan sudut maksimum\r\nterjadi ketika momen inersia minimum&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">7,4 rad/s karena kecepatan sudut maksimum\r\nterjadi ketika momentum sudut minimum&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 14.6667px;\">7,4 rad/s karena kecepatan sudut maksimum terjadi ketika momen inersia minimum&nbsp;</span></p>', NULL, 'D', -0.480, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 14:20:04', '2026-05-03 16:44:20'),
(330, 'ACTofROD45', NULL, 17, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ligatures:none;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Sebuah\r\nbenda tegar yang ditunjukkan pada gambar 42 terdiri dari tiang penyangga\r\nvertikal dan dua palang horizontal dengan bola-bola yang terpasang.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777767663_69f694ef7fb60.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: 215.228px; margin: 10px 0px; width: 281.896px;\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ligatures:\r\nnone;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID\">Gambar 42. Tiang penyangga dengan dua palang<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ligatures:none;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">Dua bola bermassa m terpasang pada palang atas dengan\r\njarak L dari sumbu rotasi. Dua bola bermassa 2m terpasang pada palang bawah\r\ndengan jarak 2L dari sumbu rotasi. Sistem berputar terhadap sumbu vertikal\r\ndengan kecepatan sudut konstan ω. Massa batang dan tiang diabaikan. Rasio\r\nmomentum sudut total dua bola atas terhadap momentum sudut total dua bola bawah\r\nadalah....</span></span></p>', '<p><strong><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nmajor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\r\nfont-weight:normal\">2 : 1</span></strong><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">, karena momentum sudut bergantung pada jarak\r\ndari sumbu yang berbanding terbalik dengan massa bola, sehingga kontribusi bola\r\nbawah menjadi jauh lebih besar</span></p>', '<p><strong><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nmajor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\r\nfont-weight:normal\">1 : 1</span></strong><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">, karena momentum sudut bergantung pada massa\r\nyang sebanding dengan kuadrat jarak dari sumbu, sehingga kontribusi bola bawah\r\nmenjadi jauh lebih besar&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><strong><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nmajor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\r\nfont-weight:normal\">1 : 2</span></strong><b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:\r\n11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nIN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">,</span></b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"> &nbsp;karena momentum sudut bergantung pada momen\r\ninersia yang berbanding terbalik dengan massa dan kuadrat jarak dari sumbu,\r\nsehingga kontribusi bola bawah menjadi jauh lebih besar&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><strong><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nmajor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\r\nfont-weight:normal\">1 : 4</span></strong><b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:\r\n11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nIN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">,</span></b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">\r\nkarena momentum sudut berbanding lurus dengan massa dan jarak dari sumbu,\r\nsehingga bola bawah yang massanya dua kali dan jaraknya dua kali menghasilkan\r\nmomentum sudut empat kali lebih besar</span></p>', '<p><strong><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nmajor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\r\nfont-weight:normal\">1 : 8</span></strong><b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:\r\n11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nIN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">,</span></b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"> &nbsp;karena momentum sudut bergantung pada momen\r\ninersia yang sebanding dengan massa dan kuadrat jarak dari sumbu, sehingga\r\nkontribusi bola bawah menjadi jauh lebih besar</span></p>', '<p><strong><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nmajor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\r\nfont-weight:normal\">1 : 8</span></strong><b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:\r\n11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nIN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">,</span></b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"> &nbsp;karena momentum sudut bergantung pada momen\r\ninersia yang sebanding dengan massa dan kuadrat jarak dari sumbu, sehingga\r\nkontribusi bola bawah menjadi jauh lebih besar</span></p>', NULL, 'E', -0.201, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 14:22:40', '2026-05-03 16:44:00'),
(331, 'ACTofROD46', NULL, 17, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">Seorang siswa melakukan percobaan pada kursi putar. Pada saat\r\ntangan ditarik ke dada, ia berputar cepat. Saat tangan direntangkan, ia\r\nberputar lambat. Siswa menyimpulkan:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><i><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">“perubahan kecepatan sudut terjadi karena saat tangan ditarik ke\r\ndada, torsi semakin besar sehingga berputar cepat”<o:p></o:p></span></i></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Tindakan\r\nyang seharusnya dilakukan siswa untuk mengevaluasi penalarannya adalah....</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">memeriksa kembali apakah benar ada torsi yang\r\nbekerja dan menyadari bahwa perubahan kecepatan sudut disebabkan oleh perubahan\r\nmomen inersia</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">memeriksa kembali apakah benar ada torsi yang\r\nbekerja dan menyadari bahwa perubahan kecepatan sudut disebabkan oleh perubahan\r\nenergi kinetik rotasi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">memeriksa kembali apakah benar ada momen inersia\r\nyang bekerja dan menyadari bahwa perubahan kecepatan sudut disebabkan oleh\r\nperubahan torsi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">memeriksa kembali apakah benar ada momen inersia\r\nyang bekerja dan menyadari bahwa perubahan kecepatan sudut disebabkan oleh\r\nperubahan energi kinetik rotasi&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">memeriksa kembali apakah benar ada torsi yang\r\nbekerja dan menyadari bahwa perubahan kecepatan sudut disebabkan oleh perubahan\r\npercepatan sudut</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">memeriksa kembali apakah benar ada torsi yang\r\nbekerja dan menyadari bahwa perubahan kecepatan sudut disebabkan oleh perubahan\r\nmomen inersia</span></p>', NULL, 'A', 0.440, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 14:24:07', '2026-05-03 16:43:42'),
(332, 'ACTofROD47', NULL, 17, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Seorang siswa memberikan kesimpulan setelah\r\nmelakukan percobaan bahwa<i>“jika kecepatan sudut suatu benda tetap maka energi\r\nkinetik rotasinya hanya bergantung pada massa benda”. </i>Ia membandingkan dua\r\nbenda yang berputar dengan kecepatan sudut yang sama.</span></p><ul><li><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">Benda A: massa 4 kg dan momen inersia 2 kg.m<sup>2</sup></span></span></li><li><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">Benda B: massa 4 kg dan\r\nmomen inersia 6 </span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">kg.m<sup>2</sup></span></span></span></li></ul><p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">Langkah evaluasi diri apa yang paling tepat\r\nuntuk memperbaiki kesimpulan siswa tersebut adalah....</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">meninjau kembali persamaan energi kinetik rotasi\r\ndan menyadari bahwa energi kinetik rotasi bergantung pada momen inersia, bukan\r\nhanya massa</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">meninjau kembali persamaan energi kinetik rotasi\r\ndan menyadari bahwa energi kinetik rotasi bergantung pada torsi, bukan hanya\r\nmassa</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">meninjau kembali persamaan energi kinetik rotasi\r\ndan menyadari bahwa energi kinetik rotasi bergantung pada kecepatan sudut,\r\nbukan hanya massa</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">meninjau kembali persamaan energi kinetik rotasi\r\ndan menyadari bahwa energi kinetik rotasi bergantung pada torsi, bukan hanya\r\nmomen inersia</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">meninjau kembali persamaan energi kinetik rotasi\r\ndan menyadari bahwa energi kinetik rotasi bergantung pada kecepatan sudut,\r\nbukan hanya torsi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">meninjau kembali persamaan energi kinetik rotasi\r\ndan menyadari bahwa energi kinetik rotasi bergantung pada momen inersia, bukan\r\nhanya massa</span></p>', NULL, 'A', -0.621, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 14:29:03', '2026-05-03 16:43:21'),
(333, 'ACTofROD48', NULL, 17, '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Pada sebuah percobaan, roda A dan B diputar\r\ndengan torsi yang sama dalam interval waktu tertentu. Roda A memiliki momen\r\ninersia lebih kecil daripada roda B. Siswa menyimpulkan: <i>” Roda B memiliki\r\nenergi kinetik rotasi lebih besar dari roda A”.</i></span></p><p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Langkah yang tepat untuk\r\nmengevaluasi kesimpulan siswa tersebut adalah....</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">meninjau hubungan torsi, momen inersia dan\r\nenergi kinetik rotasi lalu menyadari bahwa roda dengan momen inersia lebih\r\nkecil memiliki energi kinetik rotasi lebih kecil</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">meninjau hubungan torsi, momen inersia dan\r\nenergi kinetik rotasi lalu menyadari bahwa roda dengan torsi lebih kecil\r\nmemiliki energi kinetik rotasi lebih besar</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">meninjau hubungan torsi, momen inersia dan\r\nenergi kinetik rotasi lalu menyadari bahwa roda dengan momen inersia lebih\r\nkecil memiliki kecepatan sudut rotasi lebih besar</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">meninjau hubungan torsi, momen inersia dan\r\nenergi kinetik rotasi lalu menyadari bahwa roda dengan kecepatan sudut lebih\r\nkecil memiliki energi kinetik rotasi lebih kecil</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">meninjau hubungan torsi, momen inersia dan\r\nenergi kinetik rotasi lalu menyadari bahwa roda dengan momen inersia lebih\r\nkecil memiliki energi kinetik rotasi lebih besar</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">meninjau hubungan torsi, momen inersia dan\r\nenergi kinetik rotasi lalu menyadari bahwa roda dengan momen inersia lebih\r\nkecil memiliki energi kinetik rotasi lebih besar</span></p>', NULL, 'E', 0.690, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 14:30:22', '2026-05-03 16:43:03'),
(334, 'ACTofROD49', NULL, 17, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">Seorang siswa melakukan percobaan torsi menggunakan sebuah batang\r\nhomogen yang dapat berputar bebas pada titik tumpu di salah satu ujungnya.\r\nSebuah gaya 4 N diberikan secara tegak lurus batang pada jarak 20 cm dari titik\r\ntumpu. Siswa tersebut menghitung torsi sebesar:</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"color: rgb(71, 71, 71); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: start;\">???? = F x r = 4 x 0,2 = 0,8 Nm</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><!--[if gte msEquation 12]><m:oMathPara><m:oMath><i\r\n  style=\'mso-bidi-font-style:normal\'><span lang=IN style=\'font-size:12.0pt;\r\n  line-height:150%;font-family:\"Cambria Math\",serif;mso-bidi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\n  mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\'><m:r>τ</m:r><m:r>=</m:r><m:r>F</m:r><m:r>×</m:r><m:r>r</m:r><m:r>=4×</m:r></span></i><span\r\n  lang=IN style=\'font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\"Cambria Math\",serif;\r\n  mso-bidi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\'><m:r><m:rPr><m:scr\r\n     m:val=\"roman\"/><m:sty m:val=\"p\"/></m:rPr>0,2</m:r><m:r><i\r\n   style=\'mso-bidi-font-style:normal\'>=</i></m:r><m:r><m:rPr><m:scr m:val=\"roman\"/><m:sty\r\n     m:val=\"p\"/></m:rPr>0,8</m:r></span><span lang=IN style=\'font-size:12.0pt;\r\n  line-height:150%;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\n  major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\'><m:r><m:rPr><m:scr\r\n     m:val=\"roman\"/><m:sty m:val=\"p\"/><m:nor/></m:rPr> Nm</m:r></span></m:oMath></m:oMathPara><![endif]--><!--[if !msEquation]--><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;\r\nmso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><v:shapetype id=\"_x0000_t75\" coordsize=\"21600,21600\" o:spt=\"75\" o:preferrelative=\"t\" path=\"m@4@5l@4@11@9@11@9@5xe\" filled=\"f\" stroked=\"f\">\r\n <v:stroke joinstyle=\"miter\">\r\n <v:formulas>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"if lineDrawn pixelLineWidth 0\">\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @0 1 0\">\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum 0 0 @1\">\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @2 1 2\">\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelWidth\">\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelHeight\">\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @0 0 1\">\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @6 1 2\">\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelWidth\">\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @8 21600 0\">\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelHeight\">\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @10 21600 0\">\r\n </v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:formulas>\r\n <v:path o:extrusionok=\"f\" gradientshapeok=\"t\" o:connecttype=\"rect\">\r\n <o:lock v:ext=\"edit\" aspectratio=\"t\">\r\n</o:lock></v:path></v:stroke></v:shapetype><v:shape id=\"_x0000_i1025\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style=\"width:153.5pt;\r\n height:15pt\">\r\n <v:imagedata src=\"file:///C:/Users/Lenovo/AppData/Local/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_image001.png\" o:title=\"\" chromakey=\"white\">\r\n</v:imagedata></v:shape></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">Namun, setelah berdiskusi dengan temannya, siswa tersebut menyadari\r\nbahwa arah gaya sebenarnya tidak sepenuhnya tegak lurus, melainkan membentuk\r\nsudut 30° terhadap batang. Siswa kemudian meninjau kembali perhitungannya.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Tindakan\r\nreflektif paling tepat yang seharusnya dilakukan siswa tersebut adalah....</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">tetap mempertahankan hasil perhitungan karena\r\nbesar gaya dan jarak sudah diketahui</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">mengulang perhitungan dengan menyadari bahwa\r\nhanya komponen gaya tegak lurus batang yang menghasilkan torsi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">menyimpulkan bahwa kesalahan sudut tidak\r\nberpengaruh signifikan terhadap torsi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">mengubah nilai jarak karena sudut gaya\r\nmemengaruhi panjang batang&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:EN-ID;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">menghitung kembali torsi menggunakan resultan\r\ngaya translasi batang&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">mengulang perhitungan dengan menyadari bahwa hanya komponen gaya tegak lurus batang yang menghasilkan torsi</span></p>', NULL, 'B', 0.310, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 14:34:21', '2026-05-03 16:42:44');
INSERT INTO `soal_ujian` (`soal_id`, `kode_soal`, `ujian_id`, `bank_ujian_id`, `pertanyaan`, `pilihan_a`, `pilihan_b`, `pilihan_c`, `pilihan_d`, `pilihan_e`, `pembahasan`, `foto`, `jawaban_benar`, `tingkat_kesulitan`, `is_bank_soal`, `created_by`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(335, 'ACTofROD50', NULL, 17, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Raka mempelajari konsep momen inersia dan\r\nmembuat kesimpulan berikut:<i>“Jika dua benda memiliki massa dan bentuk yang\r\nsama, maka momen inersianya sama”. </i>Untuk memastikan pemahamannya, raka\r\nmembandingkan dalam 2 kondisi yaitu:</span></p><ul><li><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">batang homogen diputar pada ujungnya</span></li><li><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">batang homogen diputar pada titik tengahnya</span></li></ul><p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">Setelah meninjau kembali kesimpulannya, tindakan\r\nreflektif yang paling tepat yang seharusnya dilakukan Raka adalah....</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">tetap mempertahankan kesimpulan awal karena\r\nmassa dan bentuk benda tidak berubah</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">mengubah kesimpulan dengan menyadari bahwa\r\nposisi sumbu rotasi memengaruhi distribusi massa terhadap sumbu&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">mengabaikan perbedaan sumbu rotasi karena tidak\r\nberpengaruh pada gerak rotasi&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">menyimpulkan bahwa momen inersia hanya\r\nbergantung pada panjang benda&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">menyatakan bahwa momen inersia sama selama gaya\r\nyang diberikan sama besar&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">mengubah kesimpulan dengan menyadari bahwa posisi sumbu rotasi memengaruhi distribusi massa terhadap sumbu&nbsp;</span></p>', NULL, 'B', 0.190, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 14:36:32', '2026-05-03 16:42:20'),
(336, 'ACTofROD51', NULL, 17, '<p style=\"margin:0cm;text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\">Saat mempelajari roda pejal yang dipercepat oleh massa\r\njatuh, seorang siswa menganggap bahwa energi potensial massa hanya berubah\r\nmenjadi energi kinetik translasi massa, dan energi rotasi roda “<i>muncul\r\nsendiri</i>”. Setelah mempelajari prinsip kekekalan energi, siswa mulai\r\nmenyadari ketidaksesuaian dalam penalarannya.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Langkah\r\nkoreksi diri apa yang paling tepat dilakukan siswa untuk memperbaiki\r\nkesalahpahaman tersebut adalah....</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">mengakui bahwa ia perlu memperbaiki pemahaman\r\ndan meninjau kembali bagaimana energi potensial berubah menjadi energi kinetik\r\ntranslasi </span><em><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\r\nfont-style:normal\">dan</span></em><i><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"> </span></i><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">rotasi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">menyadari bahwa ada ketidaksesuaian, namun tetap\r\nmempertahankan pandangannya sampai ia mempelajari lebih banyak contoh</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">mempertimbangkan kembali hubungannya, tetapi\r\ntetap yakin bahwa energi rotasi tidak berasal dari energi potensial</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">meninjau penjelasan energi, tetapi menunggu\r\nvalidasi dari sumber lain sebelum mengubah pemahaman awalnya</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">mengakui keraguannya tetapi berasumsi bahwa\r\nenergi rotasi tidak penting dalam analisis sehingga pemahaman awal tetap\r\nrelevan</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 15.6933px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">mengakui bahwa ia perlu memperbaiki pemahaman dan meninjau kembali bagaimana energi potensial berubah menjadi energi kinetik translasi&nbsp;</span><em><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 15.6933px; font-style: normal;\">dan</span></em><i><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 15.6933px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;</span></i><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 15.6933px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">rotasi</span></p>', NULL, 'A', 0.690, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 14:38:50', '2026-05-03 16:41:59'),
(337, 'ACTofROD52', NULL, 17, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Seorang siswa awalnya berpendapat bahwa ketika\r\nkemudi putar ekskavator diputar untuk memindahkan pengeruk, massa boom, dan\r\nlengan tidak memengaruhi usaha yang diperlukan, karena <i>“semua bagian\r\nekskavator hanya ikut berputar secara otomatis tanpa memberikan rotasi tambahan\".</i></span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777768784_69f699501e6cb.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: 194.615px; margin: 10px 0px; width: 406.244px;\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">Gambar 39. Eskavator <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:0cm;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\">Setelah melihat\r\ngambar 43 dan memahami bahwa bagian-bagian tersebut berada pada jarak yang\r\nberbeda dari sumbu rotasi, siswa menyadari bahwa pemahamannya mungkin keliru.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">Tindakan\r\nrefleksi yang paling tepat dilakukan siswa untuk memperbaiki pemahamannya\r\nadalah....</span><i></i></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">tetap mempertahankan pendapat awal karena\r\nekskavator dirancang untuk memutar kemudi putar dengan mudah terlepas dari\r\nposisi beban</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">mengabaikan keraguan yang muncul dan fokus pada\r\nintuisi awal bahwa massa tidak relevan dalam rotasi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">menyimpulkan bahwa kesalahan terjadi karena\r\ngambar ekskavator tidak menunjukkan semua gaya sehingga tidak perlu mengubah\r\npemahaman awal</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">meninjau kembali konsep momen inersia untuk\r\nmemahami bagaimana jarak massa dari sumbu rotasi memengaruhi rotasi ekskavator</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">menghafal rumus momen inersia tanpa meninjau\r\nkembali penyebab kesalahan pemahaman sebelumnya</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 14.6667px;\">meninjau kembali konsep momen inersia untuk memahami bagaimana jarak massa dari sumbu rotasi memengaruhi rotasi ekskavator</span></p>', NULL, 'D', -0.480, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 14:40:49', '2026-05-03 16:41:42'),
(338, 'ACTofROD53', NULL, 17, '<p style=\"margin:0cm;text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\">Seorang siswa&nbsp;\r\npercaya bahwa besar gaya adalah satu-satunya faktor yang menentukan\r\nbesar torsi pada sebuah engkol. Ia mengabaikan informasi bahwa torsi juga\r\ndipengaruhi oleh jarak gaya dari sumbu rotasi. Setelah mengamati percobaan di\r\nmana gaya kecil dapat menghasilkan torsi besar jika gaya diberi pada lengan\r\nyang lebih panjang, siswa ini mulai meragukan pandangannya.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Tindakan\r\nrefleksi yang paling tepat dilakukan siswa untuk memperbaiki pemahamannya\r\nadalah....</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">menyadari bahwa pemahaman awalnya tidak lengkap\r\ndan meninjau kembali konsep bahwa torsi dipengaruhi oleh besar gaya </span><em><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;\r\nmso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">dan</span></em><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"> jarak dari sumbu rotasi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">mengakui bahwa mungkin ada faktor lain yang\r\nterlibat, tetapi tetap berpegang pada pandangan awal sampai ia melihat\r\npercobaan lebih banyak</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">mempertimbangkan kembali penjelasan percobaan,\r\ntetapi tetap mengutamakan keyakinan awal bahwa gaya adalah faktor dominan</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">meninjau kembali rumus torsi, namun menunggu\r\nkonfirmasi dari guru sebelum mengubah pemahaman lamanya</span></p>', '<p><br></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 15.6933px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">menyadari bahwa pemahaman awalnya tidak lengkap dan meninjau kembali konsep bahwa torsi dipengaruhi oleh besar gaya&nbsp;</span><em><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 15.6933px;\">dan</span></em><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 15.6933px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;jarak dari sumbu rotasi</span></p>', NULL, 'A', -0.480, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 14:42:05', '2026-05-03 16:41:22'),
(339, 'ACTofROD54', NULL, 17, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">Rina membantu ayahnya memperbaiki sepeda di bengkel kecil depan\r\nrumah. Ia memperhatikan bahwa roda sepeda balap dan roda sepeda gunung memiliki\r\nukuran dan berat yang sama namun distribusi massa yang berbeda. Kemudian Rina\r\nmemberikan kesimpulan kepada ayahnya bahwa:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><i><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">“Karena kedua roda memiliki ukuran dan berat yang sama seharusnya\r\nenergi kinetik rotasi rodanya juga sama.”<o:p></o:p></span></i></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Kemudian\r\nRina mencoba mengendarai kedua sepeda tersebut dengan gaya yang sama. Saat\r\nmengayuh sepeda balap, menurut Rina kayuhannya terasa cukup ringan, sedangkan\r\nketika mengayuh sepeda gunung, Rina merasakan kayuhan yang lebih berat meskipun\r\ndilakukan dengan gaya yang sama. Namun, Rina kemudian meninjau kembali\r\nkesimpulan tersebut dengan mengaitkannya pada konsep energi kinetik gerak\r\nrotasi yang telah ia pelajari di kelas. Berdasarkan proses refleksi Rina,\r\npernyataan yang paling tepat adalah....</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">energi kinetik rotasi roda sepeda gunung lebih\r\nbesar karena distribusi massa roda berada lebih jauh dari sumbu rotasi,\r\nsehingga momen inersia roda menjadi lebih besar</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">energi kinetik rotasi roda sepeda gunung lebih\r\nbesar karena distribusi massa roda lebih terkonsentrasi di pusat roda, sehingga\r\nmemerlukan energi lebih besar untuk berputar</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">energi kinetik rotasi roda sepeda gunung lebih\r\nbesar karena distribusi massa total roda lebih besar, sehingga energi rotasinya\r\nmeningkat meskipun distribusi massanya sama</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">energi kinetik rotasi roda sepeda gunung lebih\r\nbesar karena ban yang lebih lebar meningkatkan gaya gesek, sehingga roda\r\nmemerlukan energi rotasi lebih besar</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">energi kinetik rotasi roda sepeda gunung lebih\r\nbesar karena jari-jari roda lebih panjang, sehingga kecepatan sudut rodanya meningkat&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">energi kinetik rotasi roda sepeda gunung lebih\r\nbesar karena distribusi massa roda berada lebih jauh dari sumbu rotasi,\r\nsehingga momen inersia roda menjadi lebih besar</span></p>', NULL, 'A', -0.200, 1, 1, '2026-05-03 14:43:33', '2026-05-03 16:41:06'),
(340, 'ACTofROD54', 11, NULL, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">Rina membantu ayahnya memperbaiki sepeda di bengkel kecil depan\r\nrumah. Ia memperhatikan bahwa roda sepeda balap dan roda sepeda gunung memiliki\r\nukuran dan berat yang sama namun distribusi massa yang berbeda. Kemudian Rina\r\nmemberikan kesimpulan kepada ayahnya bahwa:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><i><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">“Karena kedua roda memiliki ukuran dan berat yang sama seharusnya\r\nenergi kinetik rotasi rodanya juga sama.”<o:p></o:p></span></i></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Kemudian\r\nRina mencoba mengendarai kedua sepeda tersebut dengan gaya yang sama. Saat\r\nmengayuh sepeda balap, menurut Rina kayuhannya terasa cukup ringan, sedangkan\r\nketika mengayuh sepeda gunung, Rina merasakan kayuhan yang lebih berat meskipun\r\ndilakukan dengan gaya yang sama. Namun, Rina kemudian meninjau kembali\r\nkesimpulan tersebut dengan mengaitkannya pada konsep energi kinetik gerak\r\nrotasi yang telah ia pelajari di kelas. Berdasarkan proses refleksi Rina,\r\npernyataan yang paling tepat adalah....</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">energi kinetik rotasi roda sepeda gunung lebih\r\nbesar karena distribusi massa roda berada lebih jauh dari sumbu rotasi,\r\nsehingga momen inersia roda menjadi lebih besar</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">energi kinetik rotasi roda sepeda gunung lebih\r\nbesar karena distribusi massa roda lebih terkonsentrasi di pusat roda, sehingga\r\nmemerlukan energi lebih besar untuk berputar</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">energi kinetik rotasi roda sepeda gunung lebih\r\nbesar karena distribusi massa total roda lebih besar, sehingga energi rotasinya\r\nmeningkat meskipun distribusi massanya sama</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">energi kinetik rotasi roda sepeda gunung lebih\r\nbesar karena ban yang lebih lebar meningkatkan gaya gesek, sehingga roda\r\nmemerlukan energi rotasi lebih besar</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">energi kinetik rotasi roda sepeda gunung lebih\r\nbesar karena jari-jari roda lebih panjang, sehingga kecepatan sudut rodanya meningkat&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">energi kinetik rotasi roda sepeda gunung lebih\r\nbesar karena distribusi massa roda berada lebih jauh dari sumbu rotasi,\r\nsehingga momen inersia roda menjadi lebih besar</span></p>', NULL, 'A', -0.200, 0, 1, '2026-05-03 16:46:18', '2026-05-03 16:46:18'),
(341, 'ACTofROD53', 11, NULL, '<p style=\"margin:0cm;text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\">Seorang siswa&nbsp;\r\npercaya bahwa besar gaya adalah satu-satunya faktor yang menentukan\r\nbesar torsi pada sebuah engkol. Ia mengabaikan informasi bahwa torsi juga\r\ndipengaruhi oleh jarak gaya dari sumbu rotasi. Setelah mengamati percobaan di\r\nmana gaya kecil dapat menghasilkan torsi besar jika gaya diberi pada lengan\r\nyang lebih panjang, siswa ini mulai meragukan pandangannya.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Tindakan\r\nrefleksi yang paling tepat dilakukan siswa untuk memperbaiki pemahamannya\r\nadalah....</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">menyadari bahwa pemahaman awalnya tidak lengkap\r\ndan meninjau kembali konsep bahwa torsi dipengaruhi oleh besar gaya </span><em><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;\r\nmso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">dan</span></em><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"> jarak dari sumbu rotasi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">mengakui bahwa mungkin ada faktor lain yang\r\nterlibat, tetapi tetap berpegang pada pandangan awal sampai ia melihat\r\npercobaan lebih banyak</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">mempertimbangkan kembali penjelasan percobaan,\r\ntetapi tetap mengutamakan keyakinan awal bahwa gaya adalah faktor dominan</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">meninjau kembali rumus torsi, namun menunggu\r\nkonfirmasi dari guru sebelum mengubah pemahaman lamanya</span></p>', '<p><br></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 15.6933px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">menyadari bahwa pemahaman awalnya tidak lengkap dan meninjau kembali konsep bahwa torsi dipengaruhi oleh besar gaya&nbsp;</span><em><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 15.6933px;\">dan</span></em><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 15.6933px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;jarak dari sumbu rotasi</span></p>', NULL, 'A', -0.480, 0, 1, '2026-05-03 16:46:18', '2026-05-03 16:46:18'),
(342, 'ACTofROD52', 11, NULL, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Seorang siswa awalnya berpendapat bahwa ketika\r\nkemudi putar ekskavator diputar untuk memindahkan pengeruk, massa boom, dan\r\nlengan tidak memengaruhi usaha yang diperlukan, karena <i>“semua bagian\r\nekskavator hanya ikut berputar secara otomatis tanpa memberikan rotasi tambahan\".</i></span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777768784_69f699501e6cb.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: 194.615px; margin: 10px 0px; width: 406.244px;\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">Gambar 39. Eskavator <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:0cm;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\">Setelah melihat\r\ngambar 43 dan memahami bahwa bagian-bagian tersebut berada pada jarak yang\r\nberbeda dari sumbu rotasi, siswa menyadari bahwa pemahamannya mungkin keliru.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">Tindakan\r\nrefleksi yang paling tepat dilakukan siswa untuk memperbaiki pemahamannya\r\nadalah....</span><i></i></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">tetap mempertahankan pendapat awal karena\r\nekskavator dirancang untuk memutar kemudi putar dengan mudah terlepas dari\r\nposisi beban</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">mengabaikan keraguan yang muncul dan fokus pada\r\nintuisi awal bahwa massa tidak relevan dalam rotasi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">menyimpulkan bahwa kesalahan terjadi karena\r\ngambar ekskavator tidak menunjukkan semua gaya sehingga tidak perlu mengubah\r\npemahaman awal</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">meninjau kembali konsep momen inersia untuk\r\nmemahami bagaimana jarak massa dari sumbu rotasi memengaruhi rotasi ekskavator</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">menghafal rumus momen inersia tanpa meninjau\r\nkembali penyebab kesalahan pemahaman sebelumnya</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 14.6667px;\">meninjau kembali konsep momen inersia untuk memahami bagaimana jarak massa dari sumbu rotasi memengaruhi rotasi ekskavator</span></p>', NULL, 'D', -0.480, 0, 1, '2026-05-03 16:46:18', '2026-05-03 16:46:18'),
(343, 'ACTofROD51', 11, NULL, '<p style=\"margin:0cm;text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\">Saat mempelajari roda pejal yang dipercepat oleh massa\r\njatuh, seorang siswa menganggap bahwa energi potensial massa hanya berubah\r\nmenjadi energi kinetik translasi massa, dan energi rotasi roda “<i>muncul\r\nsendiri</i>”. Setelah mempelajari prinsip kekekalan energi, siswa mulai\r\nmenyadari ketidaksesuaian dalam penalarannya.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Langkah\r\nkoreksi diri apa yang paling tepat dilakukan siswa untuk memperbaiki\r\nkesalahpahaman tersebut adalah....</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">mengakui bahwa ia perlu memperbaiki pemahaman\r\ndan meninjau kembali bagaimana energi potensial berubah menjadi energi kinetik\r\ntranslasi </span><em><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\r\nfont-style:normal\">dan</span></em><i><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"> </span></i><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">rotasi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">menyadari bahwa ada ketidaksesuaian, namun tetap\r\nmempertahankan pandangannya sampai ia mempelajari lebih banyak contoh</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">mempertimbangkan kembali hubungannya, tetapi\r\ntetap yakin bahwa energi rotasi tidak berasal dari energi potensial</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">meninjau penjelasan energi, tetapi menunggu\r\nvalidasi dari sumber lain sebelum mengubah pemahaman awalnya</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">mengakui keraguannya tetapi berasumsi bahwa\r\nenergi rotasi tidak penting dalam analisis sehingga pemahaman awal tetap\r\nrelevan</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 15.6933px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">mengakui bahwa ia perlu memperbaiki pemahaman dan meninjau kembali bagaimana energi potensial berubah menjadi energi kinetik translasi&nbsp;</span><em><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 15.6933px; font-style: normal;\">dan</span></em><i><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 15.6933px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;</span></i><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 15.6933px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">rotasi</span></p>', NULL, 'A', 0.690, 0, 1, '2026-05-03 16:46:18', '2026-05-03 16:46:18');
INSERT INTO `soal_ujian` (`soal_id`, `kode_soal`, `ujian_id`, `bank_ujian_id`, `pertanyaan`, `pilihan_a`, `pilihan_b`, `pilihan_c`, `pilihan_d`, `pilihan_e`, `pembahasan`, `foto`, `jawaban_benar`, `tingkat_kesulitan`, `is_bank_soal`, `created_by`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(344, 'ACTofROD50', 11, NULL, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Raka mempelajari konsep momen inersia dan\r\nmembuat kesimpulan berikut:<i>“Jika dua benda memiliki massa dan bentuk yang\r\nsama, maka momen inersianya sama”. </i>Untuk memastikan pemahamannya, raka\r\nmembandingkan dalam 2 kondisi yaitu:</span></p><ul><li><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">batang homogen diputar pada ujungnya</span></li><li><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">batang homogen diputar pada titik tengahnya</span></li></ul><p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">Setelah meninjau kembali kesimpulannya, tindakan\r\nreflektif yang paling tepat yang seharusnya dilakukan Raka adalah....</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">tetap mempertahankan kesimpulan awal karena\r\nmassa dan bentuk benda tidak berubah</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">mengubah kesimpulan dengan menyadari bahwa\r\nposisi sumbu rotasi memengaruhi distribusi massa terhadap sumbu&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">mengabaikan perbedaan sumbu rotasi karena tidak\r\nberpengaruh pada gerak rotasi&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">menyimpulkan bahwa momen inersia hanya\r\nbergantung pada panjang benda&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">menyatakan bahwa momen inersia sama selama gaya\r\nyang diberikan sama besar&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">mengubah kesimpulan dengan menyadari bahwa posisi sumbu rotasi memengaruhi distribusi massa terhadap sumbu&nbsp;</span></p>', NULL, 'B', 0.190, 0, 1, '2026-05-03 16:46:18', '2026-05-03 16:46:18'),
(345, 'ACTofROD49', 11, NULL, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">Seorang siswa melakukan percobaan torsi menggunakan sebuah batang\r\nhomogen yang dapat berputar bebas pada titik tumpu di salah satu ujungnya.\r\nSebuah gaya 4 N diberikan secara tegak lurus batang pada jarak 20 cm dari titik\r\ntumpu. Siswa tersebut menghitung torsi sebesar:</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"color: rgb(71, 71, 71); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: start;\">???? = F x r = 4 x 0,2 = 0,8 Nm</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><!--[if gte msEquation 12]><m:oMathPara><m:oMath><i\r\n  style=\'mso-bidi-font-style:normal\'><span lang=IN style=\'font-size:12.0pt;\r\n  line-height:150%;font-family:\"Cambria Math\",serif;mso-bidi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\n  mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\'><m:r>τ</m:r><m:r>=</m:r><m:r>F</m:r><m:r>×</m:r><m:r>r</m:r><m:r>=4×</m:r></span></i><span\r\n  lang=IN style=\'font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\"Cambria Math\",serif;\r\n  mso-bidi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\'><m:r><m:rPr><m:scr\r\n     m:val=\"roman\"/><m:sty m:val=\"p\"/></m:rPr>0,2</m:r><m:r><i\r\n   style=\'mso-bidi-font-style:normal\'>=</i></m:r><m:r><m:rPr><m:scr m:val=\"roman\"/><m:sty\r\n     m:val=\"p\"/></m:rPr>0,8</m:r></span><span lang=IN style=\'font-size:12.0pt;\r\n  line-height:150%;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\n  major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\'><m:r><m:rPr><m:scr\r\n     m:val=\"roman\"/><m:sty m:val=\"p\"/><m:nor/></m:rPr> Nm</m:r></span></m:oMath></m:oMathPara><![endif]--><!--[if !msEquation]--><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;\r\nmso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><v:shapetype id=\"_x0000_t75\" coordsize=\"21600,21600\" o:spt=\"75\" o:preferrelative=\"t\" path=\"m@4@5l@4@11@9@11@9@5xe\" filled=\"f\" stroked=\"f\">\r\n <v:stroke joinstyle=\"miter\">\r\n <v:formulas>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"if lineDrawn pixelLineWidth 0\">\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @0 1 0\">\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum 0 0 @1\">\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @2 1 2\">\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelWidth\">\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelHeight\">\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @0 0 1\">\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @6 1 2\">\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelWidth\">\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @8 21600 0\">\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelHeight\">\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @10 21600 0\">\r\n </v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:formulas>\r\n <v:path o:extrusionok=\"f\" gradientshapeok=\"t\" o:connecttype=\"rect\">\r\n <o:lock v:ext=\"edit\" aspectratio=\"t\">\r\n</o:lock></v:path></v:stroke></v:shapetype><v:shape id=\"_x0000_i1025\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style=\"width:153.5pt;\r\n height:15pt\">\r\n <v:imagedata src=\"file:///C:/Users/Lenovo/AppData/Local/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_image001.png\" o:title=\"\" chromakey=\"white\">\r\n</v:imagedata></v:shape></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">Namun, setelah berdiskusi dengan temannya, siswa tersebut menyadari\r\nbahwa arah gaya sebenarnya tidak sepenuhnya tegak lurus, melainkan membentuk\r\nsudut 30° terhadap batang. Siswa kemudian meninjau kembali perhitungannya.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Tindakan\r\nreflektif paling tepat yang seharusnya dilakukan siswa tersebut adalah....</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">tetap mempertahankan hasil perhitungan karena\r\nbesar gaya dan jarak sudah diketahui</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">mengulang perhitungan dengan menyadari bahwa\r\nhanya komponen gaya tegak lurus batang yang menghasilkan torsi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">menyimpulkan bahwa kesalahan sudut tidak\r\nberpengaruh signifikan terhadap torsi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">mengubah nilai jarak karena sudut gaya\r\nmemengaruhi panjang batang&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:EN-ID;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">menghitung kembali torsi menggunakan resultan\r\ngaya translasi batang&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">mengulang perhitungan dengan menyadari bahwa hanya komponen gaya tegak lurus batang yang menghasilkan torsi</span></p>', NULL, 'B', 0.310, 0, 1, '2026-05-03 16:46:18', '2026-05-03 16:46:18'),
(346, 'ACTofROD48', 11, NULL, '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Pada sebuah percobaan, roda A dan B diputar\r\ndengan torsi yang sama dalam interval waktu tertentu. Roda A memiliki momen\r\ninersia lebih kecil daripada roda B. Siswa menyimpulkan: <i>” Roda B memiliki\r\nenergi kinetik rotasi lebih besar dari roda A”.</i></span></p><p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Langkah yang tepat untuk\r\nmengevaluasi kesimpulan siswa tersebut adalah....</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">meninjau hubungan torsi, momen inersia dan\r\nenergi kinetik rotasi lalu menyadari bahwa roda dengan momen inersia lebih\r\nkecil memiliki energi kinetik rotasi lebih kecil</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">meninjau hubungan torsi, momen inersia dan\r\nenergi kinetik rotasi lalu menyadari bahwa roda dengan torsi lebih kecil\r\nmemiliki energi kinetik rotasi lebih besar</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">meninjau hubungan torsi, momen inersia dan\r\nenergi kinetik rotasi lalu menyadari bahwa roda dengan momen inersia lebih\r\nkecil memiliki kecepatan sudut rotasi lebih besar</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">meninjau hubungan torsi, momen inersia dan\r\nenergi kinetik rotasi lalu menyadari bahwa roda dengan kecepatan sudut lebih\r\nkecil memiliki energi kinetik rotasi lebih kecil</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">meninjau hubungan torsi, momen inersia dan\r\nenergi kinetik rotasi lalu menyadari bahwa roda dengan momen inersia lebih\r\nkecil memiliki energi kinetik rotasi lebih besar</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">meninjau hubungan torsi, momen inersia dan\r\nenergi kinetik rotasi lalu menyadari bahwa roda dengan momen inersia lebih\r\nkecil memiliki energi kinetik rotasi lebih besar</span></p>', NULL, 'E', 0.690, 0, 1, '2026-05-03 16:46:18', '2026-05-03 16:46:18'),
(347, 'ACTofROD47', 11, NULL, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Seorang siswa memberikan kesimpulan setelah\r\nmelakukan percobaan bahwa<i>“jika kecepatan sudut suatu benda tetap maka energi\r\nkinetik rotasinya hanya bergantung pada massa benda”. </i>Ia membandingkan dua\r\nbenda yang berputar dengan kecepatan sudut yang sama.</span></p><ul><li><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">Benda A: massa 4 kg dan momen inersia 2 kg.m<sup>2</sup></span></span></li><li><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">Benda B: massa 4 kg dan\r\nmomen inersia 6 </span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">kg.m<sup>2</sup></span></span></span></li></ul><p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">Langkah evaluasi diri apa yang paling tepat\r\nuntuk memperbaiki kesimpulan siswa tersebut adalah....</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">meninjau kembali persamaan energi kinetik rotasi\r\ndan menyadari bahwa energi kinetik rotasi bergantung pada momen inersia, bukan\r\nhanya massa</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">meninjau kembali persamaan energi kinetik rotasi\r\ndan menyadari bahwa energi kinetik rotasi bergantung pada torsi, bukan hanya\r\nmassa</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">meninjau kembali persamaan energi kinetik rotasi\r\ndan menyadari bahwa energi kinetik rotasi bergantung pada kecepatan sudut,\r\nbukan hanya massa</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">meninjau kembali persamaan energi kinetik rotasi\r\ndan menyadari bahwa energi kinetik rotasi bergantung pada torsi, bukan hanya\r\nmomen inersia</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">meninjau kembali persamaan energi kinetik rotasi\r\ndan menyadari bahwa energi kinetik rotasi bergantung pada kecepatan sudut,\r\nbukan hanya torsi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">meninjau kembali persamaan energi kinetik rotasi\r\ndan menyadari bahwa energi kinetik rotasi bergantung pada momen inersia, bukan\r\nhanya massa</span></p>', NULL, 'A', -0.621, 0, 1, '2026-05-03 16:46:18', '2026-05-03 16:46:18'),
(348, 'ACTofROD46', 11, NULL, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">Seorang siswa melakukan percobaan pada kursi putar. Pada saat\r\ntangan ditarik ke dada, ia berputar cepat. Saat tangan direntangkan, ia\r\nberputar lambat. Siswa menyimpulkan:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><i><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">“perubahan kecepatan sudut terjadi karena saat tangan ditarik ke\r\ndada, torsi semakin besar sehingga berputar cepat”<o:p></o:p></span></i></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Tindakan\r\nyang seharusnya dilakukan siswa untuk mengevaluasi penalarannya adalah....</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">memeriksa kembali apakah benar ada torsi yang\r\nbekerja dan menyadari bahwa perubahan kecepatan sudut disebabkan oleh perubahan\r\nmomen inersia</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">memeriksa kembali apakah benar ada torsi yang\r\nbekerja dan menyadari bahwa perubahan kecepatan sudut disebabkan oleh perubahan\r\nenergi kinetik rotasi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">memeriksa kembali apakah benar ada momen inersia\r\nyang bekerja dan menyadari bahwa perubahan kecepatan sudut disebabkan oleh\r\nperubahan torsi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">memeriksa kembali apakah benar ada momen inersia\r\nyang bekerja dan menyadari bahwa perubahan kecepatan sudut disebabkan oleh\r\nperubahan energi kinetik rotasi&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">memeriksa kembali apakah benar ada torsi yang\r\nbekerja dan menyadari bahwa perubahan kecepatan sudut disebabkan oleh perubahan\r\npercepatan sudut</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">memeriksa kembali apakah benar ada torsi yang\r\nbekerja dan menyadari bahwa perubahan kecepatan sudut disebabkan oleh perubahan\r\nmomen inersia</span></p>', NULL, 'A', 0.440, 0, 1, '2026-05-03 16:46:18', '2026-05-03 16:46:18'),
(349, 'ACTofROD45', 11, NULL, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ligatures:none;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Sebuah\r\nbenda tegar yang ditunjukkan pada gambar 42 terdiri dari tiang penyangga\r\nvertikal dan dua palang horizontal dengan bola-bola yang terpasang.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777767663_69f694ef7fb60.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: 215.228px; margin: 10px 0px; width: 281.896px;\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ligatures:\r\nnone;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID\">Gambar 42. Tiang penyangga dengan dua palang<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ligatures:none;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-ID;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">Dua bola bermassa m terpasang pada palang atas dengan\r\njarak L dari sumbu rotasi. Dua bola bermassa 2m terpasang pada palang bawah\r\ndengan jarak 2L dari sumbu rotasi. Sistem berputar terhadap sumbu vertikal\r\ndengan kecepatan sudut konstan ω. Massa batang dan tiang diabaikan. Rasio\r\nmomentum sudut total dua bola atas terhadap momentum sudut total dua bola bawah\r\nadalah....</span></span></p>', '<p><strong><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nmajor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\r\nfont-weight:normal\">2 : 1</span></strong><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">, karena momentum sudut bergantung pada jarak\r\ndari sumbu yang berbanding terbalik dengan massa bola, sehingga kontribusi bola\r\nbawah menjadi jauh lebih besar</span></p>', '<p><strong><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nmajor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\r\nfont-weight:normal\">1 : 1</span></strong><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">, karena momentum sudut bergantung pada massa\r\nyang sebanding dengan kuadrat jarak dari sumbu, sehingga kontribusi bola bawah\r\nmenjadi jauh lebih besar&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><strong><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nmajor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\r\nfont-weight:normal\">1 : 2</span></strong><b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:\r\n11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nIN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">,</span></b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"> &nbsp;karena momentum sudut bergantung pada momen\r\ninersia yang berbanding terbalik dengan massa dan kuadrat jarak dari sumbu,\r\nsehingga kontribusi bola bawah menjadi jauh lebih besar&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><strong><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nmajor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\r\nfont-weight:normal\">1 : 4</span></strong><b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:\r\n11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nIN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">,</span></b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">\r\nkarena momentum sudut berbanding lurus dengan massa dan jarak dari sumbu,\r\nsehingga bola bawah yang massanya dua kali dan jaraknya dua kali menghasilkan\r\nmomentum sudut empat kali lebih besar</span></p>', '<p><strong><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nmajor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\r\nfont-weight:normal\">1 : 8</span></strong><b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:\r\n11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nIN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">,</span></b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"> &nbsp;karena momentum sudut bergantung pada momen\r\ninersia yang sebanding dengan massa dan kuadrat jarak dari sumbu, sehingga\r\nkontribusi bola bawah menjadi jauh lebih besar</span></p>', '<p><strong><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nmajor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\r\nfont-weight:normal\">1 : 8</span></strong><b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:\r\n11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nIN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">,</span></b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"> &nbsp;karena momentum sudut bergantung pada momen\r\ninersia yang sebanding dengan massa dan kuadrat jarak dari sumbu, sehingga\r\nkontribusi bola bawah menjadi jauh lebih besar</span></p>', NULL, 'E', -0.201, 0, 1, '2026-05-03 16:46:18', '2026-05-03 16:46:18'),
(350, 'ACTofROD44', 11, NULL, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Sebuah Gambar 41\r\nmenunjukkan perubahan momen inersia I (kg·m²) seorang atlet loncat indah\r\nterhadap waktu selama melakukan rotasi di udara. Pada t = 0, memiliki kecepatan\r\nsudut awal ω₀ = 4,4 rad/s.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777767501_69f6944d9654f.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: 368.615px; margin: 10px 0px; width: 474.567px;\"></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin:0cm;text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"SV\">Gambar 41. Grafik momen inersia terhadap waktu</span></p><p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%;\">Dengan\r\nmengacu pada grafik &nbsp;4 dan prinsip\r\nkekekalan momentum sudut, kecepatan sudut maksimum yang diperoleh atlet loncat\r\nindah adalah....</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">7,4 rad/s karena kecepatan sudut maksimum\r\nterjadi ketika momen inersia maksimum</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">7,5 </span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">rad/s karena kecepatan sudut maksimum terjadi\r\nketika momen inersia minimum</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">7,5 rad/s karena kecepatan sudut maksimum\r\nterjadi ketika momen inersia maksimum&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">7,4 rad/s karena kecepatan sudut maksimum\r\nterjadi ketika momen inersia minimum&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">7,4 rad/s karena kecepatan sudut maksimum\r\nterjadi ketika momentum sudut minimum&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 14.6667px;\">7,4 rad/s karena kecepatan sudut maksimum terjadi ketika momen inersia minimum&nbsp;</span></p>', NULL, 'D', -0.480, 0, 1, '2026-05-03 16:46:18', '2026-05-03 16:46:18'),
(351, 'ACtofROD43', 11, NULL, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Sebuah gambar 40 menunjukkan satelit yang\r\nberputar dengan dua teleskop kecil pada ujung lengan teleskop. Ketika\r\nlengan-lengan sepenuhnya diperpanjang, momen inersia total satelit adalah 240\r\nkg·m². Momen inersia badan satelit sendiri adalah 71 kg·m², dan setiap teleskop\r\nbermassa 5 kg. Motor pada badan satelit perlahan menarik lengan, membuat\r\nteleskop bergerak lebih dekat ke sumbu rotasi dengan momentum sudut yang\r\nkonstan.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777767397_69f693e571aef.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin: 10px 0px;\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">Gambar 40. Satelit yang berputar dengan 2 teleskop kecil</span></p><p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%;\">Perubahan kecepatan sudut satelit yang terjadi saat lengan teleskop\r\nditarik adalah....</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">kecepatan sudut satelit meningkat karena momen\r\ninersia berkurang sehingga dengan momentum sudut yang tetap, satelit harus\r\nberputar lebih cepat</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">kecepatan sudut satelit menurun karena momen\r\ninersia berkurang sehingga dengan momentum sudut yang tetap, satelit harus\r\nberputar lebih lambat</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">kecepatan sudut satelit meningkat karena momen\r\ninersia bertambah sehingga dengan momentum sudut yang tetap, satelit harus\r\nberputar lebih cepat</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">kecepatan sudut satelit menurun karena momen\r\ninersia bertambah sehingga dengan momentum sudut yang tetap, satelit harus\r\nberputar lebih lambat</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">kecepatan sudut satelit meningkat karena momen\r\ninersia berkurang sehingga dengan momentum sudut yang tetap, satelit harus\r\nberputar lebih lambat</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">kecepatan sudut satelit meningkat karena momen\r\ninersia berkurang sehingga dengan momentum sudut yang tetap, satelit harus\r\nberputar lebih cepat</span></p>', NULL, 'A', -0.200, 0, 1, '2026-05-03 16:46:18', '2026-05-03 16:46:18');
INSERT INTO `soal_ujian` (`soal_id`, `kode_soal`, `ujian_id`, `bank_ujian_id`, `pertanyaan`, `pilihan_a`, `pilihan_b`, `pilihan_c`, `pilihan_d`, `pilihan_e`, `pembahasan`, `foto`, `jawaban_benar`, `tingkat_kesulitan`, `is_bank_soal`, `created_by`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(352, 'ACTofROD42', 11, NULL, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Gambar 39 menunjukkan roda gerinda batu berat\r\nyang digunakan untuk mengasah perkakas.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777767298_69f69382e80c7.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin: 10px 0px;\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">Gambar 39. Roda gerinda batu berat<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">Pedal\r\nterhubung ke poros roda melalui tuas penghubung dan engkol. Operator menekan\r\npedal ke bawah untuk mempercepat roda dari keadaan diam. Roda mulai berputar ke\r\narah yang ditunjukkan panah. Mengapa torsi yang diterapkan pada poros berubah\r\nsaat operator menekan pedal ke bawah adalah....</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">karena gaya gravitasi pada pedal berubah-ubah\r\nsepanjang lintasan gerak kaki operator</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">karena massa roda gerinda bertambah selama\r\nputaran sehingga membutuhkan torsi berbeda</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">karena gesekan pada poros meningkat setiap kali\r\npedal ditekan lebih cepat</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">karena pedal menghasilkan energi tetap sehingga\r\ntorsinya otomatis naik dengan kecepatan roda</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">karena panjang efektif lengan gaya berubah\r\nakibat perubahan sudut antara tuas penghubung dan engkol</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">karena panjang efektif lengan gaya berubah\r\nakibat perubahan sudut antara tuas penghubung dan engkol</span></p>', NULL, 'E', -0.070, 0, 1, '2026-05-03 16:46:18', '2026-05-03 16:46:18'),
(353, 'ACTofROD41', 11, NULL, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Mesin jahit tradisional menggunakan roda untuk\r\nmenghasilkan gerakan, bahkan ketika pedal tidak ditekan. Saat berputar, torsi\r\nmasukan diubah menjadi energi kinetik rotasi yang disimpan dalam roda.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777767188_69f693140ee62.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: 172.615px; margin: 10px 0px; width: 203.462px;\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">Gambar 38. Mesin jahit tradisional</span></p><p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%;\">Bentuk\r\nroda yang sering digunakan adalah cincin (I=mr²) daripada yang berbentuk\r\npiringan (I=12mr²). Mengapa roda berbentuk cincin lebih disukai daripada roda\r\nberbentuk piringan adalah....</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">roda berbentuk cincin lebih disukai karena\r\nseluruh massanya berada pada jarak yang lebih besar dari sumbu rotasi, sehingga\r\nmomen inersia maksimum dapat dicapai untuk menghasilkan&nbsp; energi kinetik rotasi lebih besar</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">roda berbentuk cincin lebih disukai karena massa\r\nyang lebih jauh dari sumbu rotasi membuat gaya gesekan menjadi lebih kecil\r\nsehingga putaran lebih stabil</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">roda berbentuk cincin lebih disukai karena\r\nbentuk cincin memungkinkan energi kinetik rotasi berubah langsung menjadi torsi\r\ntanpa perubahan kecepatan</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">roda berbentuk cincin lebih disukai karena massa\r\nyang tersebar merata membuat perubahan energi kinetik rotasi menjadi lebih\r\ncepat saat pedal ditekan</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">roda berbentuk cincin lebih disukai karena massa\r\nyang lebih jauh menyebabkan torsi luar yang bekerja mengecil sehingga mesin\r\nlebih mudah berputar</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">roda berbentuk cincin lebih disukai karena\r\nseluruh massanya berada pada jarak yang lebih besar dari sumbu rotasi, sehingga\r\nmomen inersia maksimum dapat dicapai untuk menghasilkan&nbsp; energi kinetik rotasi lebih besar</span></p>', NULL, 'A', 0.060, 0, 1, '2026-05-03 16:46:18', '2026-05-03 16:46:18'),
(354, 'ACTofROD40', 11, NULL, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Gambar 37 menunjukkan piringan putar dengan\r\nsepotong kecil permen karet yang digantung di atasnya. Sensor optik yang\r\nterhubung ke perekam data mengukur kecepatan sudut piringan putar.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777766246_69f68f66626bb.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: 113.281px; margin: 10px 0px; width: 288.756px;\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">Gambar 37. Piringan putar<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"Default\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nIN\">Piringan dirancang untuk berputar terlebih dahulu sebelum berputar bebas.\r\nGumpalan permen karet dijatuhkan dari ketinggian kecil di atas piringan dan\r\nmenempel padanya.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"Default\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\">Piringan putar berbentuk cakram padat dengan momen inersia I = 12MR²<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"Default\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nSV\">Permen karet adalah bola padat dengan momen inersia I = 25MR²<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%;\">Berdasarkan\r\ninformasi eksperimen, untuk menentukan besar perubahan energi kinetik rotasi </span><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%;\">piringan\r\nputar dari saat sebelum permen karet dijatuhkan hingga segera setelah menempel\r\npada piringan putar adalah....</span></span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">perubahan energi kinetik rotasi hanya ditentukan\r\noleh perubahan kecepatan sudut karena momen inersia seluruh sistem tetap</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">perubahan energi kinetik rotasi ditentukan oleh\r\nperubahan momen inersia sistem dan perubahan kecepatan sudut, karena tumbukan\r\ninelastik menambah massa pada radius tertentu</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">perubahan energi kinetik rotasi hanya\r\ndipengaruhi oleh massa permen karet karena permen karet menyebabkan gaya ke\r\nbawah yang memperlambat rotasi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">perubahan energi kinetik rotasi terutama\r\ndipengaruhi oleh energi potensial permen karet saat jatuh karena energi itu\r\nhilang dari sistem rotasi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">perubahan energi kinetik rotasi ditentukan oleh\r\nbesar gaya gesekan udara yang bekerja tepat saat permen karet menempel pada\r\npiringan</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">perubahan energi kinetik rotasi terutama\r\ndipengaruhi oleh energi potensial permen karet saat jatuh karena energi itu\r\nhilang dari sistem rotasi</span></p>', NULL, 'D', -0.481, 0, 1, '2026-05-03 16:46:18', '2026-05-03 16:46:18'),
(355, 'ACTofROD39', 11, NULL, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Pada suatu hari, Rahmat melakukan beberapa\r\nkegiatan berikut.</span></p><p><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\">(i) mengayuh sepeda</font></p><p><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\">(ii) bermain jungkat jungkit dengan temannya</font></p><p><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\">(iii) mendorong meja pada bidang datar yang licin</font></p><p><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\">(iv) mendorong gerobak sampah</font></p><p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Rahmat menyadari bahwa tidak semua kegiatan\r\ntersebut melibatkan kecenderungan benda untuk berotasi terhadap suatu titik\r\natau sumbu tertentu, meskipun sama-sama melibatkan gaya. Kombinasi kegiatan\r\nyang benar-benar merupakan penerapan torsi, beserta alasan yang paling tepat\r\nadalah....</span><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\"></font></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">i dan ii, karena gaya selalu bekerja pada benda\r\nyang bergerak</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">i dan iv, karena penggunaan tali selalu\r\nmenghasilkan torsi&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">ii dan iii, karena gaya digunakan untuk\r\nmemindahkan benda berat&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">iii dan iv, karena torsi berkaitan langsung\r\ndengan besar momentum benda&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">ii dan i, karena gaya bekerja pada jarak\r\ntertentu dari titik tumpu sehingga menimbulkan rotasi</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">ii dan i, karena gaya bekerja pada jarak\r\ntertentu dari titik tumpu sehingga menimbulkan rotasi</span></p>', NULL, 'E', 1.400, 0, 1, '2026-05-03 16:46:18', '2026-05-03 16:46:18'),
(356, 'ACTofROD38', 11, NULL, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Perhatikan gambar 36 berikut.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777765872_69f68df02b7be.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: 137.948px; margin: 10px 0px; width: 258.314px;\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">Gambar 36. Katrol cakram yang dipasang beban<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">Sebuah\r\nkatrol cakram padat bermassa M dan jari-jari R ditopang oleh bantalan yang\r\nmemiliki gesekan yang dapat diabaikan. Seutas tali dengan massa diabaikan\r\ndililitkan sekeliling katrol. Beban dengan massa 0,5 M diikat pada ujung tali.\r\nMomen inersia katrol terhadap sumbu rotasi adalah 0,5 MR<sup>2</sup></span><!--[if gte msEquation 12]><m:oMath><i\r\n style=\'mso-bidi-font-style:normal\'><span lang=IN style=\'font-size:12.0pt;\r\n line-height:107%;font-family:\"Cambria Math\",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-fon