(366, 'ACTofROD28', 11, NULL, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV\">Dua roda P dan Q memiliki massa dan jari-jari\r\nsama, tetapi struktur internalnya berbeda. Keduanya dipasang pada poros licin\r\ndan diberi torsi yang sama. Hasil pengamatan menunjukkan bahwa roda P memiliki\r\nkecepatan sudut akhir yang lebih kecil dibandingkan roda Q.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Kesimpulan\r\npaling tepat yang dapat ditarik dari informasi tersebut adalah....</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">momen inersia roda P lebih besar daripada roda Q</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">momen inersia roda Q lebih besar daripada roda P</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">momentum sudut roda Q lebih besar daripada roda\r\nP</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">distribusi massa roda Q diujung poros dan\r\ndistribusi massa roda P di pusat poros</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">distribusi massa roda P diujung poros dan\r\ndistribusi massa roda Q di pusat poros</span></p>', '<p><span lang=\"SV\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:SV;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">momen inersia roda P lebih besar daripada roda Q</span></p>', NULL, 'A', 0.830, 0, 1, '2026-05-03 16:46:18', '2026-05-03 16:46:18'),
(367, 'ACTofROD27', 11, NULL, '<p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Perhatikan gambar 26 yaitu sebuah mesin cetak\r\nlogam. Jarak dari sumbu rotasi ke pusat setiap bola adalah y. Jari-jari setiap\r\nbola adalah R.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://cd-cat.ct.ws/uploads/editor-images/editor_1777763944_69f6866801aa3.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: 192.228px; margin: 10px 0px; width: 341.896px;\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi\">Gambar 26. Mesin cetak logam</span></p><p><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">Energi\r\nyang tersimpan dalam sistem berasal dari energi kinetik rotasi bola E<sub>k</sub>=1/2 I</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">ω<sup>2</sup></span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">&nbsp;dengan momen inersia bola pejal 2/5 mR<sup>2</sup>+my<sup>2</sup></span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; position: relative; top: 7pt;\"><v:shape id=\"_x0000_i1025\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style=\"width:67.5pt;height:21.5pt\"><v:imagedata src=\"file:///C:/Users/Lenovo/AppData/Local/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_image002.png\" o:title=\"\" chromakey=\"white\"></v:imagedata></v:shape></span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">. Energi yang tersimpan dapat ditingkatkan\r\ndengan:</span></p><ul><li><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">Meningkatkan y sebesar 15% tanpa mengubah R</span></span></span></li><li><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;\">&nbsp;</span></span></span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nmajor-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-ansi-language:IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Meningkatkan R sebesar 15% tanp